	text = text.replace(/Instead, an old man rallies them with poorly timed anti-war sentiments\. (.*?) walks over to the fool and uncorks a punch to silence him right into the mud\./, "但这时，一个老人用不合时宜的反战情绪召集村民。$1 见状，上去对着老人就是一拳，砰的一声，老人无声的倒在泥地上。");
	text = text.replace("Sadly, this only pisses the crowd off more and a great melee breaks out.", "但不幸的是，这种行为只会激怒群众，引发一场大混战。");
