	text = text.replace("After it\'s all said and done there are dead and dying in the mud, all tended to by women with confused and saddened faces, and the lieutenant and his soldiers are nowhere to be seen.", "混战过后，有的人被砍伤了，有的人死在泥地里，边上只剩下一脸困惑和悲伤的女人，而军官和他的士兵却不见了踪影。");
	text = text.replace("You turn to the lieutenant.", "你转向军官。");
