	text = text.replace("Get someone else to muscle peasants.", "找个人来强迫农民。");
	text = text.replace("If you can\'t do it yourself, maybe your side isn\'t fit enough to win in the first place?", "如果你自己做不到，那或许你的队伍本身就太弱了，从一开始就没有想赢？");
	text = text.replace("He huffs and steps up, meeting his chest with yours.", "他怒气冲冲地走上前去，与你相撞，就像两只打架的公鸡那样。");
