	text = text.replace("Predictably, the soldiers charge into the crowd, swords swinging, maces clubbing.", "不出所料，士兵们挥舞着剑或者狼牙棒冲向人群。");
	text = text.replace("A few good laymen go down, having nothing to stop the onslaught, but the sheer number of peasants quickly overwhelms the lieutenant and his men.", "一些站在前面的农民倒下了，没有什么可以阻止进攻，但是农民的数量很快就压倒了军官和他的手下。");
	text = text.replace("A couple of children push a hovel\'s chimney over and the rain of stones crushes a soldier into the mud..", "几个孩子把一间小茅屋的烟囱推倒，一阵石头雨把一名士兵压进了泥里。");
	text = text.replace("As the rest of the soldiers pause, a farmer runs up and impales one with a pitchfork and lifts him skyward as though he were a bale of hay.", "当其他士兵停下脚步时观察情况，一个农夫跑了过来，用干草叉刺穿一个士兵，把他像一捆干草一样高高举到空中。");
	text = text.replace("The lieutenant breaks and flees, but he\'s tripped up by a pair of women who descend upon him with shearing knives.", "军官看情况不对，打算逃跑，但他被两个女人拿着剪刀的妇女绊倒了。");
	text = text.replace("After it\'s all said and done, many villagers and every single soldier is dead.", "一段时间后，战斗结束了，所有士兵都死了，但是村民也死了不少。");
	text = text.replace("Victorious, the townspeople drag the bannermen into the trees and hang their bodies for further mutilation.", "随后，镇民们把贵族的手下拖到树上，把他们的尸体挂起来，以便进一步肢解。");
	text = text.replace("The mercenaries thank you for not needlessly getting involved.", "你的雇佣兵们感谢你没有多管闲事。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s a choice to be made here - stand with the powerless commoners, or go with the violent ambassadors of those who wield power like the goblet of a drunk wench.", "在这里，我们必须做出一个选择－要么站在无能为力的平民一边，要么站在那些随意滥用权力的暴力使节一边。");
	text = text.replace("Of the two, you figure the latter might serve a greater purpose in the future.", "在这两者中，你认为帮助后者在未来可能会对你更有帮助。");
	text = text.replace(/You order the (.*?) to stand with the soldiers\./, "你命令 $1 与士兵站在一起。");
	text = text.replace("It\'s a quick battle, one which ends with the peasants fleeing across the fields and women begging for the wounded to not be executed.", "这是一场速战速决的战斗，结局是农民逃到田野里，妇女乞求不要处死伤员。");
	text = text.replace("Their pleas are not heard.", "他们的请求被无视了。");
	text = text.replace("Cleaning his blade, the lieutenant thanks you for saving him and his men.", "军官擦着他的刀，感谢你救了他和他的手下。");
	text = text.replace("That wasn\'t the smartest decision I could have made, but for some reason I knew you\'d step in to help out.", "那不是我能做出的最明智的决定，但出于某种原因，我知道你会来帮忙的。");
	text = text.replace("Been awhile since I had a good day of killin\'.", "我已经有一段时间没有好好享受杀戮了。");
	text = text.replace("Thanks, sellsword. The nobles will hear of your deeds here.", "谢谢了，佣兵。贵族们将会听到你在这里的事迹。");
	text = text.replace("Ah, powerless commoners standing up against the boot of the amoral nobility.", "唉，无力的平民站起来反抗混蛋贵族。");
	text = text.replace("You stand with the poorer of the two assholes.", "而你决定站在平民这边。");
	text = text.replace(/As soon as the soldiers clash with the peasants, you order the (.*?) to swoop in behind the bannermen and clean up\./, "一旦士兵与农民发生冲突，你就命令 $1 的人乘虚而入。");
	text = text.replace("Each soldier is swiftly stabbed in the back.", "背刺贵族一方。");
	text = text.replace("You take care of the lieutenant yourself, slicing a dagger across his neck.", "你亲自偷袭军官，用匕首划过他的脖子。");
	text = text.replace("He turns around, clutching his mortal wound in an attempt to mend the unmendable.", "他转过身来，紧紧抓住自己致命的伤口，试图弥补这无法弥补的伤口。");
	text = text.replace("Seeing you, his eyes go wide and confused, as though he\'d never expected a sellsword to betray him.", "看到你，他的眼睛睁得大大的，不知所措，好像他从没有想到会有一个佣兵出卖他。");
	text = text.replace("He coughs out a surge of crimson and then falls to his knees and backward into the mud.", "他咳嗽带出出一股深红色的激流，随后跪倒在泥地里，没了声息。");
	text = text.replace("An elderly man slowly approaches as you clean your blade.", "当你清洁刀刃时，一位老人慢慢走近。");
	text = text.replace("He thanks you for saving the village, small it may be, and promises to spread word of your - apparently - \'saintly\' reputation.", "他感谢你拯救了这个小村庄，并承诺传播你的“圣洁”声誉。");

//civilwar_dead_knight_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/You happen across a throng of kids scrambling around something in the grass like flies on a shitpile\. (.*?) starts booting them away\./, "你碰巧遇到一群孩子在草地上围着什么东西团团转，就像一堆屎上的苍蝇一样。$1 开始赶走这些孩子。");
	text = text.replace("Scamper you larks. Scamper!", "你这个笨蛋。跑个什么跑！");
	text = text.replace("Oh, damn. Sir, come take a look!", "噢，该死的。先生，快过来看看！");
	text = text.replace("A fat-faced chubster of a kid yells at you.", "一个胖胖的孩子对你大喊大叫。");
	text = text.replace("I found it first! It\'s mine!", "这是我最先发现的！它是我的！");
	text = text.replace("You effortlessly palm him out of the way and get a look.", "你毫不费力地把他推开，看了一眼。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s a dead knight in the grass and he\'s no doubt been there for a while.", "草地上躺着一个死了一段时间的骑士。");
	text = text.replace("A soft tik-tik-tik noise emits from his armor as ants crawl all over it.", "当蚂蚁在他的盔甲上爬来爬去时，他的盔甲发出一种轻柔的嘀嗒嘀嗒声。");
	text = text.replace("A little girl holds her nose with a pinch.", "一个小女孩一边捏着鼻子。");
	text = text.replace("Somewhat nasally and high-pitched, she tries her hand at some astute diplomacy.", "一边用手扇风，好像周围恶臭让她无法呼吸似的。");
	text = text.replace("Let \'em have it, Robbie!", "让他们尝尝厉害，罗比！");
	text = text.replace("These men are dangerous!", "这些人很危险！");
	text = text.replace("Aren\'t ya? Aren\'t ya some dangerous men?", "是吗？你不也是危险人物吗？");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) unsheathes his weapon and dramatically flashes it around\./, "$1 解开他的武器，并把它呼呼的舞了起来。");
	text = text.replace("The tiny wench is right!", "小丫头说得对！");
	text = text.replace("Y\'all best git before we put ya in the dirt just like we did this here knight!", "你们最好在我们把你们扔进泥里之前离开，就像我们对待这个骑士一样！");
	text = text.replace("That\'s right, we are his murderers and we\'ve come back to see our handiwork!", "没错，这个骑士是我们杀的，现在我们来回头验收成果了！");
	text = text.replace("Screaming and crying, the kids are scattered like birds from a bush.", "孩子们尖叫着，哭喊着，像灌木丛中的小鸟一样四散奔逃。");
	text = text.replace("Robbie remains behind, leering over a bush at his lost treasures.", "罗比留在后面，斜视着灌木丛中他丢失的财宝。");
	text = text.replace("You tell the mercenary he didn\'t need to scare them so badly.", "你告诉手下，他没必要把他们吓得那么厉害。");
	text = text.replace("He shrugs and starts collecting the knight\'s gear.", "他耸耸肩，开始收集骑士的装备。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) eyes Robbie who you notice is beginning to sweat\./, "$1 发现罗比开始出汗了。");
	text = text.replace("The sellsword points a finger.", "这个佣兵用手指着他。");
	text = text.replace("You\'re not just a fat piece of shit, kid.", "这可不只是胖才会这样，孩子。");
	text = text.replace("What are you hiding under your shirt?", "你衬衫下面藏着什么？");
	text = text.replace("You won\'t fool a thief, c\'mon, show it!", "你骗不了我的，来，给我们看看！");
	text = text.replace("Sighing, Robbie lifts his shirt and a bunch of crowns go clattering into the grass. The man nods.", "罗比叹了口气，撩起衬衫，一串王冠哗啦哗啦的掉在草地上。这个人点头。");
	text = text.replace("That\'s what I thought. Now git.", "我也是这么想的。现在你可以离开了。");

//civilwar_deserter_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/While on the road you come across two soldiers of (.*?)\'s army and they\'re stringing up what it appears to be one of their own\./, "你在路上遇到两个 $1的士兵，他们正在架设什么，那个东西似乎是他们自己的。");
	text = text.replace("The man\'s head is put through a noose, but upon seeing you he calls out.", "那人的头被套在绞索里，但一看见你，他就大声喊叫。");
	text = text.replace("They wanted me to kill children!", "他们想让我杀孩子！");
	text = text.replace("This is what I get for not following orders?", "这就是我不服从命令的下场？");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) looks at you with a \'maybe we can do something\' face\./, "$1 带着也许我们能做点什么的表情看着你。");
	text = text.replace(/You find two men of (.*?)\'s army stringing up a man who has been blindfolded\./, "你发现两个 $1的人把一个蒙着眼睛的人绑起来。");
	text = text.replace("Curious, you ask what his crime was.", "出于好奇，你问他犯了什么罪。");
	text = text.replace("One of the executioners laughs.", "其中一个行刑者笑了。");
	text = text.replace("He was ordered to burn a small village and refused.", "他被命令烧毁一个小村庄，但他拒绝了。");
	text = text.replace("You don\'t refuse the nobility, lest this happen.", "你不能拒绝贵族，不然就得被处死。");
	text = text.replace("The blindfolded man spits.", "被蒙住眼睛的人吐了口唾沫。");
	text = text.replace("To the hells with you all.", "你们见鬼去吧。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ll at least have my dignity and honor to the end.", "至少我会一直保持我的尊严与荣誉。");
	text = text.replace("To the side of the path you see a man slinging a rope around a tree branch.", "在小路的一边，你看到一个男人把一根绳子吊在一根树枝上。");
	text = text.replace("A second man pushes a blindfolded prisoner forward, slipping the noose about his neck.", "第二个人把一个被蒙住眼睛的囚犯往前推，把绞索套在他的脖子上。");
	text = text.replace("The executioners see you and put their hands up.", "行刑者看到你，举起手来。");
	text = text.replace("Step back, sellswords.", "退后，佣兵们。");
	text = text.replace(/This man is to be executed under the orders of (.*?)\. Interfere, and you will be dealt with in a similar fashion\./, "这个人将在 $1 的命令下被处死。如果你干涉，你也会被以同样的方式对待。");
	text = text.replace("The prisoner barks out.", "囚犯大叫起来。");
	text = text.replace("They wanted me to murder women and children.", "他们想让我谋杀妇女和儿童。");
	text = text.replace("This is the price I pay for ignoring such orders, but at least I will leave this horrid world with my honor intact.", "这是我无视这些命令所付出的代价，但至少我会带着完整的荣誉离开这个可怕的世界。");
	text = text.replace("The path opens to a shackled man sitting in the grass while two men angrily string a rope along a tree branch.", "小路通向一个戴着镣铐的男人，他坐在草地上，两个男人愤怒地在树枝上系着绳子。");
	text = text.replace("They test it with a few good pulls before nodding and putting a barrel beneath it, presumably for the prisoner to stand on.", "他们试了几次，然后点了点头，放了一个桶在下面，大概是让囚犯站在上面。");
	text = text.replace("The prisoner sees you and calls out.", "囚犯看到你后喊道。");
	text = text.replace("Sellswords, save me! All I did was refuse to burn a temple to the ground!", "佣兵们，救救我！我所做的一切就是拒绝把一座神殿夷为平地！");
	text = text.replace("One of the executioners kicks the man.", "一个行刑者踢了他一脚。");
	text = text.replace("That temple was housing rebels, rebels that killed our lieutenant, you fool!", "那神殿是叛军的住所，叛军杀死了我们的军官，你这个傻瓜！");
	text = text.replace("You deserve this fate more than anyone.", "你比任何人都更应该被这样处死。");
	text = text.replace(/If (.*?) is to win this war, we cannot have rats such as you in our midst\./, "如果 $1 想要赢得这场战争，我们就不能有你们这样的老鼠在我们中间。");
	text = text.replace("You order the executioners to let the man go.", "你命令行刑者放了他。");
	text = text.replace(/They laugh and draw out their swords, but that\'s about the last thing they do as the (.*?) descends upon them with liberating fury, hacking the two soldiers down in mere seconds\./, "他们笑着拔出了剑，但这是他们做的最后一件事，因为 $1 在一瞬间释放出了怒火，短短几秒就把两名士兵砍翻了。");
	text = text.replace("The prisoner thanks you and, in return for his rescue, offers to serve you in battle.", "囚犯感谢你，作为他获救的回报，他愿意在战场上为你效劳。");
	text = text.replace(/You won\'t stand for such an execution and order the men of the (.*?) to intervene\./, "你不能容忍这样的处决，于是你命令 $1 的人去干预。");
	text = text.replace("They quickly draw their weapons and descend upon the soldiers, slaughtering them in but a moment.", "他们迅速拔出武器，扑向士兵，不一会儿就把他们杀死了。");
	text = text.replace("The freed prisoner falls to his feet before you.", "被释放的囚犯在你面前跪下了。");
	text = text.replace("Please, let me fight in your ranks, it is the least I can offer!", "求求你，让我加入你们的队伍吧，这是我唯一能做到的了！");
	text = text.replace(/You order the (.*?) to save the prisoner\./, "你命令 $1 去营救那个囚犯。");
	text = text.replace("It is an odd series of sights and sounds to see men who thought themselves the executioners be so suddenly put to the blade.", "那个囚犯的命运瞬间逆转了，认为自己是行刑者的人突然被砍死。");
	text = text.replace("Such turns of fortune bring out wild, womanly-like screaming.", "这样的命运轮回带来一阵狂野的尖叫。");
	text = text.replace("Your men would have made it quick had they not tried to run, but a man who is intent on saving himself oft dies the slowest.", "如果那些人没有逃跑的话，你的手下会做的更加干脆利落，但是，一个求生欲望强的人是很难杀的。");
	text = text.replace("The prisoner, meanwhile, falls to your feet and offers allegiance.", "与此同时，囚犯倒在你的脚下，向你效忠。");
	text = text.replace("You order the man rescued.", "你命令去营救那个囚犯。");
	text = text.replace("One of the soldiers draws his sword and is immediately cut down for his misplaced confidence.", "其中一个对方士兵立刻自信的拔出了剑，随后就因为这错误的自信被砍翻了。");
	text = text.replace("The other soldier, seemingly sharper of mind, has already run off.", "另一个士兵，看起来头脑清醒，已经跑掉了。");
	text = text.replace(/No doubt he\'ll tell (.*?) of what you have done here\./, "毫无疑问，他会告诉 $1 你们在这的所作所为。");
	text = text.replace("The rescued prisoner comes to you personally, going to one knee as he bows.", "获救的囚犯来见你，单膝跪地向你鞠躬。");
	text = text.replace("Thank you, sellsword. You have my blade for this day until my last.", "谢谢你，佣兵。今天我的命就交给你了。");
	text = text.replace("In your mind, it is unlikely that the two executioners would abandon their noble flags to join you.", "在你看来，这两个行刑者不太可能放弃他们的贵族阵营而加入你。");
	text = text.replace("But it is quite probable that the prisoner would fight on your side, were you to free him.", "但是，如果你放了那个囚犯，他很可能会站在你这边与你一同作战。");
	text = text.replace("So you order his rescue.", "所以你下令营救他。");
	text = text.replace(/One of the soldiers draws his sword and pledges allegiance to the (.*?)\. It\'s the last thing he does\./, "其中一个敌方士兵拔出他的剑，宣誓效忠 $1。这是他这辈子做的最后一件事了。");
	text = text.replace("The other soldier flees.", "另一个士兵逃走了。");
	text = text.replace("Maybe you could have recruited him, but it\'s unlikely he\'ll come back given the prompt killing of his partner.", "也许你本可以招募他，但考虑到他的搭档被迅速杀害，他不太可能回来。");
	text = text.replace("Most likely he will tell his superiors of your actions here.", "他很可能会把你在这里的行为告诉他的上级。");
	text = text.replace("You go to the freed prisoner.", "你去找被释放的囚犯。");
	text = text.replace(/He hurriedly bows and offers to fight for the (.*?)\./, "他连忙鞠了一躬，提出要加入 $1。");
	text = text.replace("You order the soldiers to let the man go.", "你命令士兵放了那个人。");
	text = text.replace(/One laughs and simply tightens the noose about his neck and starts to hang him\. (.*?) jumps forward and knocks an executioner to the ground\./, "一个人大笑起来，只是收紧套在他脖子上的绞索，然后开始吊起他。$1 跳到前面，将行刑者击倒在地。");
	text = text.replace("He beats his face in with a rock while the second soldier runs off.", "当第二个士兵逃跑时，他摔了一跤，没追上。");
	text = text.replace("No doubt he\'ll tell his commanders what you\'ve done here.", "毫无疑问，那个逃兵会告诉他的指挥官你在这里做了什么。");
	text = text.replace("Freed, the prisoner comes to you personally and bows, offering allegiance in return for his rescue.", "获释后，被释放的囚犯亲自来向你鞠躬，表示将对你效忠来作为报答。");
	text = text.replace("Though you can\'t necessarily fault the man for ignoring his orders, the decision was his, not yours, just as his punishment will be his, and not yours.", "虽然你不能因为一个人无视他的命令而责怪他，但是这个决定是他的，不是你的，就像他的惩罚是他的，不是你的。");
	text = text.replace(/You order the (.*?) to keep marching\./, "你命令 $1 继续前进。");
	text = text.replace(/You\'ve no reason to involve the (.*?) in the politics of the quarreling nobles\./, "你没有理由把 $1 牵扯进那些争吵不休的贵族的政治活动中。");
	text = text.replace("The prisoner nods, understandingly.", "囚犯点头，表示理解。");
	text = text.replace("He lifts his head high before they hang him straight.", "在他们把他直接吊起来之前，他把头抬得很高。");
	text = text.replace("The executioners glance at you, perhaps sensing that you might step in to absolutely ruin their day.", "行刑者们看了你一眼，也许感觉到你可能会介入，彻底毁掉他们的一天。");
	text = text.replace("Instead, you tell the prisoner that it was his choice that got him here.", "相反，你告诉囚犯，是他的选择让他来到这里。");
	text = text.replace("He nods solemnly. The executioners rush to hang him, lest this dangerous stranger crossing their path have a sudden change of heart.", "他郑重地点头。行刑者们争先恐后地绞死他，以免这个穿过他们道路的危险陌生人突然改变心意。");

//civilwar_flavor_event.nut
	text = text.replace("A canopy billowing loosely across leaning tentpoles, given ghostly life by the moans of the men lingering beneath.", "一个树冠松散地在倾斜的帐篷上翻腾着，下面徘徊的人们的呻吟给了他们幽灵般的生命。");
	text = text.replace("You watch as elder healers go from wounded to wounded, but there isn\'t much to be done here.", "你看着年长的治疗师从一个伤员走到另一个伤员，但这里没有什么可做的。");
	text = text.replace("Passing their hands in the shape of aerial rites, these elder healers think it best that these fallen and falling warriors go into the next realm protected from whatever spirits lay beyond.", "这些年长的治疗师以空中仪式的形式伸出双手，他们认为最好的办法就是让这些倒下的战士进入另一个世界，远离那里的鬼魂。");
	text = text.replace("You come across two men laying by the side of a small road.", "你遇到两个躺在小路边的男人。");
	text = text.replace("They kick back at the sight of you, one raising a sword.", "他们一看到你就退缩，一个人举起了一把剑。");
	text = text.replace("It wobbles in his hand until he can no longer muster the strength to keep it up.", "它在他的手中摇晃，直到他再也没有力气把它举起来。");
	text = text.replace("Just let us die in peace.", "让我们安静地死去吧。");
	text = text.replace(/A few more men emerge under the banner of (.*?)\. They nod and tell you to get on\./, "又有几个人出现在 $1。他们点头，叫你继续前进。");
	text = text.replace("Keep it moving, strangers.", "继续前进，陌生人。");
	text = text.replace("Both sides of the road are lined with wounded warriors, armored men splayed out, hands draped across their foreheads or clutching the nubs left over from limbs gone missing.", "道路两旁排列着受伤的战士，全副武装的士兵摊开四肢，双手搭在额头上，或是紧紧抓住四肢残缺的部分。");
	text = text.replace("In a nearby field there are signs of what battle had brought them to this state of grisly being.", "在附近的田野里，有迹象表明是什么战斗把他们带到了这种可怕的境地。");
	text = text.replace("This sad lot of men, apparently, \'won\' that fight.", "很显然，这群可悲的男人“赢”了那场战斗。");
	text = text.replace(/You find a few noblemen of (.*?) peering over a sea of skewered and slain men - apparently you just missed some epic battle\./, "你发现一些 $1 的贵族在一群被扭曲和杀害的人组成的尸海上观望，很明显你错过了一场史诗般的战斗。");
	text = text.replace("Amongst the dead and dying you watch as swordsman pick through the enemy wounded and finish them off.", "在死亡和垂死的人中，你看着剑客挑出敌人的伤兵，将他们杀死。");
	text = text.replace("A few guards head you off.", "几个警卫把你赶走了。");
	text = text.replace("This ain\'t your war.", "这不是你的战争。");
	text = text.replace("Keep on moving or we\'ll make it yours.", "别管这事，否则我们会把它变成你的。");
	text = text.replace("You come across a few noblemen standing atop a hill.", "你遇到几个贵族站在山顶上。");
	text = text.replace("Guards immediately rush to you, swords drawn.", "卫兵立刻冲过来，拔出剑来。");
	text = text.replace("Do you belong here?", "你住在这里吗？");
	text = text.replace("You look beyond the group to see that scribes are writing down notes.", "你看向卫兵身后，看到书记员正在写笔记。");
	text = text.replace("And beyond the scribes lays a scene of incredible destruction, great swathes of dead men from some pointless battle or another.", "在书记员的身后，是一片令人难以置信的毁灭景象，在一场或另一场毫无意义的战斗中，一批批死去的人。");
	text = text.replace("I asked you a question, stranger.", "我在问你，陌生人。");
	text = text.replace("You glance back at the guard.", "你回头看了看卫兵。");
	text = text.replace("The noblemen are also looking down at you now.", "贵族们现在也在看着你。");
	text = text.replace(/Shaking your head, you order the (.*?) to get moving before y\'all get into another ordeal\./, "你摇了摇头，命令 $1 在所有人都陷入另一场磨难之前行动起来。");
	text = text.replace("You come across a woman cleaning the wounds of a well armored man.", "你遇到一个女人在清理一个穿着盔甲的男人的伤口。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s got some decent equipment on him, and a pair of very dim eyes stare up at you from the faceguard.", "他身上带着一些不错的装备，一双非常暗淡的眼睛从面罩上盯着你。");
	text = text.replace("Drawing out your sword, you tell the woman to step aside so you can finish the job and collect the goods.", "你拔出你的剑，让那个女人站到一边，这样你就可以完成任务，去取货了。");
	text = text.replace("She shakes her head.", "她摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("If it\'s the armor you\'re interested in you\'ll have pay better attention.", "如果这是你感兴趣的盔甲，那么你应该更加注意。");
	text = text.replace(/This man fought under the banner of (.*?), the rest of which stand over that hill yonder\./, "这个人打着 $1 的旗号，其他的人就站在那边的山上。");
	text = text.replace("They so much as peer over it while you shake us down, they\'ll be skewering you on stakes and hanging you for the crows.", "当你调查我们的时候，他们已经在观察了，他们会把你弄到木桩上钉死，然后把你吊起来喂乌鸦。");
	text = text.replace("Suspicious, you lock eyes with her.", "你觉得非常可疑，于是你盯着她看。");
	text = text.replace("The woman doesn\'t so much as flinch, but she does eventually move away from the wounded man.", "女人并没有退缩，但是她最终还是离开了受伤的男人。");
	text = text.replace("If you think I\'m lying, then have at it.", "如果你认为我在撒谎，那就试试看。");
	text = text.replace("Go on, take his life and take his gear.", "继续，夺去他的生命，夺走他的装备。");
	text = text.replace(/You shake your head and tell the (.*?) to get going\./, "你摇摇头，告诉 $1 继续前进。");
	text = text.replace("No more than a few feet further up the road do you see what is seemingly half an army of the noble house\'s men lingering.", "再往前不到几英尺，你看到半支贵族家族的军队似乎还在徘徊。");
	text = text.replace("A few soldiers hobble past you on the road.", "几个士兵在路上从你身边蹒跚而过。");
	text = text.replace("Healers are tending to their wounds, and a few women bound after them, sobbing or moaning into their fisted hands.", "治疗师正在照料他们的伤口，几个女人在他们身后被绑着，对着他们的拳头哭泣或呻吟。");
	text = text.replace("One of the men pauses at the sight of you.", "其中一个男人看到你停了下来。");
	text = text.replace("Don\'t try anything, mercenary.", "不要尝试任何事，雇佣兵。");
	text = text.replace(/The rest of (.*?)\'s army marches just yonder\./, "其余 $1的军队就在那边行军。");
	text = text.replace("You nod and let the wounded troop pass.", "你点头，让伤兵过去。");
	text = text.replace("The army never does appear.", "但之后军队从未出现过。");
	text = text.replace("You come across a man being hounded by scoundrels.", "你遇到一个被歹徒追赶的人。");
	text = text.replace("Seeing you, the thieves quickly take the fallen man\'s boots, pants, and bits of armor and one lopes off with a sword, the blade leveled across raised arms like some heretical thaumaturge carrying a relic of impossible yet brittle power.", "看到你，盗贼们很快抢走了那个倒下的人的靴子、裤子和盔甲碎片，其中一人用剑一跃而下，刀刃横在举起的手臂上，像是某种异端的屠夫携带着一种不可能但脆弱的遗俗的力量。");
	text = text.replace("When you get to the wounded soldier he raises his hands to the sky, your silhouette no doubt blurred between his splayed fingers.", "当你走到伤兵身边时，他举起双手指向天空，你的影子无疑在他张开的手指间模糊不清。");
	text = text.replace("He says something which you do not hear and then he is dead.", "他说了一些你听不清的话，然后就死了。");
	text = text.replace("There is nothing else to take from him.", "他身上已经没有东西能被夺走了。");
	text = text.replace("A wounded man is sitting up against a signpost.", "一个受伤的人正坐在路标旁。");
	text = text.replace("He nods at you as you near.", "你走近时，他向你点头。");
	text = text.replace("Mercenaries?", "雇佣兵？");
	text = text.replace(/As you get closer, you see the sigil of (.*?) stitched across an unfurled and trampled banner\./, "当你走近的时候，你看到 $1 的徽章被缝在一个展开的旗帜上。");
	text = text.replace("You don\'t answer his question, instead looking around for an ambush or soldiers from his house.", "你没有回答他的问题，而是环顾四周，看看有没有埋伏，或者他家里有没有士兵。");
	text = text.replace("There are none. And the man himself has been stripped to his skivvies.", "什么都没有。而他自己也被剥光了衣服。");
	text = text.replace("He coughs and shifts as though to tilt the pain from one end of his body to the other.", "他咳嗽着，变换着身体姿势，好像要把疼痛从身体的一端转移到另一端。");
	text = text.replace("Yeah, I suppose you don\'t have to answer.", "是的，我想你不必回答。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ll be dead soon anyhow.", "无论如何，我很快就要死了。");
	text = text.replace("I\'d feel a lot better if you didn\'t stick around to watch.", "如果你不留下来看，我会感觉好很多。");
	text = text.replace("A pleading eye meets yours.", "一双恳求的眼睛与你相遇。");
	text = text.replace("With pity, you leave the man to a peaceful, lonely death.", "带着怜悯，你离开了这个男人，让他安详而孤独地死去。");
	text = text.replace("You find a crippled man crawling toward a dead cow.", "你发现一个瘸子爬向一头死牛。");
	text = text.replace(/He\'s got the banner of (.*?) trailing behind him, a messied and shredded coattail if there ever was one\./, "他身后拖着一条 $1 的旗帜，那个旗帜看起来就像一个乱七八糟的碎燕尾。");
	text = text.replace("You watch as he nestls against the bosom of the animal and begins to suck on its teat.", "你看着他依偎在动物的怀里，开始吮吸它的乳头。");
	text = text.replace("He tries each grayed nub in turn, though not a drop of milk is to be had for Death is the driest of counties.", "他依次尝试每一个灰白的小块，但是没有一滴牛奶可以喝，因为死亡导致干燥的原因。");
	text = text.replace("Sighing, he flops over and finally sees you.", "他叹了一口气，跌倒在地，终于看到了你。");
	text = text.replace("Ah hell, don\'t look at me like that.", "啊，见鬼，别那样看着我。");
	text = text.replace("You offer water and he takes a sip.", "你给他水，他喝了一小口。");
	text = text.replace("Dreadful. I guess I won\'t miss this place much.", "太可怕了。我想我不会太怀念这个地方。");
	text = text.replace("You nod and think to speak, but you notice the man is staring straight ahead, his arms flat at his sides, and a couple of flies got news of his passing before you did.", "你点头，想要说话，但你注意到那个人直直地盯着前方，双臂平放在身体两侧，几只苍蝇在你之前就知道了他的死讯。");
	text = text.replace(/You come across a naked man clothed only in the torn banner of (.*?)\. A large black bird is eating his feet\./, "你遇到一个赤身裸体的男人，身上只披着属于 $1 的撕破的旗帜。一只大黑鸟正在吃他的脚。");
	text = text.replace("He stares at it, then at you, explaining himself in embarrassment.", "他盯着它，然后盯着你，尴尬地解释着自己。");
	text = text.replace("It asked if it could have a bite.", "它问能不能咬一口。");
	//text = text.replace("You raise an eyebrow.", "你挑挑眉毛。");
	text = text.replace("And you said yes?", "然后你说可以？");
	//text = text.replace("The man shrugs.", "那人耸了耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("I don\'t remember what I said.", "我不记得我有说。");
	text = text.replace("With a crack, the beak rips off a toe.", "随着一声裂纹，鸟喙撕裂了一个脚趾。");
	text = text.replace("You look back at the man, but he\'s slowly tilting over, the light faded from his eyes.", "你回头看那个人，但他慢慢地倾斜过来，光线从他的眼睛里消失了。");
	text = text.replace("The bird hops up to his head where there be easier pickings.", "那只鸟跳到它的头上，那里有更容易采摘的食物。");
	text = text.replace("Walls of smoke curl beyond the eaves of a burning farmstead.", "烟雾缭绕在燃烧着的农田的屋檐下。");
	text = text.replace("The owners are all dead in the grass.", "所有人都死在草地上了。");
	text = text.replace(/A dog howls wildly and then runs off at the sight of you, as though you were there to finish the job\. (.*?) nods into a pile of weeds\./, "一只狗狂吠着，一看见你就跑开了，好像这件事是你干的一样。$1 向一堆杂草点头。");
	text = text.replace("They didn\'t even spare the youngins.", "他们甚至连孩子都不放过。");
	text = text.replace("You spit and shake your head.", "你吐了口唾沫，摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("No, they did not.", "不，他们没有。");
	text = text.replace("Tufts of grey smoke pipe over a hill.", "一簇簇灰色的烟雾从山上袅袅升起。");
	text = text.replace("Cresting it, you discover a farmstead ablaze.", "最重要的是，你发现一个农场着火了。");
	text = text.replace("A few souls hang from a nearby tree.", "附近的树上挂着几个灵魂。");
	text = text.replace("Their necks show signs of desperation - their hands were not bound - and footprints in the earth show that whoever did this probably watched them die.", "他们的脖子上显示出绝望的迹象－他们的手没有被绑住－地上的脚印表明，不管是谁干的，都是可能看着他们死去的。");
	text = text.replace("A dead dog is at the base of the tree and another headless mutt swings by its feet.", "一只死狗躺在树下，另一只无头杂种狗在它的脚边摇摆。");
	text = text.replace(/Fresh blood still drips\. (.*?) comes up to your side\./, "新鲜的血液仍在滴落。$1 站到你身旁。");
	text = text.replace("We should get going, sir, before something thinks us the perpetrators here.", "我们得走了，先生，别让人以为我们是凶手。");
	text = text.replace("You come upon a smoldering farmstead.", "你来到一个正在燃烧的农庄。");
	text = text.replace(/There are bodies amongst the wood, though the charred ruin all looks the same to you. (.*?) joins you\./, "尽管烧焦后的焦状物看起来都是一样的，但是你还是发现了在木头中间有尸体。 随后，$1 向你汇报情况。");
	text = text.replace("Searched the area, sir.", "搜查了整个地区，先生。");
	text = text.replace("Didn\'t find nothin\' worth taking.", "没有发现任何值得带走的东西。");
	text = text.replace("Whoever did this was quite thorough.", "做这件事的人做得很彻底。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) points toward the horizon, more particularly toward tufts of smoke wafting lazily over a hillcrest\./, "$1 指向地平线，特别是指向山顶上飘荡的一簇簇烟雾。");
	text = text.replace("Should we go check it out?", "我们要去看看吗？");
	text = text.replace("A few riders, well-armed and with lances so long and large you know they seek only one thing - enormous and pitched battles.", "一些骑士，全副武装，装备着长而大的骑枪，你知道他们只寻求一件事－激烈的战斗。");
	text = text.replace("Not wanting to risk running into those responsible, and whatever army might be with them, you tell the men to stay low and carry on.", "你不想冒险撞上那些人，那些导致冒烟的人，你告诉手下要保持低调，继续前进。");
	text = text.replace("A horse ablaze, scattering down the road hawing and crackling like some nightmare fetched from a desert sleep.", "一匹马在熊熊燃烧，像沙漠中的梦魇一样，摇摇晃晃地跑在路上，吱吱作响。");
	text = text.replace("You watch as the animal buckles and goes headfirst into a ditch where it rolls and pitches, stands, stumbles, and finally goes still.", "你看着这只动物一个踉跄，头朝下掉进沟里，在那里翻滚、站立、绊倒，最后一动不动。");
	text = text.replace("Turning down the road, you come to find a stable consumed by fires and a nearby hovel burnt to cinders.", "沿着这条路转下去，你发现一个马厩被大火烧毁了，附近的一个小茅屋被烧成了灰烬。");
	text = text.replace("A few laymen are dead in the grass and their dogs, goats, and sheep and all else is there with them.", "有几个村民死在草地上，他们的狗、山羊、绵羊和其他一切都在那里。");
	text = text.replace("You\'re not sure which side of the realm\'s war is responsible for this, but you\'ve no desire to stick around and find out.", "你不确定这场屠杀是由王国的哪一方造成的，但你并不想留下来弄清原委。");
	text = text.replace("You come upon a hovel with fires blazing forth from its windows.", "你看见一间小屋，窗户里有熊熊燃烧的火焰。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s a body in the grass, skinned and, by the looks on its face, it was a slow treatment.", "草丛中有一具被剥了皮的尸体，从它脸上的表情来看，这是一次缓慢的处理。");
	text = text.replace("Suddenly, the door to the home kicks open and a man on fire stumbles out.", "突然，家门被踢开了，一个着火的人跌跌撞撞地走了出来。");
	text = text.replace("He takes one look at you and your men, screams, and simply goes back inside.", "他看了你和你的手下一眼，尖叫着，然后就回到里面去了。");
	text = text.replace("The roof collapses and whatever terror was born here finally dies.", "屋顶坍塌了，无论那个人在恐惧什么，现在都消失了。");
	text = text.replace(/You tell the (.*?) to get moving lest someone, or some large army, come to think it was you who did this\./, "你告诉 $1 迅速离开，以免有人，或者一些军队，认为这件事是你干的。");
	text = text.replace("You come across a soldier standing with his hands tented over the end of a spiked spear.", "你遇到一个士兵，他紧绷的双手搭在长矛上。");
	text = text.replace("He nods at you.", "他向你点头。");
	text = text.replace("\'Ello. If I were you, I\'d keep moving.", "你好。如果我是你，我就会继续前进。");
	text = text.replace("Looking around, you ask what the man is doing out here.", "环顾四周，你问这个人在这里做什么。");
	text = text.replace(/Keeping watch for the army of (.*?)\. We is at war, don\'tcha know\?/, "观察 $1 的军队。我们在打仗，你不知道吗？");
	text = text.replace("He spits and throws his hand out to the horizon.", "他吐了一口唾沫，把手伸向地平线。");
	text = text.replace("Rest of the army stands thataway.", "其余的军队就驻扎在那边。");
	text = text.replace("So I\'d fly like a crooked bee and go around.", "所以我会像一只蜜蜂一样飞来飞去。");
	text = text.replace("You nod and take the man\'s advice.", "你点头接受了他的建议。");
	text = text.replace("Sure enough, you eventually skirt around the edge of an enormous military camp.", "果然，你最终从一个巨大的军营边绕过。");
	text = text.replace("An old man is founding squatting in the middle of a path.", "一位老人蹲在路中间寻找着什么。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s eating nuts and mushrooms.", "他在吃坚果和蘑菇。");
	text = text.replace("He looks up at you.", "他抬头看着你。");
	text = text.replace(/More of (.*?)\'s soldiers\?/, "更多 $1的士兵？");
	text = text.replace("You shake your head.", "你摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("Mercenaries.", "雇佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("The man cocks his head.", "那个人昂起头。");
	text = text.replace("Didn\'t know there was a difference.", "我不知道这有什么不同。");
	//text = text.replace("You nod.", "你点头。");
	text = text.replace("We do not fly a noble banner.", "我们不挂贵族的旗帜。");
	text = text.replace("The man jaws on a nut.", "那个人咬住一颗坚果。");
	text = text.replace("Ah, yes, pressed into battle by way of gold.", "唉，是的，为钱而战。");
	text = text.replace("You fly the most common banner of all, soldier.", "你挂着最普通的旗帜，士兵。");
	text = text.replace("Would you like a mushroom?", "你想要蘑菇吗？");
	text = text.replace("He holds one up.", "他举起其中一个。");
	text = text.replace("It is mushed and muddied.", "那个已经变成糊状和泥状的了。");
	text = text.replace("You decline and order the men to get to marching again.", "你拒绝并命令士兵们继续前进。");
	text = text.replace(/You come across a few men flying the (.*?) banner\./, "你遇到一些人挂着 $1 的旗帜。");
	text = text.replace("They\'re yanking dogs at the ends of their leashes, and the dogs are being separated from corpses, leashes of flesh pulled between their teeth and the bodies.", "他们拉扯着狗链，把狗从尸体中拉出来，把狗牙从尸体里拉出来。");
	text = text.replace("Spotting you, one of the soldiers tells you off.", "一个士兵发现了你，命令你离开。");
	text = text.replace("We ain\'t got money for your services, mercenary, but I\'ll put an axe in that dumb face of yours if you don\'t move on.", "雇佣兵，我们没有请你服务的钱，但是如果你不离开，我就用斧子砍你那张蠢脸。");
	text = text.replace("There are far, far too many soldiers around to respond to that so you just nod and move on.", "周围有太多太多的士兵对此无动于衷，所以你只是点了点头，然后继续前进。");
	text = text.replace("You spot a shepherd herding goats along a hillside.", "你看到一个牧羊人在山坡上放羊。");
	text = text.replace("He spots you and waves.", "他发现了你，挥了挥手。");
	text = text.replace("This is not the safest place for folks like me.", "对于像我这样的人来说，这不是最安全的地方。");
	text = text.replace("He kicks one of the goats along.", "他踢了一只山羊。");
	text = text.replace("It bays and blurts and froths, but moves along all the same, clambering and shuffling amongst its brothers.", "它口吐白沫，但仍和平常一样移动，在它的兄弟们中间爬来爬去。");
	//text = text.replace("The man shakes his head.", "那人摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("This war between the noble houses has brought so much bloodshed to this land.", "贵族家族之间的战争给这片土地带来了如此多的血腥事件。");
	text = text.replace("The shepherd boots along another of his flock.", "牧羊人赶着他的另一群羊。");
	text = text.replace("I guess it\'s only a matter of time until they come to me looking for milk, and then for meat, and then for me.", "我想他们来找我要牛奶，然后是肉，最后是我，这只是个时间问题。");
	text = text.replace("Just another warm body thrown into the thresher these nobles call a \'grand honor\' or some such shite.", "只不过是被贵族以伟大荣誉或者类似的狗屁东西为理由，丢进绞肉机的温暖身体罢了。");
	text = text.replace("You let the man and his herd pass before continuing on yourself.", "你让那个人和他的羊群过去，然后继续自己的生活。");
	text = text.replace("You come across a man standing aside the ruins of what appear to be his home.", "你看到一个男人站在他家的废墟旁。");
	text = text.replace("Well, there goes all I had.", "好吧，我的一切都完了。");
	text = text.replace("He seems rather calm about the whole affair.", "他似乎对整个事件相当冷静。");
	text = text.replace("He spits and looks around.", "他吐了口唾沫，环顾四周。");
	text = text.replace("Hope they didn\'t take off with my dog.", "希望他们没有把我的狗带走。");
	text = text.replace("The man lets out a sharp whistle, pauses, then nods grimly.", "那个男人发出尖锐的口哨声，停顿了一下，然后严肃地点了点头。");
	text = text.replace("Suppose they did.", "看来他们也带走了。");
	text = text.replace("He goes over his charcoaled hovel and begins to kick the wooden frames away.", "他走过自己的木板棚屋，开始踢开木框架。");
	text = text.replace(/Excuse me, sir mercenary, I need to rebuild so that those damned (.*?) grunts have something else to knock over the next time they come around\./, "劳驾，雇佣兵先生，我需要重建一下房子，这样那些 $1 的该死手下下次来的时候就有别的东西可以敲了。");
	text = text.replace("By the way, if you ever see a dog, any kind of dog, send it my way.", "顺便说一句，如果你看到一只狗，任何一种狗，请给我送过来。");
	text = text.replace("Your company\'s nice, but I prefer the muttly sort of companionship.", "你的陪伴很好，但我更喜欢那种含蓄的友谊。");
	text = text.replace("You nod and go on your way.", "你点头，继续走你的路。");
	text = text.replace("Not far off you do find a dog, but it is in no state to be returned to anyone.", "在不远的地方，你确实找到了一只狗，但它现在的状态是不能还给任何人的。");
	text = text.replace("A fire consumes a farmstead, and the pyros responsible are just riding over a hill yonder.", "一场大火烧毁了一个农场，负责的点火的人骑着马翻过了那边的一座小山。");
	text = text.replace("When they leave, you rush to the home and come to hear screams inside.", "当他们离开的时候，你冲到房子边上，听到里面的尖叫声。");
	text = text.replace("The door has been jammed with shut with a wooden post.", "门被一根木柱子堵住了。");
	text = text.replace("You kick it aside and instantly fires burst forth and a woman scatters out from the flames.", "你把它踢到一边，立刻就有火焰冒出来，一个女人从火焰中扑了出来。");
	text = text.replace("She is in tatters, smoky and charcoaled and ghastly orange.", "她衣衫褴褛，烟雾缭绕，焦炭烧焦，皮肤呈可怕的橙色。");
	text = text.replace("It is too late.", "太晚了。");
	text = text.replace("She falls into the grass and you can only step away.", "她倒在草地上，你只能走开。");
	text = text.replace("The hovel cracks and then collapses.", "小屋裂开了，然后塌了。");
	text = text.replace("A man barks out to you.", "一个男人对你大喊大叫。");
	text = text.replace("Like what you see, mercenary?", "就像你看到的，雇佣兵？");
	text = text.replace("Why don\'t you go on and get going.", "你为什么不继续走呢。");
	text = text.replace(/It\'s the bannermen of (.*?) and there are far too many soldiers to start any sort of battle\./, "这是 $1 的手下，已经有太多的士兵开始烧杀掠夺了。");
	text = text.replace("You get on going.", "你继续前进。");
	text = text.replace("The trees that line the path are creaking with ropes weighted with corpses.", "小路两旁的树被装满尸体的绳子压得吱吱作响。");
	text = text.replace("Every branch has found a use in this vocation - you count at least a dozen bodies swinging, most with sacks over their heads.", "每一根树枝都在这个职业中找到了用途－至少有12具尸体在摇摆，大多数尸体头上都挂着袋子。");
	text = text.replace(/The house words of (.*?) have been carved into the base of the tree\./, "这棵树的底部刻有 $1 的字样。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s a sort of haughty confidence in the typography.", "排版上有一种傲慢的自信。");
	text = text.replace(/A few soldiers of (.*?) stand beside a tree\./, "几个 $1 的士兵站在一棵树旁。");
	text = text.replace("It is caked with blood from treetop to its roots.", "它从树梢到根部都沾满了血。");
	text = text.replace("You can hear the squash of the soldiers\' boots as they step through it.", "你可以听到士兵们走过的时候踩踏的声音。");
	text = text.replace("Say, mercenary, do you think the dead could fertilize new trees?", "说吧，雇佣兵，你认为死人可以给新的树施肥吗？");
	text = text.replace("The man sounds awfully educated to be a murderous soldier, but really you have no idea what fertilize means.", "这个人听起来在成为一名刽子手前受过很好的教育，但实际上你根本不知道肥料是什么意思。");
	text = text.replace("You simply nod. He nods in return.", "你只是点头。他点头作为回应。");
	text = text.replace("Yeah, I figured as much.", "是的，我想也是。");
	text = text.replace("Well, I suppose in a couple years there\'s gonna be a whole forest thataway.", "好吧，我想再过几年就会有一整片森林了。");
	text = text.replace("He points toward some distance, silhouettes of horror stacked high in the grass.", "他指着远处，恐怖的轮廓堆在高高的草丛里。");
	text = text.replace("The man bursts into laughter.", "那人突然大笑起来。");
	text = text.replace("You tell your men to get going before something stupid goes down.", "你告诉你的人在一些愚蠢的事情发生之前离开。");
	text = text.replace("You come to find a few trees along the path have been cut down and their stumps sawed into spikes.", "你来到这里，发现沿路有几棵树被砍倒了，树桩被锯成了尖刺。");
	text = text.replace("This wasn\'t an artistic matter - bodies have been spiked there, grisly and cruel, faces appropriately contorted to the horrors that met them in the end.", "这不是一件艺术品－尸体被钉在那里，恐怖而残忍，脸被适当地扭曲成恐怖的样子。");
	text = text.replace(/A few bannermen of (.*?) stand nearby, seemingly happy with their work\./, "几个 $1 的手下站在附近，似乎对他们的工作很满意。");
	text = text.replace("Hey, mercenary. \'Wood\' you please kindly move along?", "嘿，雇佣兵。“木头”你能不能让开？");
	text = text.replace("He laughs and turns to the rest of his men.", "他笑了笑，转向他的其他手下。");
	text = text.replace("Get it?", "懂吗？");
	text = text.replace("Moving along a path, you come across a bodies all clumped together.", "沿着一条小路走，你遇到一堆堆的尸体。");
	text = text.replace("They\'re lying face down and naked.", "他们脸朝下赤身裸体地躺着。");
	text = text.replace("Wounds pepper their backs, superficial until they weren\'t.", "伤口会在他们的背上留下伤疤。");
	text = text.replace("Whoever did this wanted to exact some amount of pain on these poor folks - and those creatures of crueler stock might still be around.", "无论是谁干的，都想给这些可怜的人们带来一些痛苦－而那些更加残忍的生物可能还在附近。");
	text = text.replace(/You spot a banner of (.*?) laying in the mud just nearby\./, "你看到一个 $1 的旗帜就在附近的泥地上。");
	text = text.replace(/That\'s enough to spur the (.*?) along before it can find trouble\./, "这是在 $1 遇到麻烦之前的一个警告。");
	text = text.replace("A few mounds of earth mottle the sides of the path you are on.", "你正在走的路旁垒着几个土丘。");
	text = text.replace("Some mudworn shovels are nearby, and you can\'t help but notice that a hand is sticking forth from one of the graves.", "附近有一些用旧的铲子，你注意到有一只手从一个坟墓中伸出来。");
	text = text.replace("Uncovering it, you find a naked corpse, mouth full of dirt and beetles.", "于是你挖开它，你发现一具赤裸的尸体，满嘴的泥土和甲虫。");
	text = text.replace("You need not uncover the rest to know they\'re in a similar state.", "你不需要挖开其他土丘，就可以知道它们都处于相似的状态。");
	text = text.replace(/You come to find a body crucified to a signpost with (.*?)\'s sigil carved into his forehead\./, "你发现一具尸体被钉十字架上，前额上有 $1的家徽。");
	text = text.replace("His hands help aide you in finding a nearby town, though his open mouth seems to shout to not go there.", "他的手帮助你找到附近的一个城镇，虽然他张开的嘴似乎在喊不要去那里。");
	text = text.replace(/Along the road lay rows of wounded men from one of (.*?)\'s armies\./, "沿路躺着几排伤兵，他们是 $1的一支部队。");
	text = text.replace("You watch as an elderly healer walks the lines, drill and scalpel in hand, tending to those souls who are loudest.", "你看着一位上了年纪的治疗师，手里拿着钻子和手术刀，走在队列中，照料着那些最吵闹的灵魂。");
	text = text.replace("He sets himself upon a particularly shrill fellow who is clutching a green and puckered nub where one of his legs used to be.", "他走到一个尖叫的特别大声的家伙面前，那家伙抓着一个绿色皱巴巴的瘤子，那是他以前的一条腿。");
	text = text.replace("The healer holds the wounded soldier down and with no trepidation in his trephination he begins to bore a hole into the man\'s skull.", "治疗师把受伤的士兵按倒在地，毫不畏惧地在他的头骨上钻了一个洞。");
	text = text.replace("You wince at the screams.", "听到尖叫声，你退缩了。");
	text = text.replace("A moonly fluid seeps from the brainpan, chips of bone coursing along the froth, and as the sickly blue ruin pours over the man\'s face he appears to smile and be at ease, as though peace came by way of an augered and fevered dream.", "一种月光般的液体从他的头壳中渗出，骨头碎片沿着泡沫流动，他似乎微笑着，显得很自在，仿佛刚刚的痛苦只是一个梦。");
	text = text.replace(/A few of (.*?)\'s bannermen line up to see an elderly healer\./, "一些 $1的手下排队去看一个老医生。");
	text = text.replace("You watch as the old man turns his patients this way and that, pressing his thumbs into their flesh, smelling their clothes, their hair, their blood.", "你看着这位老人把他的病人这样那样地转着，用拇指戳着他们的肉，闻着他们的衣服、头发、血液。");
	text = text.replace("His summations are scribed into a scroll no one can see, and then he moves the men off to a side.", "他的总结被抄写成一卷没有人能看见的卷轴，然后他把人们移到一边。");
	text = text.replace("You ask a lieutenant what is going on. He explains.", "你问军官这是怎么回事。他解释道。");
	text = text.replace("We are seeing who is still fit to fight.", "我们正在看谁还有能力继续战斗。");
	text = text.replace("If you are not fit, you go to the left, if you are fit, you go to the right.", "如果不合适，就放在左边，如果合适，则放在右边。");
	text = text.replace("Slowly, you realize not a single man is put to the left.", "慢慢地，你意识到没有一个人被放在左边。");
	text = text.replace("Not even the one-legged or blind or wheezing. The lieutenant grins.", "即使是独腿的，瞎眼的或者呼吸困难的，军官咧嘴一笑。");
	text = text.replace("I told the healer my requirements for going to the right and he seems to be following them satisfactorily.", "我告诉了老医生去右边的要求，他似乎很满意地遵循了这些要求。");
	text = text.replace("You ask what those requirements might be.", "你问那些要求可能是什么。");
	text = text.replace("The lieutenant raises an eyebrow.", "军官挑了挑眉毛。");
	text = text.replace("Why, they must be breathing, of course!", "当然，他们一定还在呼吸！");
	text = text.replace("Don\'t tell the men that, though.", "不过，不要告诉那些人这件事。");
	text = text.replace("Illusions of relaxation is nothing but decay to an army!", "对于一支军队来说，放松的幻想是不能有的！");
	text = text.replace("A man is found along a path.", "沿着小路可以看到一个人。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s missing both his legs, the nubs of their trunks in each hand as though he had no idea how he\'d come to this state.", "他的两条腿都断了，两只手都抓着树干的尖端，好像他不知道自己是怎么落到这种地步的。");
	text = text.replace("With pitiful eyes, he glances up at you.", "他用可怜的眼睛抬头瞥着你。");
	//text = text.replace("What happened?", "发生了什么？");
	text = text.replace("You shake your head.", "你摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace(/Seeing the banner of (.*?), though, you gather that he was attacked in the midst of the war amongst the nobles\./, "但是，看到 $1 的旗帜，你可以推测他是在贵族之间的战争中受伤的。");
	text = text.replace("The wounded man coughs and a rope of red spurts from one of the stumps.", "受伤的人咳嗽了一声，血液就像一根红绳子一样从他的嘴里喷了出来。");
	text = text.replace("His face goes pale.", "他脸色变得苍白。");
	text = text.replace("Huh, I feel much better now.", "哏，我现在感觉好多了。");
	text = text.replace("I think I\'ll do that again.", "我想我会再做一次。");
	text = text.replace("He gathers his breath to cough, smiles, and falls over.", "他屏住呼吸，咳嗽着，微笑着，倒下了。");
	text = text.replace("You find a few men crawling about naked.", "你发现有几个男人裸着身体四处爬。");
	text = text.replace("They\'re dragging innards and loosely tethered limbs behind them, moaning and groaning like the refuse of a medical ward come alive.", "他们拖着内脏，四肢松散地绑在身后，呻吟着，像病房里的垃圾一样活着。");
	text = text.replace(/One glances up at you, the banner of (.*?) stuffed into his mouth\./, "有人抬头瞥了你一眼，他嘴里塞着一个 $1 的旗帜。");
	text = text.replace("Please...", "求求你…");
	text = text.replace("He collapses. Another man grabs onto your boot, but you shake him off and he, too, dies in the moment.", "他断气了。另一个男人抓住你的靴子，但你把他甩开，他也立刻死了。");
	text = text.replace("The rest stop moving one by one in turn.", "其余的也停止了移动。");
	text = text.replace("It appears as though they sought you as a savior and, upon getting the bad news, they died in disappointed union.", "看起来好像他们之前把你当作救世主，但在得到这个坏消息后，他们在失望之中死去了。");
	text = text.replace("A man\'s slathered in blood, setting squat in the middle of a path, naked save for the metal knife he\'s biting down on.", "一个男人满身是血，蹲在小路中间，赤身裸体，除了他正在咬的那把金属刀。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s got gore in his hands, and mad lust in his eyes. Bodies lay nearby.", "他的手上有血迹，眼睛里带着疯狂。尸体躺在附近。");
	text = text.replace("Destroyed, demolished in shells of armor that they once depended upon for protection.", "他们曾经依靠坚硬的盔甲来保护自己，被摧毁了。");
	text = text.replace("The insane man glances at them, then at you.", "那个疯子瞥了他们一眼，然后又看了你一眼。");
	text = text.replace("Oh, it was good fight.", "噢，打得不错。");
	text = text.replace("Oh, it was a good fight.", "噢，那是一场精彩的比赛。");
	text = text.replace("Oh, my sirs, it was a good fight!", "噢，我的先生们，这是一场精彩的比赛！");
	text = text.replace("He jumps to his feet and you draw your sword, but the man turns and sprints away.", "他跳起来，你拔出剑，但那人转身冲了过去。");
	text = text.replace("You dare not catch him or his curse.", "你不敢抓住他。");
	text = text.replace("You come to a tree along the path.", "你沿着小路来到一棵树前。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s a man talking to a cat, but as you get closer you realize he\'s tied a rope around the fearful feline\'s neck.", "有一个人在和一只猫说话，但当你靠近他时，你发现他在可怕的猫科动物的脖子上绑了一根绳子。");
	text = text.replace("Purr, yes, keep purring... all will be well.", "咕噜，是的，继续咕噜…一切都会好起来的。");
	text = text.replace("I\'m sorry you saw the things I did.", "我很抱歉你看到了我所做的事。");
	text = text.replace("I love your purring...", "我喜欢你的咕噜声…");
	text = text.replace("You raise your voice.", "你提高了你的音量。");
	text = text.replace("Sir?", "先生？");
	text = text.replace(/The second the man turns around you see that he is a bannerman of (.*?)\. Seeing its chance, the cat slips its noose and scatters\./, "当这个人转过身来的时候，你就会发现他是 $1 的手下。猫看到了机会，挣脱了套索，跑了。");
	text = text.replace("The man cries out and gives chase.", "那人大叫起来，追了上去。");
	text = text.replace("Hopefully, that is the last you see of them both.", "希望这是你最后一次见到他们。");
	text = text.replace("You come to a man sitting in the road.", "你走到一个坐在路上的男人面前。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s got a dog nestled in his lap, though the mutt\'s head is hanging limp and bloodied.", "他的大腿上坐着一只狗，尽管那只杂种狗的头软绵绵地垂着，浑身是血。");
	text = text.replace("The man looks up at you.", "男人抬头看着你。");
	text = text.replace("Have you seen my dog?", "你看见我的狗了吗？");
	text = text.replace("It\'s black, matted, has a white tail.", "它是条黑狗，有一条白色的尾巴。");
	text = text.replace("Have you seen my dog?", "你看见我的狗了吗？");
	text = text.replace("The pup he\'s describing is currently in his lap, but you do not say as much.", "他所描述的小狗现在在他的腿上，但是你不能说太多。");
	text = text.replace(/Instead, you shake your head and tell the man a simple \'no\.\' He shakes his head in return\./, "相反，你摇摇头，告诉他一个简单的“没。”他摇摇头作为回应。");
	text = text.replace(/The bannermen of (.*?) came by\./, "$1 的手下来过。");
	text = text.replace("Destroyed everything. And they took my dog.", "毁了一切。他们还带走了我的狗。");
	text = text.replace("Say, have you seen my dog?", "喂，你看见我的狗了吗？");
	text = text.replace("You find a burning cottage beside the path.", "你在小路旁边发现了一座燃烧着的小屋。");
	text = text.replace("A few dead bodies are scattered about the grass, some of them quite small.", "草地上散落着几具尸体，有些很小。");
	text = text.replace(/Looking around, you do not find the perpetrators, though the banner of (.*?) is flying from the branches of a nearby tree\./, "环顾四周，你没有发现肇事者，尽管 $1 的旗帜从附近一棵树的树枝上飘扬而下。");
	text = text.replace("The war is sparing no one.", "这场战争无人幸免。");
	text = text.replace("You come to find a shepherd standing before a massacre.", "你发现一个牧羊人站在大屠杀前。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s crouched, hands balanced over his knees, a cane balanced over his arms, like some fleshen clock with shadows for time.", "他蜷缩着，双手平放在膝盖上，一根拐杖架在手臂上，就像一只带着阴影的血肉钟。");
	text = text.replace("Seeing you, he speaks up and he\'s rather articulate, as though he\'s getting something long on his mind.", "看到你，他说话很大声，而且口齿伶俐，好像他有什么心事。");
	text = text.replace("Soldiers came by. I said don\'t kill my sheep.", "士兵们经过。我说不要杀我的羊。");
	text = text.replace("They said what sheep.", "他们说什么羊。");
	text = text.replace("I said nothing. They pushed me down.", "我什么也没说。他们把我推倒在地。");
	text = text.replace("Went over the hill.", "翻山越岭。");
	text = text.replace("Found my sheep. Slaughtered my sheep. Ate my sheep.", "找到我的羊了。宰了我的羊。吃了我的羊。");
	text = text.replace("I should have kept my mouth shut.", "我不应该多嘴的。");
	text = text.replace("His thumbs twist the ends of his walking staff, but he says nothing more.", "他的拇指扭动着拐杖的两端，但他什么也没说。");
	text = text.replace(/You find a man impaled to a tree by the banner pole of his house, (.*?)\. His eyes stare at the ground before him, at a litter of footprints that seemed to have been standing around long enough to leave deep grooves in the mud\./, "你发现一个人被 $1 的旗杆钉在树上。他的眼睛盯着眼前的地面，看着一串脚印，这些脚印似乎已经站了足够长的时间，在泥泞中留下了深深的凹槽。");
	text = text.replace("And then he departed and so did they.", "然后他离开了，他们也离开了。");

//civilwar_hungry_hamlet_event.nut
	text = text.replace("While traveling the roads, you come across a small hamlet with, apparently, it\'s entire populace standing outside.", "当你在路上走的时候，你遇到了一个小村庄，很明显，几乎所有人都站村外。");
	text = text.replace("Their leader steps forward, hands out, pleading, though with hardly the strength to keep his hands clasped together.", "他们的村长向前走了几步，伸出双手，恳求着，尽管他虚弱的几乎没有力气把双手合在一起。");
	text = text.replace("Please, would you help us?", "拜托，你能帮帮我们吗？");
	text = text.replace("We have been without food for almost a week now.", "我们已经将近一个星期没有食物吃了。");
	text = text.replace("We\'re down to eating dirt!", "我们只能吃土了！");
	text = text.replace("You have to understand, we have nothing!", "我们已经什么都没有！");
	text = text.replace("The war has ravaged us all.", "战争蹂躏了我们所有人。");
	text = text.replace("A small hamlet emerges beside your travels, little more than a cursory wink were it not for the large band of villagers standing outside seemingly awaiting you.", "在你的旅途的路旁出现了一个小村庄，如果不是因为似乎外面站着一大群村民在等你的村民，这只不过是旅途路上的匆匆一瞥。");
	text = text.replace("Their leader steps forward.", "他们的村长走上前来。");
	text = text.replace("Mercenary, I know you are probably not the one to ask for this, but do you have any food to spare?", "雇佣兵，我知道你不是那个能保护我们的人，但是你有多余的食物吗？");
	text = text.replace("The war has ravaged our crops and the soldiers that roam the land have taken what else there is to take!", "战争蹂躏了我们的庄稼，在这片土地上游荡的士兵们拿走了我们的一切！");
	text = text.replace("Please, help us!", "求求你，救救我们！");
	text = text.replace("The roads lead you to a small hamlet.", "这条路通向一个小村庄。");
	text = text.replace("Villagers are squatting outside their hamlets, heads between their knees, looking thin and grey.", "村民们蹲在他们的村子外面，头埋在膝盖之间，看上去又瘦又灰。");
	text = text.replace("Children are with them, frail and wiry, yet with the glow of youth still in their eyes.", "孩子们和他们在一起，身体虚弱，精力充沛，但他们眼中仍闪烁着青春的光芒。");
	text = text.replace("The town\'s leader comes to you personally.", "村长亲自来找你。");
	text = text.replace("Sir... sellsword? Yes, sellsword.", "先生…是佣兵？是的，佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("Please, we\'ve been without food for a week now.", "求求你，我们已经一个星期没吃东西了。");
	text = text.replace("We\'ve been surviving on our pets, insects... even the dirt.", "我们靠我们的宠物，昆虫生存…甚至是泥土。");
	text = text.replace("Do you have anything to help us?", "你能帮帮我们吗？");
	text = text.replace("As your men take a rest beside the road, villagers from a nearby hamlet come to you.", "当你的人在路边休息的时候，附近一个村庄的村民来找你们。");
	text = text.replace("They bumble forward, wiry legs shambling them from side to side.", "他们蹒跚向前，瘦削的腿从一边到另一边摇晃着。");
	text = text.replace("The head of the group raises and lowers a hand as though to bless your presence.", "一群人的头抬起或者低下一只手，好像在祝福你的存在。");
	text = text.replace("Oh sellsword, mercenary, please, do you have anything to eat?", "噢，佣兵，请问，你有什么吃的吗？");
	text = text.replace("We\'ve yet to have a bite in two days!", "我们已经两天没有吃东西了！");
	text = text.replace("And what we have eaten are things not to be said aloud!", "我们这几天所吃的，一些根本不能说的东西！");
	text = text.replace("The war between nobles has ruined this place, but maybe you can help?", "贵族之间的战争毁了这个地方，你能帮帮我们吗？");
	text = text.replace(/Against typical mercenary judgment, you elect to give the poor villagers some food\. (.*?) is told to disperse what he can, although obviously not too much\./, "你不是唯利是图的雇佣兵，你选择给穷人一些食物。$1 被告知要尽可能的分给每个穷人，虽然这样每个人就分不到太多。");
	text = text.replace("The people are forever grateful, swarming the sellsword as though he was about whisper an immense and unforgettable truth.", "村民们感激不尽，他们涌向佣兵，仿佛他要低声说出一个惊天大秘密似的。");
	text = text.replace("The leader of the small town says he will spread word of your goodwill.", "这儿的村长说他会传播你的善意。");
	text = text.replace("You\'re actually not sure if news of altruism is good for a mercenary band...", "你实际上并不确定利他主义的新闻是否对雇佣兵团有好处…");
	text = text.replace(/Shocking the villagers, you order (.*?) to hand out some food\./, "你命令 $1 给村民分发食物，这个命令震惊了村民。");
	text = text.replace("Not too much, just enough that these people can eat.", "你没给太多，给的刚好够这些人吃。");
	text = text.replace("And obviously, don\'t give away anything too good!", "显然，不要放弃任何太好的东西！");
	text = text.replace("The leader of the town comes to you, shaking hands clapping your shoulders.", "这儿的村长向你走来，握着你的手拍着你的肩膀。");
	text = text.replace("You\'ve no idea what this means to us!", "你根本不知道这对我们意味着什么！");
	text = text.replace("All shall hear of the good in the...", "所有人都会知道的…");
	text = text.replace("He glances at you and then your banner. You nod.", "他瞥着你，然后看着你的旗帜。你点头。");
	//text = text.replace(/The (.*?)\./, "这是 $1。");
	text = text.replace("The man laughs.", "这个人笑了。");
	text = text.replace(/Of course! Everyone shall hear of the (.*?)!/, "每个人都该知道 $1 ！");
	text = text.replace(/Goodness gets the better of you: you order (.*?) to start handing out food\./, "善良占了上风: 你命令 $1 开始分发食物。");
	text = text.replace("He complies, but as soon as he starts handing it out, the crowd goes nearly rabid, snatching it from one another.", "他答应了，但是当他开始分发的时候，人群几乎疯狂地互相抢夺。");
	text = text.replace("Fiery tempers are quickly fed by the air of empty bellies.", "暴躁的脾气很快被空腹的空气所助长。");
	text = text.replace("The mercenary tries to maintain order, but anything he says only spurs the hungry masses into thinking it\'s all his fault.", "雇佣兵试图维持秩序，但他所说的一切只会促使饥饿的群众认为这都是他的错。");
	text = text.replace("The violence spills over, ironically spilling all the food into the mud.", "暴力蔓延开来，具有讽刺意味的是，所有的食物都洒进了泥里。");
	text = text.replace("Your brothers have to draw swords and by the end of it some peasants lay dead while the survivors look at the corpses with cannibalistic eyes.", "你的兄弟们必须拔出剑，最后一些农民死了，而幸存者用食人的眼睛看着尸体。");
	text = text.replace(/You quickly order the (.*?) to move on before this gets any worse\./, "在情况变得更糟之前，你迅速命令 $1 继续前进。");
	text = text.replace(/For some reason, perhaps to sleep better at night, you order (.*?) to hand out parcels of food\./, "出于某种原因，也许为了晚上睡得更好，你命令 $1 去分发食物。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s just getting started on the process when a villager quickly snatches a sack of foods.", "但他才刚刚开始分发，一个村民就迅速抓起一袋食物。");
	text = text.replace("Another peasant stoves that man\'s head in and takes the sack for himself.", "在旁边的另一个农民把那个村民的头放进炉子里，自己拿袋子。");
	text = text.replace("This quickly erupts into a total free-for-all and your mercenaries have to draw weapons to protect the rest of the stores.", "这很快就演变成一场混战，你的雇佣兵们必须拿出武器来保护其他的粮食。");
	text = text.replace("By the end of the scuffle a few laymen lay dead and your brothers are a little marked up.", "混战结束时，几个村民死了，你的手下们也受了点伤。");
	text = text.replace("Seeing no reason to hang around, you order the company to get back on the road.", "看到没有理由留下来，你命令大伙重新上路。");
	text = text.replace("The leader who asked for your help is spotted in the distance, staring out at the horizon as a bitter wind curls his thin pantaloons about his shins.", "在远处，你发现了乞求你们帮助的村长，他凝视着远方的地平线，一股刺骨的寒风把他的破裤子卷在小腿上。");
	text = text.replace("Well. This world is a terrible place and if you can do a little to relieve it of its horrid nature, why not?", "好吧。生活是残酷的，为什么不做点让世界更美好的事情呢？");
	text = text.replace(/You order (.*?) to start doling out food, but not too much, and nothing that your tastes will miss\./, "你命令 $1 去分发食物，不要发太多，但每个人都要有。");
	text = text.replace(/But as he goes about the business, a few soldiers waving the (.*?) banner show up\./, "但就在他刚刚分完食物之后，些许 $1 的手下出现了。");
	text = text.replace("They sift through the hungry crowd, taking food and drawing swords whenever someone resists.", "他们从饥饿的人群中筛选，拿走食物，每当有人反抗时就拔剑。");
	text = text.replace("Their supposed leader speaks out.", "他们所谓的头子狂妄的说。");
	text = text.replace(/This food is needed by the arm of (.*?)\. Do not resist its seizure\./, "这些食物是 $1 所需要的。不准拒绝我们。");
	text = text.replace("You explain to the man that it is in fact your food and you just handed it out.", "你向那个人解释说，这实际上是你的食物，而你只是把它们分发出去。");
	text = text.replace("If it\'s your food, why is it in their hands?", "如果是你的食物，为什么在他们手里？");
	text = text.replace("Go along, men, take all that you can!", "去吧，伙计们，尽你们所能！");
	text = text.replace("And don\'t try anything, sellsword, or there will be violence.", "别轻举妄动，佣兵，否则我们就不客气了。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) glances at you as if to say, what should we do\?/, "$1 瞥了你一眼，就好像在说，我们该怎么办？");
	text = text.replace("The lieutenant turns back to his men, directing them in their thievery.", "军官转向他的士兵，指挥他们抢夺。");
	text = text.replace("You draw your sword and hobble over, the pain in your side still lingering, but it doesn\'t take much effort to sneak up on a man.", "你拔出剑，一瘸一拐地走过去，身体一侧的疼痛仍然挥之不去，但是悄悄接近一个男人并不费劲。");
	text = text.replace("With a quick blade about his neck, you call out to the rest of his men.", "你用匕首抵着他脖子，你向他手下的其他人喊道。");
	text = text.replace("Is it violence you really want?", "你真的想要暴力吗？");
	text = text.replace("Holding his hands up, the lieutenant squeaks out some words.", "军官举起手，尖声说出了一些话。");
	text = text.replace("Wait, wait, hold on.", "等等，等等，都停下。");
	text = text.replace("I think we, uh, made a mistake.", "我想我们，呃，犯了个错误。");
	text = text.replace("This is the wrong village, fellas.", "伙计们，我们走错村庄了。");
	text = text.replace("You nick him with the sword before releasing him.", "在释放他之前，你先用匕首刺伤了他。");
	text = text.replace("The peasants rejoice as the food goes back to them.", "当食物回到农民手中时，他们高兴极了。");
	text = text.replace("No doubt, the nobility will hear of your \'good\' deeds done here, but so will the common man.", "毫无疑问，贵族们会听说你在这里所做的“好事”，但是普通人也会听说。");
	text = text.replace("You grab the lieutenant by the shoulder and pull him close.", "你抓住军官的肩膀把他拉近。");
	text = text.replace("He grabs you arm and throws you off, going to draw his sword in the same motion.", "他抓住你的胳膊，把你扔了出去，然后用同样的动作拔出他的剑。");
	text = text.replace("You jump to his side, blocking the draw, and in turn pull a quick dagger and plunge it into his neck.", "你跳到他身边，挡住了他拔剑，然后迅速拔出匕首，刺入他的脖子。");
	text = text.replace("His soldiers come scrambling through the crowd, but your mercenaries cut them down and the peasants finish them off with sheer brutality only hunger can create.", "他的士兵从人群中匆匆而来，但是你的雇佣兵把他们砍倒了，农民们用只有饥饿才能创造出来的残忍把他们杀死。");
	text = text.replace("The lieutenant slowly slides down from your grip.", "军官慢慢地从你的手里滑了下来。");
	text = text.replace("You stare down at his blackening eyes.", "你低头看着他那双发黑的眼睛。");
	text = text.replace("Yes, there will be violence.", "对，我们确实不客气了。");
	text = text.replace("The peasants cheer the results, though you recommend they bury the bodies or, even better, not be here anymore.", "农民们对结果欢呼雀跃，尽管你建议他们埋葬尸体，或者，更好的是，不再留在这里。");
	text = text.replace("No doubt an army will wonder where these men went.", "毫无疑问，一支军队会想知道这些来征粮的人去了哪里。");
	text = text.replace("You inform your men to stand down.", "你通知你的人撤退。");
	text = text.replace("The commonfolk wail as their food is taken from them again.", "老百姓哀号着，因为他们的食物又被夺走了。");
	text = text.replace("It is a horrid cry and many damn you, stating they\'d rather you have never shown up at all than be tortured in this manner.", "这是一个可怕的哭声，许多人诅咒你，说他们宁愿你从来没有出现过，也不愿意被这样折磨。");
	text = text.replace("Giving food is one thing, quarreling with soldiers is another.", "给予食物是一回事，与士兵战斗是另一回事。");
	text = text.replace("You inform the soldiers that there will be no fight and that they can carry on.", "你告诉士兵们不会有战斗，他们可以继续前进。");
	text = text.replace("The laymen cry out, begging you to put a stop to it.", "村民们叫喊着，乞求你阻止这一切。");
	text = text.replace("Some are too weak to say anything, this sudden turn of events having been a bigger blow than any long weeks of hunger.", "有些人虚弱得什么也说不出来，这种突如其来的事态变化比长达数周的饥饿对他们的打击更大。");

//civilwar_intro_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/You enter (.*?) and find a group of laymen standing around a wooden platform\./, "你进入 $1，发现一群村民站在一个木制平台周围。");
	text = text.replace("Thinking there\'s a hanging to be seen, you quickly push through the crowd.", "你以为有什么悬着的东西等着看，便迅速地从人群中挤了过去。");
	text = text.replace("What you find instead is a queerly dressed man barking out news to the townsfolk.", "结果恰恰相反，你发现一个穿着奇怪的男人在向镇民;大声宣布新闻。");
	text = text.replace(/Harken harken harken, a determination has been made between the noble houses (.*?) and (.*?)! They have come to a conclusion all sides can agree upon: they hate one another!/, "瞧一瞧啊，看一看啊，贵族家族 $1 与 $2 之间互相仇恨！他们要全面开战了！");
	text = text.replace("Nervous whispers wrinkle the crowd.", "人群之中传来窃窃私语的声音。");
	text = text.replace("As the volume builds, the whispers crescendo into hushes. The minstrel continues.", "随着音量越来越大，低语声逐渐消失。吟游诗人继续道。");
	text = text.replace("That is right, my fair fair-folk!", "是的，村民们！");
	text = text.replace("War is upon us!", "战争就要来了！");
	text = text.replace("Ah yes, that fickle beast which lies dormant in all men.", "啊，是的，那个潜伏在所有人心中的变幻无常的野兽。");
	text = text.replace("A sad affair, a righteous affair, an honorable one!", "一件可悲的事，一件正义的事，一件光荣的事！");
	text = text.replace("An old man standing in front of you grumbles and spits.", "站在你面前的一位老人嘟哝着吐口水。");
	text = text.replace("He leaves, shaking his head and murmuring to himself.", "他走了，摇摇头，自言自语。");
	text = text.replace("The minstrel presses on, his excitement not matching the terrified faces before him.", "吟游诗人继续前进，他的兴奋与他面前惊恐的面孔极不相称。");
	text = text.replace("Let us not dawdle on ceremony.", "我们不要在仪式上磨磨蹭蹭的。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ve been instructed to speak thusly: men, take up arms where you can, plough the fields while you can\'t.", "男人们，拿起你们能拿的武器，在不拿武器的时候多耕地！");
	text = text.replace("Women, raise yer sons right, lest they may raise a sword all wrong!", "女人们，把你们的儿子养好，免得他们连剑都拿不起来！");
	text = text.replace("Finally, the minstrel takes a great big breath.", "最后，吟游诗人深吸了一口气。");
	text = text.replace("And those among you who wish to earn a good crown or two, the noble houses are looking for the fine services of any man who can swing a sword.", "而你们当中那些希望获得一两个克朗的人，贵族家族正在寻找任何能挥剑的人的优质服务。");
	text = text.replace("Those among you of lesser honor, you bridle-loosers, bride-stealers, leech-sellers, smellsmocks, ne\'er do wells, vice obsessed and run amuck, brigands, bandits, and thieving graduates, you sickly and poison moistened, the cursed and rabid, the cured and vapid, sellswords and poets selling words, this, my fine genteel men, is YOUR time.", "你们这些不太体面的人，你们这些放荡的，偷新娘的，卖水蛭的，臭气熏天的，不干好事的，恶习成性的，胡作非为的人，还有强盗，土匪，偷东西的，病态的，染毒的，被诅咒的，狂暴的，被治愈的，愚蠢的，佣兵，吟游诗人等等，先生们，现在是你们表现的时间了。");
	text = text.replace("Go out there, fight for the nobles, and earn yourself a new life!", "为贵族而战，为自己赢得新生活！");
	text = text.replace("A shame that a war shan\'t last forever, so best do it quick!", "战争不会永远持续下去，出人头地要乘早！");
	text = text.replace(/It looks as though the (.*?)\'s future just got brighter - on account of the loads of gold you\'re about to be earning\./, "看起来好像 $1的未来要变得更加光明了，因为你将会赚到大量的金子。");

//civilwar_outro_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/You\'re in your tent when (.*?) makes an entrance\. He speaks bluntly\./, "当你待在帐篷里时，$1 突然进来了。他直言不讳。");
	text = text.replace("Nobles be talking. Big fancy tent setup yonder and they\'re in there.", "贵族们在谈话。那边有一个又大又漂亮的帐篷，他们就在里面。");
	text = text.replace("Putting your quill pen down, you respond.", "你放下羽毛笔，答道。");
	text = text.replace("Just talking?", "只是聊天？");
	text = text.replace("The mercenary shrugs.", "雇佣兵耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("It\'s quiet. So they\'re either talking, or killing one another real quiet like.", "这里很安静。所以他们要么是在交谈，要么就是悄无声息地互相残杀。");
	text = text.replace("You get up and step outside.", "你站起来，走出去。");
	text = text.replace("A brisk air hits you, and on it is the scent of spices and flavors.", "清新的空气扑面而来，里面弥漫着香料的味道。");
	text = text.replace("Looking upwind, you spot the tent.", "迎风望去，你发现了帐篷。");
	text = text.replace("Cooks and chefs are hurrying about with orders of food and other makings.", "厨师们正忙着订购食物和其他材料。");
	text = text.replace("Servants carry platters of meats, vegetables, and fruits.", "仆人端着一碟碟肉、蔬菜和水果。");
	text = text.replace("An opulent tent, black with gold embroidering, houses the nobles.", "一个华丽的黑色帐篷，上面绣着金丝，里面住着贵族。");
	text = text.replace("Bannermen stand outside. They take no part in the festivities.", "贵族的士兵们站在外面。他们不参加庆祝活动。");
	text = text.replace("They\'re mostly playing cards while occasionally glancing at one another.", "他们大部分时间都在打牌，偶尔也会互相看一眼。");
	text = text.replace("Some are bandaged with blood splotched linens.", "有些人用血迹斑斑的亚麻布包扎。");
	text = text.replace("One man stands on crutches with a haggard, half-cocked knee.", "一个人拄着拐杖，膝盖歪歪斜斜，形容枯槁。");
	text = text.replace(/You ask (.*?) what the news is\./, "你问 $1 这是怎么回事。");
	text = text.replace("He nods toward the scene.", "他朝现场点了点头。");
	text = text.replace("Well, they rolled up about an hour ago while you were checking the maps.", "好吧，大约在一个小时前，你在看地图的时候，它们就在这驻扎了。");
	text = text.replace("We didn\'t want to bother ya, but, well, they seemed intent on staying so, you know.", "我们不想打扰你，但是，嗯，他们似乎打算留下来，你知道。");
	text = text.replace("You get a good look at the noble tent.", "你可以好好看看这个高贵的帐篷。");
	text = text.replace(/Through its opening, you can see the faint glisten of crowned heads passing back and forth\. (.*?) spits and asks\./, "透过它的开口，你可以看到头戴王冠的人隐隐约约地来回走动，头上的王冠闪闪发光。$1 吐了口唾沫，问道。");
	text = text.replace("Well, who do you think won the war?", "好吧，你觉得这场战争谁赢了？");
	text = text.replace("You hock a loogie, spit, and shake your head.", "你吞了口痰，吐了口唾沫，摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("Who gives a shite?", "谁他妈在乎呢？");
	text = text.replace("All that matters to you is that peace means fewer contracts.", "对你来说最重要的是，和平就意味着更少的合同。");
	text = text.replace("Perhaps now would be a good time to put up the sword and enjoy your crowns?", "也许现在是提起剑戴上王冠的好时机？");
	text = text.replace("Or maybe say to hell with all that sentimental crap and just keep pressing forward, leading the company to even greater things?", "或者说，让所有这些感情用事见鬼去吧，继续前进，带领你的队伍走向更伟大的未来？");
	text = text.replace("You\'ve won! Battle Brothers is designed for replayability and for campaigns to be played until you\'ve beaten one or two late game crises.", "你已经胜利了！战场兄弟是为可重玩性和战役而设计的，直到你在游戏后期打败了一两次危机。");
	text = text.replace("Starting a new campaign will allow you to try out different things in a different world.", "开始一个新的战役会让你在不同的世界尝试不同的东西。");
	text = text.replace("That said, you can choose to continue your campaign for as long as you want.", "也就是说，你可以选择继续你的战役，只要你想。");
	text = text.replace("Just be aware that campaigns are not intended to last forever and you\'re likely to run out of challenges eventually.", "只是要意识到，战役并不是要永远持续下去的，你可能最终会尝尽所有的挑战。");

//civilwar_refugees_event.nut
	text = text.replace("A true war has plenty of living amongst the casualties and this one is no different: going along a path, you find a large group of refugees huddling together.", "通常情况下，一场真正的战争会有大量人员伤亡，这场战争也不例外：沿着一条小路，你看到一大群难民挤在一起。");
	text = text.replace("They were washing themselves in a creek when you discovered them, a party half-naked and half-washed and all-terrified.", "你发现他们时，他们正在小溪里洗澡，一个帮人半裸半洗，你吓到他们了。");
	text = text.replace("Mostly women and children, a few elders, and a few men who seem ready to lay down their lives for the rest, no matter how fruitless an effort their defense would be.", "难民中大多数是妇女和儿童，还有一些老人，以及一些准备用生命守护周围人的男人，虽然他们非常瘦弱。");
	text = text.replace("One such man steps forward.", "一个这样的人站出来。");
	text = text.replace("What is it that you want?", "你想要什么？");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) approaches you\./, "$1 靠近了你。");
	text = text.replace("Sir, we could take everything they got, but I\'m sure they won\'t give it up willingly.", "先生，我们可以拿走他们所有的东西，但我相信他们不会自愿放弃的。");
	//text = text.replace(/(.*?) shakes his head\./, "$1 摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("I\'d say it ain\'t worth it.", "我得说他们不值得我们这样做。");
	text = text.replace("These people been through enough as it is and they\'ve little left to give the world.", "这些人已经经历了太多东西了，他们现在已经一无所有了。");
	text = text.replace("You come across a band of refugees.", "你遇到一群难民。");
	text = text.replace("Women, children, elders, and a scattering of wide-eyed men.", "女人，孩子，老人，还有一些瘦小的男人。");
	text = text.replace("They\'ve little of value, but they still have things worth taking were you to put in the effort.", "他们几乎一无所有，但如果你花点力气，他们仍然有值得的东西。");
	text = text.replace("Refugees. A band of them stringed along the path in a long and filed row.", "难民。他们中的一群人沿着小路排成一长排。");
	text = text.replace(/At the sight of you, the head of the suffering centipede rears to a stop and all the bodies slowly shuffle together into a fearful blob\. (.*?) suggests killing them and taking what they got, although what they got doesn\'t appear to be much at all by your measurement\./, "一看到你，这个蜈蚣一样的队伍就停了下来，所有的身体慢慢地拖着步子，变成了一团可怕的东西。$1 建议杀了这些难民，拿走他们的所有东西，尽管你认为这些难民已经一无所有了。");
	text = text.replace("You order your men to take what they can.", "你命令你的人拿走他们能拿走的东西。");
	text = text.replace("The refugees reel back in horror and some protest as your brothers file into their ranks.", "当你的兄弟们列队进入难民的队伍时，难民们带着恐惧开始抗议。");
	text = text.replace(/Suddenly, one of the refugees takes a large stone and bashes (.*?) over the head with it\./, "突然，其中一个难民拿起一块大石头，砸向了 $1 的头。");
	text = text.replace("Women and children scream and a few other men grab onto the mercenaries, fighting over weapons still sheathed.", "妇女和儿童尖叫着，其他几个男人抓住雇佣兵，争抢着他身上的武器。");
	text = text.replace("But the wandering souls haven\'t eaten in days and their weakened bodies are no match for your men.", "但是这些瘦弱的人们已经好几天没有吃东西了，他们虚弱的身体根本无法与你的人匹敌。");
	text = text.replace(/The (.*?) takes what it wants\./, "$1 拿走了他们想要的一切。");
	text = text.replace("You order your men to take what they can.", "你命令你的人拿走他们能拿走的东西。");
	text = text.replace("The refugees reel back in horror.", "难民们吓得东倒西歪。");
	text = text.replace("Women cry out, children, more confused than understanding, do the same.", "妇女们和孩子们哭喊着。");
	text = text.replace("Some tearful men beg that you simply leave.", "一些泪流满面的人乞求你离开。");
	text = text.replace(/Unfortunately for this band of useless tramps, the (.*?) takes what it wants\./, "不幸的是，对于这帮无家可归的流浪汉来说，$1 可以随心所欲。");
	text = text.replace("Your men freely sift through the crowds, eventually returning with their hauls.", "你的手下在人群中自由地筛选，最终带着他们的战利品返回了。");
	text = text.replace(/You tell (.*?) to give the refugees some food\./, "你叫 $1 给难民们一些食物。");
	text = text.replace("The disconcerted group stares at you incredulously as they\'re handed some bread and a carboy of water.", "当他们拿到一些面包和水的时候，不知所措的人们不可思议地盯着你。");
	text = text.replace("An elderly fellow walks up and shakenly gets to his knees to kiss your feet.", "一个老人走上前来，颤颤巍巍地跪下来亲吻你的脚。");
	text = text.replace("You lift the man back up and tell him there is no need for such theatrics.", "你把他扶起来，告诉他没必要这么夸张。");
	text = text.replace("A few of the mercenaries snicker and call you the \'The Dough of Doughs, the Stale Bread King.\'", "你手下的一些雇佣兵窃笑着称你为“面包大王。”");
	text = text.replace("These people would be easily robbed, but you get the feeling such news wouldn\'t sit kindly when word of it spread about the region.", "这些人很容易被抢劫，但是当这些消息在这个地区传开的时候，你觉得这样的消息不会是好消息。");
	text = text.replace(/Instead, you order (.*?) to start handing out food and water\./, "相反，你命令 $1 去给这些难民分发食物和水。");
	text = text.replace("The refugees are annoyingly happy, glomming onto you as though you were a god throwing mana out of your hands.", "难民们非常高兴，他们把你当成神，把你当成一个从手中扔魔法石的神。");
	text = text.replace("You\'ve just some old food to get rid of.", "而你只是扔掉了一些快要变质的食物。");
	text = text.replace("Then again, some say that when the old gods were more human, the men were more divine.", "不过，也有人说，当古老的神明更仁慈的时候，人们会更神圣。");
	text = text.replace(/You decide to weigh on a man who has personal experience as a refugee: (.*?)\./, "你决定对一个有难民经历的人施加压力：$1。");
	text = text.replace("The mercenary heads into the sobbing and praying mass of weary travelers.", "这位雇佣兵走进了一大群哭泣着、祈祷着的难民们中。");
	text = text.replace("He talks with them for a time and shares some food, his friendly gesticulations and tales of his own past gradually bringing the crowd to his side.", "他和他们聊了一会儿，分享了一些食物，友好的手势和他自己过去的故事，渐渐的，人群聚拢到他的身边。");
	text = text.replace("You watch as an old man hands him something wrapped in sheepskin with leather thongs swooping beneath.", "你看到一个老人递给他一些用皮带和羊皮包着的东西。");
	text = text.replace("The sellsword bows, shakes the man\'s hand, and returns.", "佣兵鞠了个躬，握了握他的手，然后回来了。");
	text = text.replace(/He throws the sheepskin back to unveil a sword that glints in the light about as sharply as you can imagine it cuts. (.*?) smiles\./, "他把羊皮和皮带解开，露出一把剑，剑在阳光下闪闪发光，你能想象它有多锋利这把剑就有多锋利。$1 笑了");
	text = text.replace("Like me mum always said, a bit of friendliness never hurt nobody, but this sword sure will!", "就像我妈妈常说的，一点友善永远不会伤害任何人，但这把剑一定会的！");

//civilwar_savagery_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/While marching down a path, you come across a lieutenant of (.*?) leading a band of men in a slaughter\./, "当你沿着一条路行进时，你遇到一个 $1 的军官率领一群人在屠杀。");
	text = text.replace("They\'ve gathered the inhabitants of a small hamlet and are preparing to put them all to the sword.", "他们聚集了一个小村庄的村民，准备将他们全部杀掉。");
	text = text.replace("One of the laymen calls out to you, begging for you to intervene.", "其中一个村民向你呼喊，乞求你阻止他们。");
	text = text.replace("The lieutenant glances at you.", "军官瞥了你一眼。");
	text = text.replace("He doesn\'t have enough men to stop you, and you him, but there\'s enough on both sides to ensure everyone loses.", "他没有足够的人手来阻止你，你也没有足够的人手来阻止他，但是双方都有足够的人手来确保对方的行动会失败。");
	text = text.replace("Don\'t bother, mercenary.", "少管闲事，雇佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s no profit here for you.", "这对你没有任何好处。");
	text = text.replace("Just keep on walking.", "继续走你的。");
	text = text.replace(/The march of the (.*?) is suddenly interrupted when you come across a band of men carrying the banner of (.*?)\. Unfortunately, carrying a banner isn\'t the only thing they are doing - they\'ve lined up peasants of a nearby hamlet and look prepared to slaughter them all\./, "当你遇到一群手持 $2 旗帜的人时，$1 的行军突然中断了。不幸的是，他们做的不仅仅是举着旗帜－他们把附近村庄的农民排成一排，准备把他们全部杀光。");
	text = text.replace("The lieutenant of the troop stares you down.", "贵族手下的军官盯着你看。");
	text = text.replace("Let\'s not get messy, mercenary.", "我劝你少管闲事，雇佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("I suggest you keep on walking.", "我建议继续走你的。");
	text = text.replace("You come to a hovel.", "你来到一间小屋。");
	text = text.replace(/A few bannermen of (.*?) are standing guard outside its door\./, "几个 $1 的手下在门外站岗。");
	text = text.replace("Inside, you hear the screams of a woman and man.", "你可以听到里面传出一个男人和一个女人的尖叫声。");
	text = text.replace("The lieutenant steps out and sees you.", "军官走出来，看到了你。");
	text = text.replace("He fixes himself, even combing his hair back, and tells you to git.", "他整理了一下自己的仪容仪表，甚至把头发梳到了后面，然后叫你走开。");
	text = text.replace("Don\'t start nothing, sellsword.", "少管闲事，佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("Just keep on keeping on.", "继续走你的。");
	text = text.replace("You come to sort of holy temple, sacred to this old god or that.", "你来到一座古老的神明圣殿。");
	text = text.replace(/A few bannermen of (.*?) are boarding up the door while their lieutenant waves around a torch\./, "几个 $1 的手下正在用木板封门，而他们的军官则在火把周围挥手致意。");
	text = text.replace("People are screaming for mercy inside the building.", "人们在庙宇里尖叫着求饶。");
	text = text.replace("You raise an eyebrow and the lieutenant spots it.", "你挑挑眉毛，军官就发现了。");
	text = text.replace("Hey, sellsword. Yeah, you.", "嘿，佣兵。是你");
	text = text.replace("Get moving. This ain\'t your show.", "走你的。少管闲事。");
	text = text.replace(/While stepping down a path, you come across a lieutenant of (.*?)\. He\'s got a couple of women standing on stools beneath a tree\./, "当你走下一条路的时候，你遇到了一个 $1 的军官。他让几个女人站在树下的凳子上。");
	text = text.replace("They\'ve got ropes around their necks and tears down from their eyes.", "她们的脖子上挂着绳子，眼里流着泪水。");
	text = text.replace("The lieutenant glares at you.", "军官瞪着你。");
	text = text.replace("Don\'t get any heroic ideas, sellsword.", "不要有任何英雄的想法，佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("This ain\'t your business.", "这不关你的事。");
	text = text.replace("While marching, you suddenly hear the shrill cries of children.", "行进中，你突然听到孩子们的尖叫声。");
	text = text.replace("Their baying draws you near, and you find them on one side of the road while on the other their parents are kneeling beneath about a dozen executioners\' swords.", "他们的尖叫声引起了你的注意，你发现他们在路的一边，而在另一边，他们的父母跪在十几个行刑者的剑下。");
	text = text.replace(/A lieutenant of (.*?) stands nearby, proudly holding up his noble house\'s banner\./, "一个 $1 的军官站在附近，骄傲地举着他贵族家族的旗帜。");
	text = text.replace("He stares at you.", "他凝视着你。");
	text = text.replace("Oh, sellsword. Have you come to watch?", "噢，佣兵。你是来观看行刑的吗？");
	text = text.replace("I hope so, because you best not intervene.", "我希望如此，你最好不要插手。");
	text = text.replace("This is not your fight.", "这与你无关。");
	text = text.replace("Needing a piss, you climb a nearby hill for a little privacy, but mostly just to get your thoughts in order.", "当你需要小便的时候，你会爬上附近的一座小山，以获得一点隐私。");
	text = text.replace("Sadly, that won\'t be happening.", "遗憾的是，这种情况不会发生。");
	text = text.replace(/Down the opposite slopes stand a number of men from (.*?), following the barking orders of their lieutenant who squats not far from where you were going to piss\./, "对面的山坡上站着一些人，他们是 $1 的人，听从他们的军官的命令，他们蹲伏在离你小便的地方不远的地方。");
	text = text.replace("The troops are rounding up women from a couple of hovels stitched into an adjacent hillside.", "军队正在把妇女从附近山坡上的几间小屋里围起来。");
	text = text.replace("The men of the hamlet are already slain, dead in the grass here and there.", "村子里的人已经被杀死了，死在草地上，到处都是。");
	text = text.replace("Little more than blotchy lumps at this distance.", "但是在你这个位置上看，那些尸体只不过是一些斑点。");
	text = text.replace("The lieutenant looks up at you.", "军官抬头看着你。");
	text = text.replace("Hello there, sellsword, nice day, no?", "你好，佣兵。很棒的一天，不是吗？");
	text = text.replace("He must have seen the disconcerting look on your face as his own soon sours.", "他一定看到了你脸上令人不安的表情。");
	text = text.replace("Hey. Listen. Don\'t be getting any ideas of heroism, yeah?", "嘿，听着。不要有任何英雄主义的想法，好吗？");
	text = text.replace("Just keep on walking.", "继续走你的。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ve seen that look before and if you don\'t put it away there\'ll be trouble for all of us.", "我以前见过这种表情，如果你不把它收起来，我们大家都会有麻烦。");
	text = text.replace("While walking a path, you hear the baying of some hounds.", "当你走在一条小路上时，你听到几只猎犬的吠叫声。");
	text = text.replace(/Apparently, a band of men from (.*?) have cleared out a few hovels and all that\'s left are the poor mongrels holed up in a kennel\./, "显然，一群来自 $1 的人已经清理了一些茅舍，剩下的只有躲在狗窝里的可怜杂种狗。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s a few soldiers standing outside it with torches, ready to set every mutt ablaze.", "外面站着几个拿着火把的士兵，随时准备点燃所有的狗窝。");
	text = text.replace("A lieutenant stands nearby, a horrid grin on his face, though it quickly fades upon seeing you.", "一个军官站在附近，脸上露出可怕的笑容，虽然这个表情在看到你后很快就消失了。");
	text = text.replace("Oh, you a dog lover or something?", "噢，你喜欢狗还是什么？");
	text = text.replace("Don\'t give me that look.", "别那样看着我。");
	text = text.replace("You\'d best keep to stepping, sellsword, or I\'ll treat you like one of these dogs here.", "你最好别管这件事，佣兵，不然我就把你当成这里的狗一样对待。");
	text = text.replace("During times of war, roads are often the worst places to be - they bring the terror to and fro and today is no different.", "在战争时期，道路往往是最糟糕的地方，他们的附近总是充斥着死亡。");
	text = text.replace(/You find a couple of (.*?) soldiers idling beside the path, staring down at someone they\'ve hogtied and hung over a fire yet to be lit\./, "你发现几个 $1 的士兵在小路旁闲逛，盯着一个他们绑在柴堆上的男人。");
	text = text.replace("As you walk up, the soldiers\' lieutenant turns to get a look at you.", "当你走过去的时候，士兵们的军官转过身来看你。");
	text = text.replace("Hey, if you don\'t like what you see, then keep on marching.", "嘿，如果你不喜欢你所看到的，那就不要管。");
	text = text.replace("This is war, what did you expect?", "这是战争，你想要什么？");
	text = text.replace("Now get outta here, we got a fire to start.", "现在离开这里，我们要生火了。");
	text = text.replace(/While trudging down a path off the main roads, keeping clear of the carnage that a civil war will wrought, you come to find a few soldiers of (.*?) torturing a man\./, "当你沿着一条偏离主干道的小路艰难跋涉，避开战争可能造成的大屠杀时，你发现几个 $1 的士兵正在折磨一个人。");
	text = text.replace("They\'ve lit torches partially wrapped in leather and are letting the scraps of burning hot strips fall onto their poor prisoner.", "他们点燃了用皮革包裹的火把，让燃烧着的碎片落到他们可怜的囚犯身上。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s screaming for mercy, but they\'ve certainly have none for him.", "他尖叫着要求宽恕，但是他们肯定没有宽恕他。");
	text = text.replace("Seeing you, though, he calls out, begging for help.", "然而，看到你，他大声呼救，乞求帮助。");
	text = text.replace("One of the soldiers turns to you.", "其中一个士兵转向你。");
	text = text.replace("Like what you see?", "就像你看到的？");
	text = text.replace("My father made this form of torture up.", "我父亲创造了这种酷刑。");
	text = text.replace("You just let the fiery leather drip all over them.", "让火热的皮革片滴在他们身上。");
	text = text.replace("Much better than just simple little embers.", "比简单的小火苗好多了。");
	text = text.replace(/With a quick bark of an order, the (.*?) charges to the rescue\./, "随着你一声令下，$1 决定进行救援。");
	text = text.replace(/The men of (.*?) are dispatched, bloody and quick\./, "$1 的人瞬间就被你的手下砍翻了。");
	text = text.replace("Crying and forever thankful, the rescued laymen practically kiss your feet.", "获救的村民一边哭一边感激着你，几乎要亲吻你的脚。");
	text = text.replace("You tell them to run, lest the rest of the nobility\'s army show up.", "你叫他们快跑，以免贵族军队的其他人出现。");
	text = text.replace(/You tell the men of (.*?) to make it quick\./, "你叫 $1 的人们动作快一点。");
	text = text.replace(/The soldiers of (.*?) try and defend themselves, but they\'d spent the last few minutes preparing to kill innocents, not defend themselves against hardier stock\./, "$1 的士兵试图保护自己，但是他们在生命的最后几分钟准备杀害无辜的人，而不是保护自己不受敌人伤害。");
	text = text.replace("They are felled with little difficulty.", "他们像稻草一样一个个倒下了。");
	text = text.replace("The rescued laymen run off, they shout thanks but stick around for little else.", "获救的村民迅速逃走，他们喊着谢谢，却没有留下来干别的。");
	text = text.replace(/The (.*?) isn\'t going to stand for such atrocities this day\./, "今天 $1 绝不会支持这种暴行。");
	text = text.replace(/You order the mercenaries to kill the few unprepared soldiers of (.*?) and they do as much in speedy fashion\./, "你命令雇佣兵杀死 $1 的士兵，你手下动作非常快。");
	text = text.replace("Rescued, the peasants and laymen give thanks.", "获救后，农民们表示感谢。");
	text = text.replace("You simply tell them to get lost as clearly this land is no longer safe for anyone.", "你告诉这些村民迅速离开这里，因为很明显，这片土地对任何人来说都不再安全。");
	text = text.replace("Against better judgment, you involve yourself.", "你的良知战胜了你的理性。");
	text = text.replace(/The men of (.*?) are ordered forth\./, "你命令 $1 的人迅速出击。");
	text = text.replace(/Unprepared for an actual fight, the soldiers of (.*?) are cut down in a quick, sometimes screaming order\./, "$1 的士兵对真正的战斗毫无准备，他们就像被割草一样死去。");
	text = text.replace("The peasants and common folks gives thanks for the rescue before hurrying off.", "村民们在逃走之前对你的救援千恩万谢。");
	text = text.replace(/You order your men to save the poor peasants, but the soldiers of (.*?) are ready for you\./, "你命令你的手下去拯救村民，但是 $1 的士兵已经准备好了。");
	text = text.replace("Not in arms - no, they do not have enough men for that - but in a couple of nearby horses.", "他们没有武器，人手也不足，但是他们有几匹快马。");
	text = text.replace("They ride off, no doubt to ruin your reputation with the nobility, but who gives a damn.", "毫无疑问，你在这里的行为会被贵族老爷知道的一清二楚。");
	text = text.replace("The laymen, by comparison, are forever grateful.", "但谁在乎呢，相比之下，获救的村民们是永远感激你的。");
	text = text.replace(/You order the man of (.*?) to make quick work of the soldiers\./, "你命令 $1 的人迅速干掉士兵。");
	text = text.replace("A few are quickly dispatched, but the lieutenant manages to field a horse and take off.", "有几个士兵很快就倒下了，但是军官设法骑上了一只快马。");
	text = text.replace("It\'s a very quick horse.", "这是一匹很快的马。");
	text = text.replace("You doubt you\'d be able to catch it if you had a horse yourself, which you do not.", "如果你自己有一匹马，你可能能抓住它，但你没有。");
	text = text.replace(/The rescued peasants are very grateful, though that probably won\'t help your reputation with the nobility of (.*?) now\./, "获救的农民非常感激，但这并不会让你和 $1 的关系变好。");
	text = text.replace("You failed to spot a few horses idling nearby.", "你没发现附近有几匹马在闲逛。");
	text = text.replace("While a few soldiers are quickly cut down, your mercenaries can\'t catch up to the lieutenant who mounts up and rides off in a cloud of dust and, in your case, soured reputation with the nobility.", "虽然一些雇佣兵很快就被杀死了，但是你的手下却无法追上军官，军官骑着快马跑了，这将会损害你在贵族那边的声誉。");
	text = text.replace("Not that you\'ve two shits to give what they think.", "并不是说你不在意他们的想法。");
	text = text.replace("The laymen, by comparison, are almost crying in their thanks.", "相比之下，那些村民们几乎要哭出来以表示感谢了。");
	text = text.replace("You tell them to leave and fast.", "你告诉他们快点离开这里。");
	text = text.replace("Who knows what dangers or ill intentions roam the lands these days.", "谁知道这些天在这片土地上会出现什么样的危险。");

//civilwar_town_conquered_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/News on the wind has it that (.*?) has taken (.*?) from (.*?)!/, "有消息说 $1 夺取 $2 赶走了 $3！");
	text = text.replace(/Messengers on the road say that (.*?) is the new ruler of (.*?), having taken it from (.*?) after a gruesome battle\./, "路上的信使说 $1 是 $2 的新统治者，是在一场可怕的战斗中击败了 $3 得到的。");
	text = text.replace("Redraw the maps!", "现在地图要重新绘制了！");
	text = text.replace(/Refugees, messengers, and traders on the road are reporting that (.*?) now belongs to (.*?)!/, "难民、信使和商人都在路上谈论一件事情，$1 现在属于 $2 了！");

//civilwar_trapped_soldiers_event.nut
	text = text.replace("You come across a large throng of peasants in an uproar.", "你遇到一大群吵吵闹闹的农民。");
	text = text.replace(/Upon closer look, they\'ve surrounded a small band of soldiers carrying the banner of (.*?), who this very village belongs to\./, "你仔细一看，这些农民包围了一队举着 $1 旗帜的士兵，这个村庄就是属于他们的。");
	text = text.replace("Each man has his sword out, but they\'ve been back into a corner and completely outnumbered.", "每个士兵都拔出了自己的剑，但是他们被逼到了角落里，寡不敌众。");
	text = text.replace("The laymen shout and point.", "村民们大喊大叫，指指点点。");
	text = text.replace("Murderers! Rapists! Arsonists!", "杀人犯！强奸犯！纵火犯！");
	text = text.replace(/Spitting and tomato throwing follow suit\. (.*?) comes to you and asks if the men should step in or stay out of it\./, "口水和烂西红柿跟雨点一样飞向那些士兵。$1 来问你，是该介入此事还是置身事外。");
	text = text.replace("No man, especially of the fighting stock, deserves to be lynched.", "没有人应该被处以私刑，尤其是那些战士。");
	text = text.replace("You order you men to step in, barking the command loud enough to turn half the crowd around to see you.", "你命令你的人站出来，大声发出命令，让一半的人都看到你。");
	text = text.replace("Gasps ripple through the throng, and you nod confidently.", "人群一下安静了下来，你自信的点了点头。");
	text = text.replace("Step aside, peasants. These men might be deserving of many things, but your unruly justice is not one of them.", "都给我让开，农民们。这些人或许应该受到一些惩罚，但你们这些私刑可不在其中。");
	text = text.replace("A scruffy layman cries out.", "一个衣衫褴褛的农民大叫起来。");
	text = text.replace("But they\'re murderers and worse!", "但他们是杀人犯，甚至更糟！");
	text = text.replace("You throw a stern look.", "你做出一个严厉的表情。");
	text = text.replace("And so are my men.", "我的人也一样。");
	text = text.replace("Now get out of the way.", "现在给我让开。");
	text = text.replace("The crowd does as told.", "人们照你说的做了。");
	text = text.replace(/The rescued soldiers tell you that (.*?) will hear of your deeds here\./, "获救的士兵告诉你 $1 会知道你在这里的事迹。");
	text = text.replace("Getting involved might simply complicate matters - peasants are fickle and uneducated, seers of their own solitude, purveyors of bad luck and paranoia.", "参与其中可能只会使事情变得更加复杂，农民善变，没有文化又固执己见。");
	text = text.replace("You order your men not to just stand aside, but to make themselves small.", "你命令你的人尽量站在一边，不要引起注意。");
	text = text.replace("A thrown rocks open up the attack, soon followed by a wall of pitchforks and machetes.", "一块扔出去的石头吹响了进攻的号角，随着而来的是一堵由干草叉和大砍刀组成的墙。");
	text = text.replace("The soldiers try and put up a fight, but the best summation of their defense is one of horrid screaming.", "被包围的士兵奋起试图防抗，但总结他们防御的最佳解释就是一声尖叫。");
	text = text.replace("One is dragged out of the pile, kicking and screaming, and the peasants stab him repeatedly until he stops.", "一个士兵从人堆中被拉出来，又踢又叫，农民们不停的用干草叉插他，直到这名士兵一动不动。");
	text = text.replace("Another is roped and run up a tree, hanged by the pull of three angry men.", "另一个士兵被三个愤怒的农民用绳子捆起来，吊到一棵树上，勒死了。");
	text = text.replace("Satiated, the crowd quiets down.", "混乱之后，人群满足了，安静了下来。");
	text = text.replace("Children dance around the dead man\'s feet.", "孩子们围着死者跳舞。");
	text = text.replace("A poor and mumbling man lily hops around the corpses, picking through the pockets of each.", "一个可怜而喃喃自语的男人在尸体周围走来走去，从每具尸体的口袋里掏钱。");
	text = text.replace("You decide to keep out of it.", "你决定置身事外。");
	text = text.replace("This isn\'t your fight and involving yourself will only complicate things.", "这不是你的战斗，卷入其中只会让事情变得更复杂。");
	text = text.replace("Standing back, you watch as the crowd collapses in on the soldiers.", "站在后面，你看着人群向士兵们挤过来。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s a scuffle, shrill voices pipe over the din of the chaos, squirming cries of those unprepared for such a brutal final moment.", "在混乱的喧闹声中传来一阵扭打声，刺耳的声音盖过了嘈杂的声音，是那些还没有做好面对疯狂农民的士兵发出的扭曲尖叫。");
	text = text.replace("But one man pushes his way through the crowd, kicking people off his legs and daggering one man in the eye.", "但一名士兵从人群中挤出去，把农民从腿上踢下来，并用匕首刺穿了一个农民的眼睛。");
	text = text.replace("He manages to sprint to a nearby horse, mount up, and spur it into a sprint.", "他设法向附近的一匹马冲刺，骑上马，鞭策它冲刺。");
	text = text.replace(/The man eyes the (.*?)\'s banner as he passes by\./, "那个人经过时，眼睛盯着 $1的旗帜。");
	text = text.replace(/You can\'t help but think that (.*?) might hear of your neutrality on this day\.\.\./, "你不禁会想，$1 可能会在这一天听到你保持中立的消息…");

//civilwar_treasurer_event.nut
	text = text.replace("While marching the lands, you come to find a farmer being accosted by a well-to-do looking man.", "当你在行军时，你发现一个农夫正被一个看上去很富裕的人搭讪。");
	text = text.replace("Seeing you, the farmer quickly calls out.", "看到你，农夫很快叫了起来。");
	text = text.replace("Sir, help me! This treasurer wants to take my crops!", "先生，帮帮我！这位司库要拿走我的庄稼！");
	text = text.replace("The treasurer nods, seemingly as though there\'s no crime being committed here.", "司库理所当然的点了点头。");
	text = text.replace(/That is correct\. I\'ve been sent from (.*?) and I am here to collect food stores for the army\./, "没错。我是 $1 派来为军队收集粮食的。");
	text = text.replace("This is our land, and thus our crops.", "这是我们的土地，也是我们的庄稼。");
	text = text.replace(/The grind of war gets steadily worse\.\.\. (.*?) asks what you want to do\./, "战争的折磨越来越严重... $1 问你想做什么。");
	text = text.replace("Although morality has little play in the game of war, you can\'t help but think this poor farmer\'s done nothing wrong.", "虽然道德在战争中没有什么用，但你认为这个贫穷的农夫并没有做错什么。");
	text = text.replace("You grab the treasurer by his shirt and press him against a farmhouse.", "你抓住司库的衬衫，把他按在农舍的墙上。");
	text = text.replace("His eyes go wide, as though you just pierced some veil of invincibility.", "他的眼睛睁得大大的，好像你刚刚刺破了某种不可战胜的面纱。");
	text = text.replace("Just what do you think you\'re doing?", "你知道你在做什么吗？");
	text = text.replace("You loosen your grab, because while this man may not be invincible, his name does have the backing of one.", "你松开了手，因为这个人虽然没有什么战斗力，但从他名字上看出来他有后台。");
	text = text.replace("Tell your men that this farmer had nothing to offer.", "告诉你的人，这个农夫已经没有什么可给的了。");
	text = text.replace("Crops were bad this season, got it?", "这个季节庄稼欠收，知道吗？");
	text = text.replace("You put one hand on the pommel of your sword.", "你把一只手放在剑柄上。");
	text = text.replace("The man glances at it, then quickly nods.", "男人瞥了它一眼，然后迅速点头。");
	text = text.replace("Alright, I got it.", "我会的，我照做！");
	text = text.replace("The farmer thanks you from the bottom of his heart, and also a little by the bottom of his food stores, rewarding you with a few sacks of grains for your help.", "农夫从心底感谢你，他从他的食物储备里面挤出一袋谷物来感谢你的行为。");
	text = text.replace("While you feel bad for the farmer, feelings aren\'t exactly worth much when there\'s a great war going on between the noble houses.", "跟贵族家族战争中的利益相比，农夫的事情不过是小事。");
	text = text.replace("You choose not to involve yourself.", "你选择置身事外。");
	text = text.replace("As the treasurer\'s daytalers carry sacks of grain onto a wagon, he comes over to talk.", "当司库的临时工把一袋袋的谷物搬上载重货车时，他走过来说。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ll tell the nobility of your, well, noble decision here.", "我要告诉贵族们你在这的决定。");
	text = text.replace("You could have caused a stir, but you did not.", "你本可以阻止我们，但你没有。");
	text = text.replace("Thank you, mercenary. The men of our army needed this food more than you can know.", "谢谢你，雇佣兵。我们军队的人比你想象的更需要这些食物。");
	text = text.replace("Initially, it seemed as though there were two options here, but as a sellsword free from the bonds of nobility, responsibility, and well, any sort of social shackle, you choose a third angle: taking the food for you and your men.", "起初，这里似乎有两个选择，但是作为一个没有贵族责任和任何社会束缚的佣兵，你有了第三个选择：给你和你的人拿食物。");
	text = text.replace("Both treasurer and farmer protest, but your men draw their blades, which is a quick way to silence any sort of debate.", "司库和农夫都表示抗议，但是你的手下拔出了刀，这是一个让任何形式的辩论都能瞬间保持沉默行动。");
	text = text.replace("In total, there\'s really not that much to take and you get the ire of the common man as well as the nobility for the trouble.", "总的来说，没什么好拿的，而且你会为此惹恼平民和贵族。");

//civilwar_warnings_event.nut
	text = text.replace("You come across a stranger in the path.", "你在路上碰到一个陌生人。");
	text = text.replace("He regards you with a steely gaze, a troop of sheep and dogs idling at his side.", "他凝视着你，一群绵羊和狗在他身边闲荡。");
	text = text.replace(/Mmm, don\'t suppose yer gearing up to fight for (.*?) are ya\?/, "嗯，难道你不准备为 $1 而战吗？");
	text = text.replace("I hear it and the other families of the realm are quarreling.", "我听说，王国里的其他家族在因为某种我不知道的原因争吵。");
	text = text.replace(/Don\'t know what about\. Just know they\'ll come by my place and ask, \'(.*?), why don\'tchu come and fight for us, or else we hang ya\', and I\'ll say \'okay\', because a buncha gold-britches nobleman ruining my year is a part of life, and life just ain\'t fair\./, "我只知道他们会来我家问我，“$1，要么加入我们，要么被我们绞死！”，而我会说“没问题”，因为平静生活被贵族摧毁也是生活的一部分，生活就是不公平的。");
	text = text.replace("A woman in the road stands by the company\'s wayside as you march past.", "在你行军的时候，有个女人站路边。");
	text = text.replace("She looks your sigil up and down.", "她上下打量着你的印记。");
	text = text.replace("Hmph, don\'t recognize that one.", "嗯哼，我不认识这个。");
	text = text.replace("S\'pose the nobles will be calling for your services soon.", "不过贵族们很快就会要求你为他们服务。");
	text = text.replace("You ask what she means. She shrugs.", "你问她什么意思。她耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("Way I hears it, the pompy pissants be mad about a royal marriage gone awry.", "据我所知，那些夸夸其谈的人对皇室婚姻的失败感到愤怒。");
	text = text.replace("Lotta noise coming about how it means war or some such shite.", "关于战争或诸如此类的蠢事的声音越来越多。");
	text = text.replace("They noblefolk always squabbling over something, only a matter of time \'til they cross swords with one another, or ask us poorfolk to do it for them.", "他们贵族总是为一些事情喋喋不休，只是时间的问题，直到他们彼此交战，或让我们这些穷人为他们做这件事。");
	text = text.replace("An old man sitting and smoking a pipe regards your company with a long, hazy stare.", "一个坐着抽烟斗的老人用一种朦胧的眼光久久地凝视着你。");
	text = text.replace("Mercenaries, eh? There will be a lotta good work for you in the coming days.", "雇佣兵，嗯？在未来的日子里，你会有很多活可以接。");
	text = text.replace("You ask what he means.", "你问他是什么意思。");
	text = text.replace("He cleans the pipe, clattering it against his cheer.", "他把烟斗擦干净，发出咔嚓咔嚓的响声。");
	text = text.replace("Ohh, you know. The feather-wearin\' noblefolk are peacockin\' again.", "噢，你知道的。贵族们又在炫耀了。");
	text = text.replace("War\'s coming, no doubt about it - can\'t let all this good weather go to waste.", "战争即将来临，毫无疑问－不能让这么好的天气白白浪费掉。");
	text = text.replace("A messenger comes by the path, his pannier swinging empty.", "一个信使走了过来，他的挎包里空荡荡的。");
	text = text.replace("Ah, I\'m all out of news, but I got some rumors if yer interested.", "唉，我没什么消息，但如果你有兴趣的话，我有一些谣言。");
	text = text.replace("You nod. He smiles.", "你点头。他笑了。");
	text = text.replace("Figured as much. Now, sometimes the noblefolk call me up to give me papers to send out.", "大概是这样。现在，贵族们有时会让我把文件寄出去。");
	text = text.replace("Sometimes little ol\' me eavesdrops on their conversations.", "有时我也会偷听他们的谈话。");
	text = text.replace("And what I hear is a lot of army talk, lotta \'we gotta conquer them sumbitches\' sorta talk.", "我听到的很多关于军队的言论，很多诸如“我们要征服他们”之类的言论。");
	text = text.replace("So, sellsword, you should be expecting some good business real soon.", "所以，佣兵，你马上就有很多活要接了。");
	text = text.replace("Psst. Psst! Hey!", "嘘。嘘！嘿！");
	text = text.replace("You turn around to see a boy poking his head out of a bush.", "你转过身，看到一个男孩从灌木丛中探出头来。");
	text = text.replace("He smiles at you.", "他对你微笑。");
	text = text.replace("Hey, I got something to say.", "嘿，我有话要说。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s a war a comin\'.", "战争马上就要来了。");
	text = text.replace("Believing this snarky little runt isn\'t high on your to do list.", "你不是很相信这个小矮子。");
	text = text.replace("You ask how he knows that. He smiles again.", "你问他怎么知道的。他又笑了。");
	text = text.replace("I fetch water for a man who wears silk britches.", "我给一个穿丝绸裤子的人打水。");
	text = text.replace("He said, \'I can give ye some sweets, or give ye something to think about.\' I said tell me something good.", "他说，“我可以给你们一些糖果，或者给你们一些思考的东西。”我说，告诉我一些好消息。");
	text = text.replace("He said, \'the nobility are gonna fight one another.\' So that\'s what I\'m telling ya.", "他说，“贵族们要开战了。”这就是我要告诉你的。");
	text = text.replace("The kid pauses.", "这个孩子停顿了一下。");
	text = text.replace("Say, ya wouldn\'t happen to have any sweets, would ya? Hey... hey!", "喂，你不会碰巧有糖果吧？嘿…嘿！");
	text = text.replace("You push the kid\'s head back into the bushes.", "你把孩子的头推回灌木丛。");
	text = text.replace("An old man and a fair-skinned maiden meets you on the road.", "一个老人和一个皮肤白皙的姑娘在路上遇见你。");
	text = text.replace("She\'s twisting a braid of hair over a shoulder, glancing at a couple of your better looking men with plying eyes.", "她把一根发辫搭在肩膀上，用一双迷人的眼睛瞥了你两个相貌较好的男人一眼。");
	text = text.replace(/Before you get a word out, she asks if you\'re going to fight for (.*?) or (.*?)\./, "在你开口之前，她问你是要为什么而战，是 $1 还是 $2。");
	text = text.replace("They say a prince ran off with a princess, said it t\'was a matter of love. Isn\'t that dreamy?", "他们说王子和公主私奔了，说这是爱情的问题。那不是梦吗？");
	text = text.replace("You shrug. The elderly man hocks and spits.", "你耸耸肩。这位老人咳嗽了几声，吐了几口唾沫。");
	text = text.replace("Don\'t bother the sellswords with your fantasies, woman.", "女人，不要用你的幻想去打扰佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("Sorry, mercenary, she gets these ideas in her head and I don\'t know where from.", "对不起，雇佣兵，她脑子里有这些想法，我也不知道是从哪儿来的。");
	text = text.replace("The houses are talking of war, but it sure as shite ain\'t over a prancing prince or some punter of a princess.", "家家户户都在谈论战争，但毫无疑问，战争不会比一个欢蹦乱跳的王子或某个公主更可怕。");
	text = text.replace("Economics! That\'s the issue.", "经济学！这就是问题所在。");
	text = text.replace("Long standing trade agreements are falling apart just like the paper they was written upon.", "长期存在的贸易协定正在分崩离析，就像当初签署它们的那张纸一样。");
	text = text.replace("Let me tell you, I was there when they...", "让我告诉你，当他们…");
	text = text.replace("The old fart dawdles on.", "这个老家伙慢吞吞地说着一些你听不懂的话。");
	text = text.replace("You much preferred the lady\'s story, as ludicrous as it sounded.", "你更喜欢那位女士的故事，尽管听起来很可笑。");
	text = text.replace("You come across a man sitting atop a signpost.", "你看见一个人坐在路标顶上。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s tightening strings on a lute and testing the sounds.", "他正在勒紧琵琶上的琴弦，测试琴声。");
	text = text.replace("Mmhmm, that was better, wouldn\'t you agree? Just agree.", "嗯哼，那样更好，你不同意吗？只要同意就行。");
	text = text.replace("Nodding, you ask the man what he is doing.", "你点头，你问他在做什么。");
	text = text.replace("He jumps off the signpost and lands arms and legs out like a jester at the end of his act.", "他从路标上跳下来，像个小丑一样在表演结束时拉伸胳膊和腿。");
	text = text.replace("Practicing! War is comin\', heard on the winds m\'self, and with war comes a need for... for... for... c\'mon, you can do it, entertainment! That\'s right!", "练习！战争即将来临，我能在风中听到它的声音，随着战争的到来…为了…为了…拜托，你能做到的，娱乐！没错！");
	text = text.replace("And in any call for nightly pleasures is a call for me - and in more ways than one, let me tell ya.", "对我来说，任何一个夜晚快乐的呼唤都是对我的呼唤－在很多方面，让我告诉你。");
	text = text.replace("He pirouettes and grins.", "他踮起脚尖，咧着嘴笑。");
	text = text.replace("You\'ve never seen a man with a whiter smile and you have a strong urge to blacken it dearly.", "你从未见过一个笑容更白的男人，而你却有一种强烈的冲动要把他的笑容深深地涂黑。");
	text = text.replace("The minstrel prances down the path.", "吟游诗人在小路上翩翩起舞。");
	text = text.replace("Don\'t you worry, sellsword, with the nobles fighting amongst themselves there shall never be a shortage of work for men of your, er, talents. G\'day!", "别担心，佣兵，贵族们互相厮杀，像你这样有才能的人永远都不会缺少工作。今天！");
	text = text.replace("More and more, you\'re coming across peasants and merchants murmuring about a war between the noble houses.", "你越来越多地遇到抱怨贵族家族战争的农民与商人。");
	text = text.replace("Your station as a sellsword has them asking you which side you are planning to carry your banner for.", "你处于佣兵的地位，他们同时也会问你打算为哪个贵族而战。");
	text = text.replace(/If these rumors are true, then the (.*?) stands to make a great deal of coin out of the misery wrought between pompous highborn\./, "如果这些谣言是真实的，那么 $1 将会从这两个自命不凡的贵族之间获得巨大的财富。");
	text = text.replace("You come across a number of gamblers on the road.", "你在路上遇到许多赌徒。");
	text = text.replace("They\'ve positioned little flags representing all the noble families of the land.", "他们插上小旗子，代表这片土地上所有的贵族。");
	text = text.replace("The bookie is writing down notes and looks over his scroll.", "赌徒正在写笔记，并看了看他的卷轴。");
	text = text.replace("Now remember, the results of this war between houses isn\'t going to be obvious for some time.", "现在记住，这场贵族之战在短期是不会有结果的。");
	text = text.replace("Hell, I most of ye will be conscripted.", "见鬼，我们大多数人都会被征召入伍。");
	text = text.replace("But all who survive shall return to me in one year\'s time.", "但所有幸存的人将在一年后回到我身边。");
	text = text.replace("From there, we will pay out the monies to those who bet on the winning noble house. Deal?", "从那里，我们会把钱支付给那些押注于获胜的贵族家族的人。干不干？");
	text = text.replace("Crooked faced and slackjawed peasants shrug.", "歪着脸、松着嘴的农民耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("Sounds like a deal to me!", "听起来很划算！");
	text = text.replace("The bookie grins, a golden incisor glinting ever so slightly.", "赌徒咧嘴一笑，金门牙微微一闪。");
	text = text.replace("Great!", "很好！");
	text = text.replace("He takes the bets in a satchel and loads up for the road, most likely to never return again.", "他把赌注装在一个袋子里，然后满载而归，并且很可能再也不会回来了。");
	text = text.replace("Truly a shame what sorta nonsense the lowborn get themselves into.", "真是可耻，下层社会的人都是些什么狗屁东西。");
	text = text.replace("During your travels, you keep hearing a particularly interesting rumor: that the noble houses are positioning for war.", "在你的旅行中，你不断听到一个特别有趣的谣言：贵族家族正在为战争做准备。");
	text = text.replace(/If true, the (.*?) could stand to make a lot of coin, particularly if it chooses a winning side\./, "如果是真的，$1 可以赚很多硬币，特别是它选对了获胜方。");
	text = text.replace("Peasant after peasant is telling the same story lately.", "近来，一个接一个的农民都在讲同样的故事。");
	text = text.replace("In fact, they seem to be repeating it every time you meet them...", "事实上，每次你见到他们时，他们似乎都在重复这句话…");
	text = text.replace("War. War is on their lips.", "战争。战争就在他们的嘴边。");
	text = text.replace("The noble houses are squabbling over something you could care less about, but what it means is war, and war means crowns for a sellsword, and crowns are good, so war is good.", "贵族家族正在为一些你不太关心的事情争吵，但这意味着战争，战争意味着佣兵的克朗，克朗是好的，所以战争是好的。");
	text = text.replace(/Should these rumors be true, the (.*?) should measure its options carefully and choose a noblehouse to support in the conflict to come\./, "如果这些传言是真的，$1 应该仔细衡量自己的选择，并选择一个贵族来应付即将到来的冲突。");
	text = text.replace("You\'ve noticed recruiters for the noble houses are afoot, pulling young, fresh men out of their homes.", "你已经注意到，贵族家族的招聘人员正忙着把年轻的男性从家里拉出来。");
	text = text.replace("Conscription isn\'t unordinary, but typically you still need the fellas to farm the fields.", "征兵并不是什么新鲜事，但通常情况下，你还是需要小伙子来种田。");
	text = text.replace("If the highborn are leaving that to the womenfolk, then it means something else is of greater import, and that something else is undoubtedly a brewing war.", "如果出身高贵的人把这些都留给了女性，那就意味着有某个东西更重要，而这个东西无疑是一场酝酿中的战争。");
	text = text.replace(/The (.*?) should prepare itself for the worst - well, the worst for everyone else\./, "$1 应该为最坏的情况做好准备－好吧，为其他人做最坏的准备。");
	text = text.replace("A war between rich arseholes is the greatest time to be a sellsword!", "有钱人之间的战争是成为佣兵的最好时机！");

//civilwar_wounded_soldier_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/While marching along a path, you come across a soldier of (.*?), your allies\./, "当你沿着一条小路行进时，你遇到了一个 $1 的士兵，他是你的盟友。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s on the ground, leaning against a rock wall, one draped over the top of it as if he\'d just placed the last stone.", "他躺在地上，靠在石墙上，石墙上盖着一块石头，好像他刚把最后一块石头放下来似的。");
	text = text.replace("Looking up at you, he sneers.", "他抬头看着你，冷笑着。");
	text = text.replace("Whatcha want, mercenary?", "你想要什么，雇佣兵？");
	text = text.replace("You come to finish me off, huh?", "你是来杀我的，哏？");
	text = text.replace("Take all I got and more?", "要拿走我所有的东西？");
	text = text.replace("He\'s wearing a nice set of armor and has a weapon on him.", "他穿着一套漂亮的盔甲，身上还带着件武器。");
	text = text.replace(/Not that he\'ll be defending himself with it in his current state, but it\'d look good in the hands of one of your men\. (.*?) walks up\./, "在他现在的状态下，不是说他会用它来保护自己，而是在你的手下手里看起来不错。$1 走上去。");
	text = text.replace("We can take him, sir, but we should make it quick.", "我们可以干掉他，先生，但我们得速战速决。");
	text = text.replace("Who knows who could catch us for he wears the cloth of a nobleman\'s army.", "因为他这身贵族军服，我们行动越慢就越有危险。");
	text = text.replace(/You come across a wounded soldier of (.*?), your allies\./, "你遇到一个受伤的 $1 士兵，是你的盟友。");
	text = text.replace("Lying in the grass, he postures up to get a good look at you and you get a good look at him in return: the man is adorned with a decent armor piece and he\'s got a weapon balanced across his legs.", "他躺在草地上，盯着你，你也盯着他：这个人身上戴着一件像样的盔甲，腿上还摆放着一把武器。");
	text = text.replace("You could take both, but the man does not seem willing to peacefully part with either.", "你可以把他的东西全部抢走，但是很明显，他不会愿意。");
	text = text.replace("And there\'s a good chance the rest of the soldier\'s army is not far off...", "而且士兵的军队很可能就在不远处…");
	text = text.replace(/A wounded soldier of (.*?), your allies, lays in the path\./, "一位受伤的 $1 士兵，你的盟友，躺在路上。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s dragging himself away, but upon hearing you he stops and turns around.", "他拖着身子爬行，但一听到你的声音，他就停下来转过身来。");
	text = text.replace("Ah hell. You\'d best turn \'round, mercenary.", "啊，见鬼。你最好不要对我有什么坏心思，雇佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("My men are not far yonder and if you come after me I\'ll scream.", "我的人就离着不远，如果你再跟着我，我就会尖叫。");
	//text = text.replace("You raise an eyebrow.", "你挑挑眉毛。");
	text = text.replace("You\'ll go out like a woman, eh?", "你会像个娘们那样做，嗯？");
	text = text.replace("The man spits.", "那个人吐了口唾沫。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ll go out knowing I won\'t have to wait long to meet ya again in the next world.", "我知道我不用等太久就能在另一个世界看到你了。");
	text = text.replace(/The snarky git has a nice set of armor and weapons on him, but (.*?) does warn he is a member of a nobleman\'s army\./, "这个狡猾的家伙身上有一套很好的盔甲和武器，但是 $1 警告你，他是贵族军队的一员。");
	text = text.replace(/A wounded soldier of (.*?)\'s army lies before you\./, "一个 $1的军队的伤兵躺在你面前。");
	text = text.replace("On one hand, he does have a weapon and some armor you could take from him.", "一方面，他确实有一件武器和一些盔甲，你可以从他身上抢走。");
	text = text.replace("On the other hand, he is no doubt party to a much, much larger force than yours.", "另一方面，他无疑是一支比你们强大得多的军队的一部分。");
	text = text.replace("It just happens to not be watching at this very moment.", "只是此时此刻这支军队不在周围。");
	text = text.replace("If you decide to take his things, be sure to be quick about it.", "如果你决定抢他的东西，一定要快。");
	text = text.replace("Luck or impending disaster?", "是幸运还是灾难？");
	text = text.replace("You\'ve found a wounded soldier dressed in reasonably nice looking armor.", "你发现一个伤兵穿着相当漂亮的盔甲。");
	text = text.replace(/He\'s also got a weapon by his side that\'d look even better by the side of one of the (.*?)\'s men\./, "他身边还带着一件武器，放在 $1的人旁边看起来会更好看。");
	text = text.replace("Taking his things would be a cinch.", "拿走他的东西很容易。");
	text = text.replace("No one\'s around to see and muffling him wouldn\'t be that hard.", "周围没有人能看见他，而且让他发不出声也不是什么难事。");
	text = text.replace(/Then again, if someone were to see it\'d most likely be someone party to a very, very large army because this soldier happens to wear the cloth of (.*?), your ally. Decisions, decisions\.\.\./, "但是你这样做很可能会被一支人数众多的军队所注意，因为这个士兵碰巧穿着你的盟友 $1 的衣服。于是你决定，决定…");
	text = text.replace(/You come across a wounded soldier wearing a shredded banner of (.*?), your ally\./, "你遇到一个伤兵，他身上挂着你的盟友 $1 的破旗子。");
	text = text.replace("Seeing you, he quickly scoots backward across the grass.", "看到你，他飞快地向后跨过草地。");
	text = text.replace(/He throws his hand out and tries to curse, but only blood spits from his mouth. (.*?) walks up to you\./, "他伸出手想骂人，但从他嘴里喷出来的只有血。$1 向你走过来。");
	text = text.replace("Sir, he\'s got a nice set of armor and a weapon on him.", "先生，他身上有一套漂亮的盔甲和武器。");
	text = text.replace("We could take him out, if you want, but there is a risk that his army is not far off.", "如果你愿意的话，我们可以把他干掉，但他的军队有可能就在不远处。");
	text = text.replace("We should be very careful about this.", "我们应该非常小心。");
	text = text.replace(/You find a soldier of (.*?) trying to kick in the door of an abandoned hovel\./, "你发现一个 $1 的士兵试图踢进一个废弃的小屋的门。");
	text = text.replace("Hearing you, he quickly wheels around, lifting a sword up to defend himself.", "听到你的话，他迅速转过身来，举起一把剑自卫。");
	text = text.replace("The blade, however, wobbles in an unsteady grip.", "然而，刀刃摇摇晃晃，握力不稳。");
	text = text.replace("Blood runs the length of his arm, dripping off at the wrist, and the man is struggling to stand.", "血从他的手臂一直流到手腕，他挣扎着站着。");
	text = text.replace("Stay back, the lot of you!", "退后，你们所有人都给我退后！");
	text = text.replace("A fearful man backed into a corner.", "之后他慢慢的往角落里靠。");
	text = text.replace("How unfortunate he isn\'t an animal, lest you\'d think twice about...", "就当你准备下令前进时…");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) grabs you by the arm\./, "$1 抓着你的手。");
	text = text.replace("Hold on, sir. If the rest of his army spots us we are going to be in some real trouble.", "等一下，先生。如果他的军队发现我们，我们就有麻烦了。");
	text = text.replace("Let\'s try and think this out, yeah?", "我们行动前得先认真想想。");
	text = text.replace("You unsheathe your sword and approach the soldier.", "你拔出剑来，向士兵走去。");
	text = text.replace("He cries out, but it is brief, ending on the sharp twang of your blade running his tongue through the back of his head.", "他叫了一声，但声音很短，最后以你的利刃划过他的后脑勺发出的尖锐鼻音而结束。");
	text = text.replace("Gargling, he batters the metal of the killing blow before settling down.", "他一边挣扎，一边敲打着那给他致命一击的金属，然后坐了下来。");
	text = text.replace("Shivering eyes look up at you as a cold death takes him.", "颤抖的眼睛仰望着你，就像寒冷的死亡带走了他。");
	text = text.replace("Retrieving your sword, you look over your shoulder and tell the men to take everything he had on him.", "你收回剑，回头告诉那些人把他身上所有的东西都拿走。");
	text = text.replace("You wipe your blade on the cloth of the dead man\'s banner.", "你在死者的旗帜布上擦拭你的刀刃。");
	text = text.replace("The man sees in the intent in your eyes and quickly raises his voice, but you dash forward, unsheathing your blade and running it through his brainpan in one swift motion.", "那个人从你的眼神中看出了你的意图，迅速提高了嗓门，但你冲过去，拔出你的利刃，飞快地把它刺穿了他的脑壳。");
	text = text.replace("He dies, and you feel a pang in your side.", "他死了，你感到一阵剧痛。");
	text = text.replace(/Not a moral one, but an older, more real pain\. (.*?) steadies you with a hand on your shoulder\./, "不是一种道德上的痛苦，而是一种更老、更真切的痛苦。$1 把手搭在你的肩膀上，让你保持稳定。");
	text = text.replace("Easy, sir, you\'re not as limber as you once were.", "放松点，先生，你已经不像以前那么灵活了。");
	text = text.replace("Nodding, you clean your blade and tell the men to loot what they can.", "你点头，你清洗你的刀刃，并且告诉手下，把这个士兵身上的东西都拿走。");
	text = text.replace("The soldier leans back.", "这个士兵向后靠了靠。");
	text = text.replace("Ah, I see.", "唉，我知道了。");
	text = text.replace("He lifts his neck.", "他抬起他的脖子。");
	text = text.replace("You got me. I\'ll go out like a man should.", "行，我已经无处可逃了。我会像一个男人一样死去。");
	text = text.replace("With a quick cut, he puts his head back down, a bubbling crimson froth running down his chest.", "他头往后仰，自刎了，血液乱喷。");
	text = text.replace("Your men loot what they can.", "你的手下随后抢光了他的东西。");
	text = text.replace("You take out your dagger.", "你拿出匕首。");
	text = text.replace("The man lifts his weapon, but you kick it aside.", "那人举起武器，你却把它踢到一边。");
	text = text.replace("His arm falls effortlessly, as though you\'d actually just relieved him of a huge burden.", "他的手臂不费吹灰之力就垂下来了，好像你刚刚帮他减轻了一个巨大的负担。");
	text = text.replace("He stares up at you.", "他盯着你看。");
	text = text.replace("Wait...", "等等…");
	text = text.replace("That is his last word.", "这是他最后一句话了。");
	text = text.replace("He tries to utter something else, but the massive gash you\'ve opened across his throat only produces horrid gargling.", "他试着说点别的，但是你在他喉咙上划开的大口子只会让他发出可怕的漱口声。");
	text = text.replace(/You order (.*?) to loot all that he can from the body\./, "你命令 $1 把尸体上所有东西都拿走。");
	text = text.replace("You take out your sword and step toward the man.", "你拿出你的剑，走向那个人。");
	text = text.replace("He puts his hand up and you drive the blade through his palm and straight into his brainpan.", "他举起手来，你把刀锋穿过他的手掌，直接插入他的大脑。");
	text = text.replace("His tongue lolls his final words, some slobbering bloodslaked utterance.", "他的舌头耷拉着最后的话语，血液混合着唾液流了下来。");
	text = text.replace(/Cleaning your blade, you turn to (.*?), only to see bannermen standing on the horizon\./, "清理着你的刀，你转向 $1，但是只看到一名士兵站在地平线上。");
	text = text.replace("Oh bloody shite. Everybody run!", "噢，该死的混蛋！大家快跑！");
	text = text.replace(/The (.*?) makes a quick, though messy escape, bounding through copses and creekbeds and doubling back and hiding and silently killing one hound dog before it could bark\./, "$1 行动很快，尽管逃跑很混乱，你们穿过灌木丛，越过河床，甚至还悄悄的杀死了一只还没来得及吠叫的猎狗。");
	text = text.replace("You manage to get away in the end, but without time to take anything.", "你最终设法逃脱了，但没有时间带走任何东西。");
	text = text.replace("You take out your sword and plunge it into the man\'s chest.", "你拿出你的剑，刺进那人的胸膛。");
	text = text.replace("He reaches out and grabs you by your shirt, pulling himself up the blade.", "他伸出手抓住你的衬衫，把自己拉上刀刃。");
	text = text.replace("He bears his teeth in a bloodying grin.", "他咧嘴一笑，露出了血淋淋的牙齿。");
	text = text.replace("Go fark yourself, mercenary.", "你自己去吧，雇佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ll see you on the other side.", "我会在另一边等你。");
	text = text.replace("He lets go and falls back, a gush of red spewing out as your sword leaves him.", "他松开手，向后倒去，你的剑离开他的时候，一股血色喷涌而出。");
	text = text.replace(/Suddenly, (.*?) calls to you, his voice pitched high\./, "突然，$1 高声向你叫喊。");
	text = text.replace("Sir, we should go! The bannermen, look!", "先生，我们快跑吧！士兵，看！");
	text = text.replace(/Standing atop a nearby hill are the riders of (.*?) and they no doubt saw what you did\./, "站在附近一座山上的是 $1 的骑手，他们无疑看到了你的所作所为。");
	text = text.replace("Shouting as loud as you can, you order the men to beat a quick retreat.", "你尽可能大声喊叫，命令士兵们迅速撤退。");
	text = text.replace("Although you manage to get away, you no doubt exchanged for good will of your potential employer.", "虽然你设法逃脱了，但毫无疑问，你换来了你未来雇主的好意。");
	text = text.replace("The soldier laughs as you bear down on him.", "当你向那个士兵施加压力时，他笑了。");
	text = text.replace("He laughs as you stick him in the chest with your sword.", "当你用剑刺入他的胸膛时，他笑了。");
	text = text.replace("And he laughs, a final, tired guffaw, as you retrieve your blade.", "当你取回你的利刃时，他笑了，一个最后的，疲倦的大笑。");
	text = text.replace("His eyes fade staring beyond you at a nearby hill where, apparently, the killing joke stands: the soldier\'s bannermen are astride the horizon, having ostensibly seen your deed.", "他的目光越过你凝视着附近的一座小山头，很明显，他知道你的事情败露了：贵族的士兵站在山头上，看到了你的所作所为。");
	text = text.replace(/Shouting, you order the (.*?) to make a hasty retreat lest a whole army bear down on you and slaughter you to a man\./, "你迅速大喊，命令 $1 的同伴们撤退，免得整个敌人大军压过来，把你们杀干净。");
	text = text.replace("In the hurried flight you forego taking any prize for your deed.", "在仓皇逃窜的途中，你放弃了刚刚杀人所获得的奖赏。");
	text = text.replace("A reasonable exchange for keeping your heads on your shoulders, though.", "这样做都是为了能把你的脑袋安稳的放在肩膀上。");
	text = text.replace("With a quick slash of your sword you open the man\'s throat.", "你用剑猛的划开了那个人的喉咙。");
	text = text.replace("He claps his hand over the wound, but his life slips between his fingers quite literally.", "他用手捂住伤口，但是他的生命还是从指缝间悄悄溜走了。");
	text = text.replace(/As he falls over, (.*?) shouts to you\./, "就在他倒下时，$1 向你大喊。");
	text = text.replace("Sir, look!", "先生，快看！");
	text = text.replace("The soldier\'s fellow bannermen are standing on a far hill, no doubt having seen what you just did.", "那个贵族士兵的战友正站在远处的一座小山上，毫无疑问，他们看到了你刚才的所作所为。");
	text = text.replace(/With a quick order, you get the (.*?) on a hurried withdrawal, leaving the area as quick as you can before an entire army bears down on top of you\./, "你迅速命令 $1 开始撤退，在整个军队冲到你们面前之前，尽快离开这个地区。");
	text = text.replace("In the frenzied retreat you have no time to take any prize for your bloody deed.", "在疯狂的撤退中，你没有时间为你的血腥行为拿任何奖品。");

//greenskins_caravan_ambush_event.nut
	text = text.replace("Cresting a small hill, you see a caravan of people along the road.", "在爬一座小山的时候，你看到一队人马正沿着路行进。");
	text = text.replace("They\'re trundling down the path with pots and pans clinking along the wagon sides, children swinging their legs off the edges, women at the front bidding the draught animals forward with sharp whippings.", "他们正沿着小路走着，载重货车边的锅碗瓢盆叮当作响，孩子们把腿从边缘上甩下来，前面的女人用鞭子命令牲口前进。");
	text = text.replace("Men march together, looking at a map and arguing over it, gesticulating in different directions to show a difference in geographic opinion.", "男人们一起走着，看着地图，争论着，朝不同的方向做着手势，表示不同的地理观点。");
	text = text.replace(/And then, further up the road, beyond the travelers\' eyes, are a few goblins laying in the grass\. (.*?) sees them, too, and comments\./, "然后，在路上更远的地方，在这队人马的视线之外，有几个哥布林躺在草地上。$1 也看到他们了，建议。");
	text = text.replace("We\'d best get down there now, sir, before there\'s a slaughter.", "先生，我们最好现在就下去帮忙，免得发生屠杀。");
	//text = text.replace(/(.*?) shrugs\./, "$1 耸了耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("Or... we let the goblins make their move, then we swoop in and clean up the mess.", "或者…我们先让哥布林行动，然后我们再冲进去收拾残局。");
	text = text.replace("Easier to fight them when they\'re tangled up, no?", "在一团糟的情况下，我们的战术优势是很大的，不是吗？");
	
	text = text.replace("You won\'t sacrifice these innocent people for tactical advantage!", "你不会为了战术上的优势而牺牲这些无辜的人！");
	text = text.replace("You order the men to attack now.", "你命令士兵现在就进攻。");
	text = text.replace("The goblins immediately hear you come and turn face.", "哥布林一听到声音就转过身来。");
	text = text.replace("In the distance, the peasants clear out, seeing the danger ahead.", "在远处，农民们看到前方的危险，纷纷撤离。");
	text = text.replace("It appears you\'ve saved them, but now you\'ll have to face the goblins in whole!", "看来你已经救了他们，但现在你必须面对整个哥布林军团！");
	
	text = text.replace("With the goblins taken care of, the peasants slowly bring their wagons back around.", "哥布林们被解决干净后，农民们慢慢地把他们的载重货车拉回来。");
	text = text.replace("They look at the scene with plenty of awe.", "他们敬畏的看着这个场景。");
	text = text.replace("One shakes your hand.", "一个人与你握手。");
	text = text.replace(/By all the old gods, everyone we meet shall hear the name of the (.*?)!/, "敬畏古老的神明，我们会把你们的善行告诉所有人的，$1！");
	text = text.replace("A few others give you food, kisses, and plenty of thanks.", "剩下的人则给了食物、亲吻还有很多感谢。");
	
	text = text.replace("You order the men to wait for the right moment.", "你命令士兵们等待合适的时机。");
	text = text.replace("When the peasants march further down the road, the goblins waylaid them with a volley of poison arrows.", "当农民们沿着大路继续前进时，一群哥布林用一排毒箭拦截了他们。");
	text = text.replace("The arguing men go down, arrows stuck in their chests, muscles stiffening, faces drawn taut as the poison courses through.", "争吵的人们倒下了，箭刺进他们的胸膛，他们肌肉僵硬、面部绷紧、身中剧毒。");
	text = text.replace("A few other men grab the reins from their wives and steer the wagons around.", "其他几个男人从他们的妻子手中夺过缰绳，驾着载重货车打算逃跑。");
	text = text.replace("Some stand guard, a bunch of pitchfork-carrying farmers for a  rearguard, but they don\'t last long in the face of the dishonorable gobbos.", "一些拿着草叉的农夫占了出来，但是他们在哥布林们的突袭面前坚持不了多久。");
	text = text.replace(/Seeing that the goblins are scattered in their attack, you order the (.*?) to begin its own ambush\./, "看见哥布林们已经开始分散进攻，你命令 $1 开始冲锋。");
	
	text = text.replace("The scattered remains of the traveling peasants slowly emerge out of the strewn battlefield.", "战斗结束了。零零散散的农民们从战场的四面八方聚集过来。");
	text = text.replace("An old man shakes your hand.", "一位老人和你握手。");
	text = text.replace("Thank ye, sir, had you not happened upon us we would have all been green-meat!", "谢谢你，先生，如果你我们没有碰巧遇到你，我们就被这些绿皮混球杀光了！");
	text = text.replace("But before he can let your hand go, another, younger man springs over, pointing with a finger.", "但他还没来得及放开你的手，另一个年轻人就冲了过来，用手指指着你。");
	text = text.replace("To hell with that, old man, I saw that bastard up on the hill just watching the whole time!", "胡说八道，老头，我看见山上那个混蛋一直在看！");
	text = text.replace("He left us out as bait!", "他把我们当诱饵！");
	text = text.replace("The old man yanks his hand back.", "老人把手向后一拉。");
	text = text.replace("Well I\'ll be. May you experience all the hells, sellsword!", "好吧，我会的。见鬼去吧，佣兵！");
	text = text.replace("Like you give a shite.", "好像你不在乎这句话似的。");
	text = text.replace("You tell the old man that anything you find is yours.", "你告诉老头子，你找到的任何东西都是你的。");
	text = text.replace("If they want to protest, they can stick their mouth on the end of a blade for all you care.", "如果他们想要抗议，你手上的家伙会劝说他们。");
	
	text = text.replace("One way or another, this isn\'t your problem.", "无论如何，这事情都与你无关。");
	text = text.replace("You quietly leave the scene, though a few brothers are rather disturbed that you left those poor peasants to such a gruesome fate, particularly when the whole realm is trying to survive these green savages.", "你悄悄离开了现场，虽然有几个兄弟很不安，你让那些贫苦的农民遭受了如此可怕的命运，尤其是当整个王国都在试图在这些绿色野蛮人下生存的时候。");

//greenskins_intro_event.nut
	//text = text.replace(/(.*?) enters your tent\./, "$1 进入你的帐篷。");
	text = text.replace("Sir, we got a group of refugees out here that\'d like to talk to you.", "先生，外面有一群难民想和你谈谈。");
	text = text.replace("You set aside your quill pen and go to meet them.", "你把羽毛笔放在一边去见他们。");
	text = text.replace("They\'re an awful mess, looking more like dishrags thrown to the mud than people.", "他们简直是一团糟，看起来更像是被扔到泥里的抹布，而不是人。");
	text = text.replace("One, a man nursing a nub where his hand used to be, steps forward and speaks.", "一个，一个男人抱着一个曾经是他手的地方，走上前说话。");
	text = text.replace("I take it you\'re the one in charge?", "我猜你是这里的头儿？");
	text = text.replace("Nodding, you ask the man what has happened and why it concerns the company.", "你点了点头，随后问他发生了什么，为什么会来找你。");
	text = text.replace("He explains, gesticulating with his one good hand.", "他一边解释，一边用他剩下的一只手做着手势。");
	text = text.replace("The greenskins are attacking.", "那些绿皮开始进攻了。");
	text = text.replace("Well, that\'s nothing new.", "好吧，这不是什么新鲜事。");
	text = text.replace("You ask where they are and if they\'re goblins or orcs.", "你问他们在哪里，他们是哥布林还是兽人。");
	//text = text.replace("The man shakes his head.", "那人摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("Well, see, that\'s just the thing.", "好吧，这就是问题所在。");
	text = text.replace("It\'s both. They\'re... they\'re working together.", "两者都有。他们…他们聚在一起。");
	text = text.replace("Hordes of them as numerous as the blades of grass beneath our feet.", "他们成群结队，就像我们脚下的草叶一样多。");
	text = text.replace("I misspoke, in a way.", "从某种程度上看，我说错了。");
	text = text.replace("What I should have said is that they aren\'t just attacking, they\'re INVADING.", "我应该说的是，他们不仅仅是在攻击，他们是在侵略。");
	text = text.replace("All of them. Together.", "所有的绿皮。一起。");
	text = text.replace("An invasion beyond any scope or measure, don\'t you understand?", "这是一种前所未有的灾难，你还不明白吗？");
	text = text.replace("You look at the crowd of refugees.", "你看着这群难民。");
	text = text.replace("Children huddled beneath the skirts of their mothers, men looking lost. The man continues.", "孩子们蜷缩在母亲的裙子下，男人们看起来很迷茫。这个人接着说。");
	text = text.replace("My father fought in the Battle of Many Names.", "我父亲是一名参加过许多大战役的老兵。");
	text = text.replace("He always did say they\'d come back and now I suppose he\'s right.", "他总是说他们会回来，现在我想他是对的。");
	text = text.replace("We hear the noble houses are panicking and might join forces, lest we all be overrun!", "据说贵族家族惊慌失措，他们可能会为了某些利益联合起来，以免我们都被入侵！");
	text = text.replace("If you want my advice, I say stay out of it.", "如果你需要我的建议，我建议你不要插手。");
	text = text.replace("Those hordes... there\'s no stopping them.", "那些成群结队的…没有什么能阻止他们。");
	text = text.replace("And the things they do...", "他们做的事…");
	text = text.replace("You grab the man by his shirt.", "你抓住他的衬衫。");
	text = text.replace("The things they do don\'t worry me.", "他们做的事我不担心。");
	text = text.replace("Get out of here, peasant, and leave the fighting to the fighters.", "离开这里，农民，把战斗留给战士们去打。");

//greenskins_investigation_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/While you restock your inventory and give the men some rest, the lord of the castle, (.*?), calls for you\./, "当你补充你的货物并让队员们休息的时候，城堡的领主 $1 来找你。");
	text = text.replace("He says that there is a goblin loose in the castle and he wants you to track it down.", "他说城堡里有个哥布林逃跑了，他想让你去追踪它。");
	text = text.replace("I\'d ask my men, but they couldn\'t find their own arses even if they ate their eyes and shat them out.", "我问过我的人了，但是他们蠢的连自己的屁股都找不到，真该挖出他们的眼睛吃了。");
	
	text = text.replace("You search the pantry, opening the door to shelves upon shelves of foodstuffs from cheeses to salted meats to vegetables which dangle from wall hooks.", "你搜索食品储藏室，打开门，看到一层又一层的食品，从奶酪到腌肉，再到挂在墙上挂钩上的蔬菜。");
	text = text.replace("Wickerwork carboys tempt you, but just as you reach out to get a taste a shape darts across your peripheral.", "藤条制成的筐吸引了你，但当你想过去品尝的时候，一个身影从你身边掠过。");
	text = text.replace("You turn, blade in hand, and stab the goblin just as it lunges toward you with a broken bottle.", "你转身，手里拿着利刃，刺向那个拿着破瓶子向你冲来的哥布林。");
	text = text.replace("It dies instantly and makes quite a mess of the floor, ruining a couple bags of flour.", "它马上就死了，把地板弄得一团糟，弄坏了几包面粉。");
	text = text.replace(/The greenskin killed, you calmly drag it to (.*?)\. The nobleman puts his hands to his hips\./, "这个绿皮被杀死了，你冷静地把它拖到 $1 那里。贵族用手拍了拍屁股。");
	text = text.replace("Most impressive, sellsword, but did you have to drag it all the way here?", "非常厉害，佣兵，但你非得一路把它拖到这里来吗？");
	text = text.replace("My servants will have to scrub the floor for weeks!", "我的仆人们将不得不擦洗地板好几个星期！");
	
	text = text.replace("You go down to the pantry and open the door.", "你下楼到食品储藏室去开门。");
	text = text.replace("Inside, you find shelves upon shelves of foods and goods.", "在里面，你发现一个又一个摆满食物和商品的架子。");
	text = text.replace("There also happens to be a man and woman having a good shag in the corner.", "还有一个男人和一个女人在角落里做爱。");
	text = text.replace("They yelp like a couple of pups and cover themselves, the man using a wet flour bag, the woman strategically angling herself behind a shelf of melons.", "他们像一对畜生一样尖叫，并遮住自己的身体，男的用了一个湿面粉包，女的战略性地躲到一个瓜架子后边。");
	text = text.replace("The man clears his throat.", "男人清了清嗓子。");
	text = text.replace(/Please, sir, do not tell (.*?)\./, "求你了，先生，不要告诉 $1。");
	text = text.replace("You were not even aware that this was the nobleman\'s wife, but now it\'s good to know.", "你甚至不知道这是贵族的妻子，但现在很高兴知道了。");
	text = text.replace("The man offers a deal.", "男人提出了一个交易。");
	text = text.replace("Look, I\'m just a stable boy.", "你看，我只是个马童。");
	text = text.replace("I can\'t offer you gold or nothing like that, but a famous jouster is staying here for a week and I can nab you his shield.", "我不能给你金子或者别的什么，但是一个著名的格斗家要在这里呆一个星期，我可以拿他的盾牌给你。");
	text = text.replace("It\'s a right pretty thing and you\'ll love it, I promise.", "这是一件漂亮的东西，我保证你会喜欢的。");
	text = text.replace("All I ask is that you don\'t tell the lord!", "我只请求你不要告诉领主！");
	
	text = text.replace(/This seems as good of a time as any to develop a steady relationship with (.*?), and the best way to go about doing that is absolutely ruining this relationship you\'ve stumbled upon\./, "这似乎是与 $1 建立稳定关系的良机，这也是最好的方法来摧毁刚才那段偶遇促成的关系。");
	text = text.replace(/You return to (.*?)\'s room and report your findings\./, "你回到 $1的房间，报告你的发现。");
	text = text.replace("His face goes red, his knuckles a stark white.", "他的脸变红了，手上青筋暴起。");
	text = text.replace("I figured. I figured. I farkin\' figured!", "我知道了。我知道了。我他妈的知道了！");
	text = text.replace("But the stable boy?", "怎么是那个马童干的？");
	text = text.replace("I will not be so insulted!", "我不会被这样侮辱的！");
	text = text.replace("He snaps his finger to his guards.", "他向他的警卫伸手示意。");
	text = text.replace("Bring me tongs and a blacksmith\'s fire.", "给我拿个铁钳过来，要铁匠烧红的。");
	text = text.replace("Take my \'wife\' to the tower.", "带我的妻子去塔楼。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ll deal with her later.", "我一会儿再收拾她。");
	text = text.replace("And you, sellsword, thank you for bringing this news to me.", "还有你，佣兵，谢谢你把这个消息带给我。");
	text = text.replace("As for the goblin, it\'s been found and taken care of.", "至于哥布林，它已经被找到并处理了。");
	text = text.replace("You need not worry about that no longer.", "你不必再为此担心了。");
	
	text = text.replace("You decide not to tell the nobleman of what is wife is up to.", "你决定不告诉贵族他的妻子做了什么。");
	text = text.replace("The two lovebirds get dressed and hurry out of the pantry, the stable boy pausing to tell you he\'ll have that shield ready when you leave the castle.", "这对小情人穿好衣服，急匆匆地走出食品储藏，马童停下来告诉你，当你离开城堡时，他会把盾牌准备好。");
	text = text.replace("In the meantime, you report to the lord who stays you with a hand.", "与此同时，你要向帮了你一把的领主报告。");
	text = text.replace("Ah, you need not worry yourself any longer, sellsword.", "唉，你不用再为自己担心了，佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("The goblin was found in the stables.", "那个哥布林是在马厩里被发现的。");
	text = text.replace("One of the horses kicked it clear across the barn!", "其中一匹马把它踹出了谷仓！");
	text = text.replace("I\'ll have to reward the stable boy on the soldiering abilities of his steeds!", "我得奖励一下那个马童，你看他的马能当兵！");
	text = text.replace("Hmm, of course.", "哼，当然。");
	text = text.replace("When you leave the castle, the stable boy is there, a suspiciously shield-shaped sack in his hands.", "当你离开城堡时，马童就在那里，手里拿着一个形似盾牌的袋子。");
	text = text.replace("Here, take this. Hurry.", "给你，拿走这个。小心点。");
	text = text.replace("And thanks again, sellsword.", "再次感谢你，佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("You tell him it\'d be best if he kept it in his pants from now on.", "你告诉他最好以后不要再犯。");
	//text = text.replace("He shakes his head.", "他摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("Nah. She\'s worth it.", "不！她值得我这么做。");
	text = text.replace("See you later, sellsword.", "回头见，佣兵。");
	
	text = text.replace("You investigate the halls to see if the little green runt is footing about.", "你调查了大厅，看看这个绿色的小矮子是不是留下了脚印。");
	text = text.replace("Walking down a hallway, you hear the cry of two women come from a nearby room.", "走在走廊上，你听到附近一个房间里传来两个女人的尖叫声。");
	text = text.replace("You draw your sword and barge in.", "你拔出剑闯进来。");
	text = text.replace("A scribe and treasurer are standing atop a desk while a little goblin jumps up and down to try and knife their ankles.", "一个记录员和司库站在办公桌上，一个哥布林跳上跳下，试图用刀割他们的脚踝。");
	text = text.replace("You casually walk in and stab the greenskin through the chest and loft it up like a skewered squirrel.", "你随意地走过去，刺穿它的胸膛，然后把它像串起来的松鼠一样放上去。");
	text = text.replace("The men calm down and thank you for your work. You nod.", "人们冷静下来，感谢你的工作。你点头。");
	text = text.replace("Anytime, ladies.", "随时效劳，女士们。");
	text = text.replace("They clear their throats and offers nervous smiles.", "他们清清嗓子，露出紧张的微笑。");
	text = text.replace(/You head on back to (.*?) and get your pay\./, "你回到 $1 那里，并得到了你的报酬。");
	
	text = text.replace("You figure the halls are as good a place as any to start your search.", "你认为大厅是一个很好的地方，开始你的搜索。");
	text = text.replace("No more than a few twists and turns later do you hear a disturbing noise coming from the treasury.", "仅仅经过几次迂回曲折之后，你就听到从账房传来一阵令人不安的噪音。");
	text = text.replace("Drawing your blade, you ease up next to the door and then shoulder it open, leveling your weapon at whatever may stand on the other side.", "拔出你的利刃，你在门边放松，然后用肩膀把它打开，把你的武器对准任何可能站在另一边的东西。");
	text = text.replace("Instead of a goblin, you find a young and old man who jump in a fright, each with trousers well dropped, and there\'s a tub of slopped butter on the desk against which they had been leaning.", "不是哥布林，而是一个吓得跳起来的年轻人和老人，他们的裤子都掉在地上，他们靠着的办公桌上有一桶洒了的黄油。");
	text = text.replace("The room smells... awful.", "房间里的气味…糟透了。");
	text = text.replace("Dressing themselves, the younger fellow states that he is the treasurer while the elder informs you of his position as scribe.", "穿好裤子，年轻的人说他是司库，而年长的人告诉你他的职位是记录员。");
	text = text.replace("The treasurer quickly offers you a good deal of coin to keep silent about these delicate matters. You laugh.", "司库很快给了你一大堆硬币，让你对这些微妙的事情保持沉默。你大笑。");
	text = text.replace("I won\'t be falling for that trick.", "我不会被这个把戏骗的。");
	text = text.replace("If I take that coin, you simply run along to your lord and tell him I stole it, no?", "如果我拿了这些硬币，你就跑去告诉你的主人是我偷的，不是吗？");
	text = text.replace("What better way to protect yourself than to ensure my execution?", "还有什么比确保我被判死刑更能保护你们自己呢？");
	text = text.replace("The treasurer retreats and the scribe steps forward.", "司库后退，记录员走上前。");
	text = text.replace("He is an elderly man who smells of arse and candlewax.", "他是个上了年纪的人，身上有股蜡味。");
	text = text.replace("In my repository, I have many things which are owned by me, not my lord.", "在我的宝库中，有许多属于我自己的东西，而不是属于我的主人。");
	text = text.replace("These items might be of great interest to you.", "这些东西你可能会很感兴趣。");
	text = text.replace("Potions, drinks, goods which a fighting man such as yourself could make use of.", "有药剂，饮品，还有一些像你这样的战士能用到的东西。");
	text = text.replace("And... and I\'ll throw in a wardog!", "还有…我还会奉上一条战犬！");
	text = text.replace("A local houndmaster owes me a favor and now is as good of a time as any to call upon it!", "一个本地的驯兽师欠我一个人情，现在正是去拜访他的好时机！");
	text = text.replace("The scribe laughs nervously as you mull the idea over.", "当你仔细考虑这个想法时，记录员紧张地笑了。");
	text = text.replace("If you turned them in, who knows what may happen.", "如果你把他们交上去，谁知道会发生什么事。");
	text = text.replace("Sodomites bother you none, but there are lords across the realm who consider such fornications to be abhorrent.", "肛交者这种事你漠不关心，但全国各地的领主都认为这种淫乱是可耻的。");
	text = text.replace(/If (.*?) is such a fellow, you might gain favor by \'rooting\' these men out\./, "如果 $1 是这样的家伙，你可能通过“揪出”这两个人来获得好感。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You close the closet door and hurry to (.*?)\. You explain to the nobleman what you\'ve seen\./, "你关上房间的门，急忙奔向 $1。你向贵族解释你所看到的。");
	text = text.replace("When you finish, he states that the goblin had been found drowning in a sewage stream and has been put out of its misery.", "当你讲完的时候，他说那个哥布林被发现淹死在一条污水沟里，现在已经脱离了它的痛苦。");
	text = text.replace("As for the sodomites, yes, what of it?", "至于肛交者，是有，那又怎样呢？");
	text = text.replace("Have you looked around?", "你四处看看了吗？");
	text = text.replace("A fort is a nonsensical place to the urges of a man.", "城堡这种环境会使人产生荒谬的欲望。");
	text = text.replace("Swingin\' dicks as far as the eye can see and nowhere to put them.", "在目所能及的地方全是坚挺的鸡巴，没有地方释放它们。");
	text = text.replace("Do I like it? No, of course not.", "我喜欢吗？不，当然不是。");
	text = text.replace("Absolutely disgusting nonsense, truly.", "绝对是恶心的存在，真的。");
	text = text.replace("But if I punished every instance of this behavior I\'d be left with a bunch of scarecrows and farm animals, and I can\'t even be sure of the latter.", "但如果我惩罚每一个这样的行为，我会留下一堆稻草人和农场牲畜，我甚至不能确定后者。");
	text = text.replace("He waves you off.", "他挥手叫你走开。");
	text = text.replace("The goblin\'s been taken care of, sellsword, I\'ve little else to speak to you about.", "哥布林的事儿已经处理好了，佣兵，我没有什么别的话要对你说。");
	text = text.replace("However, if you could, please inform the servants that the room in which you found them needs cleaning.", "不过，如果可以的话，请告诉仆人们，你找到他们的那个房间需要打扫。");
	text = text.replace("I care not to look over taxes in a smog of shite.", "我不想在一团屎雾中查看税收。");
	
	text = text.replace("You decide to keep their secret under the pretense that the scribe will give you what he has promised.", "你决定把他们的秘密隐藏起来，假设记录员会给你他所承诺的。");
	text = text.replace("The old man nods as you leave.", "你离开时，老人点了点头。");
	text = text.replace("I will find you in the courtyard, sellsword, with everything that you are owed.", "我会在院子里等你，佣兵，还有你欠的一切。");
	text = text.replace("Your silence on this matter is most appreciated.", "非常感谢你对这件事保持沉默。");
	text = text.replace(/When you return to (.*?), he explains that the goblin had been found and taken care of\./, "当你回到 $1 那里时，解释说哥布林已经找到并处理了。");
	text = text.replace("Seeing as how you weren\'t responsible, he sends you off without pay.", "鉴于你不负责任，他把你白白地打发走了。");
	text = text.replace("Outside, the scribe does in fact meet you.", "在外面，记录员确实等着你。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s got a leash in one hand and a sack in the other.", "他一只手牵着绳子，另一只手拿着袋子。");
	text = text.replace("He hands them both over.", "他把这些都交给你了。");
	text = text.replace("Once again, my thanks, sellsword.", "再次向你表示感谢，佣兵。");
	
	text = text.replace("If you were a goblin in a castle of people wanting to kill you, where would you go?", "如果你是城堡里被追杀的哥布林，你会去哪里？");
	text = text.replace("Putting yourself in the mind of the runt, you come to the conclusion that the armory would be as good a place as any to start your search.", "把你自己想象成一个小不点，你会得出结论，武器库将是你开始搜寻的最佳地点。");
	text = text.replace("When you get there, you do find an apprentice standing outside and trying to hold the door shut.", "当你到了那里，你发现一个学徒站在门外，试图把门关上。");
	text = text.replace("He yells that the goblin is inside and has already killed the blacksmith.", "他大叫地说哥布林在里面，并且已经杀死了铁匠。");
	text = text.replace("Drawing your blade, you tell the apprentice to stand aside.", "拔出你的利刃，你让学徒站到一边。");
	text = text.replace("The second he does, the door bursts open and a goblin, shaped like a scarecrow built out of broken buckets, shambles out, armored head-to-toe, a shield and spear clumsily stationed at its front.", "又一次的，门就被撞开了，一个像破桶做的稻草人模样的哥布林跌跌撞撞地走了出来，从头到脚全副武装，前面笨拙地拿着盾牌和长矛。");
	text = text.replace("Ignoring the absurdity of what is being seen, you strike through the clutter and pierce the beast\'s skull, instantly killing it.", "无视所见的荒谬，你趁乱而上，刺穿这个畜生的头颅，立刻杀死它。");
	text = text.replace("When you withdraw your sword, all the armor and weapons fall away as though you\'d just slain an apparition holding them up.", "当你拔出剑的时候，所有的盔甲和武器都掉了下来，就好像你杀死了一个举着它们的幽灵。");
	text = text.replace("The apprentice quickly shakes your hand before falling to his knees, weeping over the loss of the blacksmith.", "学徒很快握了握你的手，然后跪倒在地，为失去铁匠而哭泣。");
	text = text.replace(/With no time for tears, you take the goblin\'s head and return to (.*?) for your pay\./, "没时间流眼泪了，你拿着哥布林的头，回到 $1 那里领取奖赏。");
	
	text = text.replace("Well, if you were a tiny dwarf in a hostile fortress the first place you\'d go is the armory.", "好吧，如果你是敌方要塞里的一个小矮人，你首先要去的地方就是武器库。");
	text = text.replace("When you get there, you don\'t find any goblin, but instead there\'s a kid drawing a dagger out of a man who is face down on the floor.", "当你到达那里时，你没有发现任何哥布林，而是有一个小孩从一个面朝下趴在地板上的人身上拔出匕首。");
	text = text.replace("The murderer drops his weapon and holds his hands up.", "凶手丢下武器，举起双手。");
	text = text.replace("I had no choice!", "我别无选择！");
	text = text.replace("No choice at all!", "没的选择！");
	text = text.replace("You ask the kid who he and the dead man are. He quickly explains.", "你问那孩子他和那死人是谁。他很快解释道。");
	text = text.replace("I\'m the apprentice and this is... was the blacksmith.", "我是学徒，这是…是铁匠。");
	text = text.replace("Now, this had to be done. Had to!", "现在，这是不得不做的。不得不！");
	text = text.replace("You\'ve no idea what horrors this man has put upon me!", "你不知道这个人把我搞得多惨！");
	text = text.replace("Every time I errored, he punished me as though I was a kingslaying cretin! See this?", "每次我犯错，他就惩罚我，好像我是一个弑君的白痴！看到了吗？");
	text = text.replace("He sweeps a length of hair out of the way, revealing the bulbous scars of burns.", "他拨开一缕头发，露出烧伤的球根状伤疤。");
	text = text.replace("Letting go of the hair, he holds up a hand with a grotesque pinky that rests at a right angle, and the other hand which has no pinky at all.", "他松开头发，举起一只手，那只手的小指怪怪的，呈直角，另一只手完全没有小指。");
	text = text.replace("He starts taking a boot off, but you stop him, getting the point.", "他开始脱靴子，但你阻止了他，明白了重点。");
	text = text.replace("The apprentice clasps his hands together, his pinky sticking out like a haughty highborn sipping wine.", "学徒双手紧握在一起，他的小指伸出来，就像一个高傲的贵族在啜饮美酒。");
	text = text.replace("You\'re after the goblin, right?", "你在找哥布林，对吗？");
	text = text.replace("Just tell them the goblin did it!", "告诉他们是哥布林干的！");
	text = text.replace("I\'ll... look, I\'m not much of an armorer, but I can forge a sword like nobody\'s business and I will forge you the absolute best that I can do.", "我会…听着，我不是一个很好的武器制造者，但是我可以打造一把无人能及的剑，而且我会尽我所能打造给你。");
	text = text.replace("Just keep this secret between us, that\'s all I ask.", "我只要求你我之间保守这个秘密。");
	
	text = text.replace("You close the door and lock it, ensuring that the murderer will not be able to flee.", "你关上门，锁上，确保凶手不能逃跑。");
	text = text.replace("As the apprentice screams and bangs against the door, you return to the nobleman.", "随着学徒的尖叫和门上的砰砰声，你回到了贵族那里。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) listens to your report and nods\./, "$1 听了你的报告，点了点头。");
	text = text.replace("Mmhmm, yes. The blacksmith is not the first to fall by that boy\'s hand - we\'ve had a series of murders here, but have never been able to find the culprit.", "嗯哼，是的。铁匠不是第一个被那个男孩杀死的－我们这里发生了一连串的谋杀案，但始终没能找到罪犯。");
	text = text.replace("Many believed it him on account of his bashing his hands with hammers and putting his face to a torch.", "许多人相信他，因为他用锤子敲打他的手，把他的脸放在火把上。");
	text = text.replace("The stable boy even saw him cut the cock off a rat.", "马童甚至看到他割下一只老鼠的鸡鸡。");
	text = text.replace("He was a disturbed fellow, but now you\'ve given us definitive proof of his doings.", "他是个精神失常的人，但你现在给了我们他所作所为的确凿证据。");
	text = text.replace("Well done, sellsword! The goblin you were after has already been taken care of, but this... this is far better than hunting down some greenskin.", "很出色，佣兵！你要找的那个哥布林已经被干掉了，但是这个…这比捕猎一些绿皮要好得多。");
	text = text.replace("Consider your payment doubled!", "鉴于此你的报酬加倍！");
	text = text.replace("The nobleman snaps his fingers at his scribe and starts uttering orders, ostensibly issuing a writ of execution.", "贵族朝他的记录员打了个响指，然后开始发出命令，表面上是发出执行令。");
	text = text.replace("He goes into incredible detail about the logistics of the matter: horses, ropes, blades, tongs, hot fires, a litany of horrors to keep bored soldiers entertained for hours.", "他不可思议地长篇大论来描述事件的后勤保障：马匹，绳子，刀片，钳子，火堆，以及一长串让无聊的士兵们高兴几个小时的恐怖场景。");

//greenskins_outro_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/You come across a handful of soldiers from (.*?)\. They tilt their caps at you\./, "你遇到一些来自 $1 的士兵。他们扭头看向你。");
	text = text.replace("Evening, mercenaries.", "晚上好，雇佣兵。");
	text = text.replace(/Not sure if they\'re about to attack, you make a subtle nod toward (.*?)\. He puts his weapon within hand\'s reach and nods back\./, "不确定他们是否要进攻，你对 $1 微微点头。他把武器放在伸手可及的地方，点了点头。");
	text = text.replace("You return your attention to the soldiers, giving them a friendly wave.", "你把注意力转移到这些士兵身上，友好地向他们挥手致意。");
	text = text.replace("Their lieutenant steps forward, grinning.", "他们的军官走上前来，嗤笑道。");
	text = text.replace("Oy\' mercenary, we\'ve little use for you in this world now.", "哦，雇佣兵，你们对我们还有点用处。");
	text = text.replace("Slowly, you lower your hand, hovering it above the pommel of your sword.", "慢慢地，你放下你的手，把它悬在剑柄上。");
	text = text.replace("You ask what the man means by that. He laughs.", "你问这个人那是什么意思。他笑着说。");
	text = text.replace("You haven\'t heard? War\'s over.", "你没听说么？战争结束了。");
	text = text.replace(/The greenskins were routed from (.*?) just a few days ago\./, "绿皮已经在 $1 溃败了，就在几天前。");
	text = text.replace("Scouts report seeing them bastards running for the hills every which way, fighting amongst themselves, the orcs killing the goblins, goblins killing the orcs, just a full on rout.", "侦察兵报告说看到他们这些混蛋到处往山上跑，互相厮杀，兽人杀哥布林，哥布林杀兽人，溃不成军。");
	text = text.replace("So, yeah, noble houses need not pay your sorry arse for nothing now because us real soldiers got it under control.", "所以，是的，贵族家族现在不需要为你的屁股付钱了，因为我们这些真正战士已经控制住局面了。");
	text = text.replace("Now why don\'t you and your pathetic lot clear out of the way.", "现在你和你那群可怜虫为什么不让开。");
	text = text.replace("Us fighters got places to be, understand?", "我们这些战士在行军，明白吗？");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) reaches for his weapon, but you shake your head\./, "$1 伸手去拿武器，你却摇摇头。");
	text = text.replace("The lieutenant nods toward the mercenary.", "军官朝雇佣兵们点了点头。");
	text = text.replace("Best keep that dog on its leash, aye?", "最好拴着那条狗，明白吗？");
	text = text.replace("You fan your arm out, inviting the soldiers a \'passage\' they knew they already had.", "你张开双臂，邀请士兵们“通过”一条他们知道已经走过的通道。");
	text = text.replace("The soldiers gear up and the lieutenant smirks.", "士兵们整装待发，军官得意地笑了。");
	text = text.replace("I knew you\'d make the right choice.", "我知道你会做出正确的选择。");
	text = text.replace("We\'re just \'aving a bit of fun, yeah?", "我们只是想找点乐子，是吗？");
	text = text.replace("You ladies stay tight.", "你们这些小妞站好。");
	text = text.replace(/The man blows a kiss as he walks by\. (.*?) stands up looking like someone just socked his mother\./, "那个男人在经过时飞吻了一下。$1 站起来，就像有人打了他的母亲。");
	text = text.replace("You tell him to sit back down and he begrudgingly does so.", "你让他坐回去，他很不情愿地坐了下来。");
	text = text.replace("It\'s all bullshit, these theatrics, but you\'re not one to lose your temper and get people killed over it.", "这些表演全是狗屁，但你不是那种会发脾气，让人送命的人。");
	text = text.replace("The incident does make you wonder if maybe it\'s time to turn it all in.", "这件事确实让你怀疑是不是该把一切都结束了。");
	text = text.replace("The greenskins are beaten back and you\'ve made enough money to leave the life for good, but then again you\'d hate to live out the rest of your days wondering \'what if\'...", "绿皮被打败了，你赚了足够的钱，可以永远离开这个世界了，但是你也不愿意余生都活在对“如果…”的疑惑中。");
	text = text.replace("You\'ve won! Battle Brothers is designed for replayability and for campaigns to be played until you\'ve beaten one or two late game crises.", "你已经胜利了！战场兄弟是为可重玩性和战役而设计的，直到你在游戏后期打败了一两次危机。");
	text = text.replace("Starting a new campaign will allow you to try out different things in a different world.", "开始一个新的战役会让你在不同的世界尝试不同的东西。");
	text = text.replace("That said, you can choose to continue your campaign for as long as you want.", "也就是说，你可以选择继续你的战役，只要你想。");
	text = text.replace("Just be aware that campaigns are not intended to last forever and you\'re likely to run out of challenges eventually.", "只是要意识到，战役并不是要永远持续下去的，你可能最终会尝尽所有的挑战。");
	
	text = text.replace("The soldiers\' lieutenant glares at you.", "士兵们的军官瞪着你。");
	text = text.replace("Do as I said, sellsword, or there will be trouble.", "照我说的去做，佣兵，否则会有麻烦的。");
	text = text.replace(/Ignoring him, you give another nod to (.*?)\. He gets up, the blade of his weapon loudly scraping off the dirt\./, "你不理他，又对 $1 点了点头。他站了起来，他的刀锋响亮地甩掉了灰尘。");
	text = text.replace("The soldiers turn to the mercenary.", "士兵们转向这个雇佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("He hefts his weapon into both hands and stares back.", "他双手捧起武器，回头看着。");
	text = text.replace(/As the lieutenant starts to talk, (.*?) bluntly interrupts\./, "当军官开始说话时，$1 直言不讳地打断了他。");
	text = text.replace("Shush, little man. I see softness in your skin.", "嘘，小家伙。我看到你皮肤柔软。");
	text = text.replace("Not a scar to be seen.", "看不出有什么伤痕。");
	text = text.replace("Eyes as fresh as the day they were born.", "眼睛和出生时一样新鲜。");
	text = text.replace("Hands as smooth as untouched candles.", "手就像没碰过的蜡烛一样光滑。");
	text = text.replace("If you was of the fightin\' sort, you\'d be out there in those battles you speak of, not out here pissing into the wind.", "如果你是那种喜欢战斗的人，你就会出现在你所提到的那些战斗中，而不是在这里的空气中小便。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ll give you two options because I\'m feeling nice.", "我给你两个选择，因为我感觉很好。");
	text = text.replace("First option, are you listening?", "第一个选择，你在听吗？");
	text = text.replace("First option is this.", "第一种选择是这样的。");
	text = text.replace("Go where you are going and don\'t say another goddam word.", "去你要去的地方，别再说一句该死的话。");
	text = text.replace("He pauses to hold up two fingers.", "他停下来举起两根手指。");
	text = text.replace("Option two is a mystery.", "选项二是一个谜。");
	text = text.replace("Speak and ye shall learn of it.", "说出来，你就会学到的。");
	text = text.replace("The lieutenant\'s eyes have gotten a little wider, and his mouth infinitely quieter.", "军官的眼睛睁得更大了，嘴巴也安静多了。");
	text = text.replace("He glances at you, but all you can do is shrug.", "他瞥了你一眼，但你只能耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("After another moment, the soldiers hurry away with determined silence.", "又过了一会儿，士兵们带着绝对的沉默匆匆离去。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) laughs it up, but the incident has you wondering if perhaps it is finally the time to retire\./, "$1 哈哈大笑，但是这件事让你怀疑是不是该退休了。");
	text = text.replace("How many more of these cockups are in your future?", "你的未来还会有多少这样的错误？");
	text = text.replace("How many more battles?", "还要打多少仗？");
	text = text.replace("How many more dead men will you have to bury?", "你还要埋葬多少死人？");
	text = text.replace("The company would do well standing on the foundations you\'ve built for it.", "战队会在你为它建立的基础上做得很好。");
	text = text.replace("But on the other hand, if you retired now, what adventures would you miss out on?", "但另一方面，如果你现在退休了，你会错过什么冒险呢？");
	text = text.replace("You\'ve won! Battle Brothers is designed for replayability and for campaigns to be played until you\'ve beaten one or two late game crises.", "你已经胜利了！战场兄弟是为可重玩性和战役而设计的，直到你在游戏后期打败了一两次危机。");
	text = text.replace("Starting a new campaign will allow you to try out different things in a different world.", "开始一个新的战役会让你在不同的世界尝试不同的东西。");
	text = text.replace("That said, you can choose to continue your campaign for as long as you want.", "也就是说，你可以选择继续你的战役，只要你想。");
	text = text.replace("Just be aware that campaigns are not intended to last forever and you\'re likely to run out of challenges eventually.", "只是要意识到，战役并不是要永远持续下去的，你可能最终会尝尽所有的挑战。");

//greenskins_pet_goblin_event.nut
	text = text.replace("While walking through the forest, you come into a clearing where a small little hut sits.", "当你穿过森林时，你来到一片空地上，那里有一间小茅屋。");
	text = text.replace("There are bear traps hanging from its walls, squirrel pelts from the eaves, and the windows are dressed with wet leaves in their corners.", "墙上挂着捕熊器，屋檐上挂着松鼠皮，窗户的角落里挂满了湿漉漉的树叶。");
	text = text.replace("An old man is on the porch, rocking in his chair.", "一位老人坐在门廊上的椅子上摇来摇去。");
	text = text.replace("He has a crossbow aimed at you.", "他拿着一把弩瞄准你。");
	text = text.replace("This is my property.", "这是我的财产。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s a chain running from the arm of his chair to a hatch on the bottom of the cabin door.", "有一条链子从他的椅子扶手一直延伸到地窖的门口。");
	text = text.replace("It moves slightly to the man\'s speaking and he turns and butts the crossbow against the door.", "它随着那个人的谈话轻微地移动了一下，那个人转过身，用那把弩顶着门。");
	text = text.replace("Hush, you! Now you, man with the sword, and all yer friends, get going.", "嘘,你！现在你，拿着剑的人，和你所有的朋友，走吧。");
	text = text.replace("Another the step the wrong way, which would be my way, and I\'ll put a bolt up yer arse.", "如果再走错一步，在我的地盘，我就把你的屁股拴起来。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) eases up to your side\./, "$1 悄悄来到你身边。");
	text = text.replace("What should we do, sir?", "我们该怎么做，先生？");
	
	text = text.replace("You\'ve no reason to further transgress upon this old man\'s day, and so you tell the company to give him and his hut a wide berth.", "你没有理由再冒犯这位老人，所以你让大家离他和他的小屋远点。");
	text = text.replace("The elder eyes you suspiciously every step of the way.", "老人用怀疑的目光看着你前进的每一步。");
	text = text.replace("Mmhmm, y\'all have a good day now.", "嗯哼，你们现在都有美好的一天了。");
	text = text.replace("You nod and respond.", "你点头回应。");
	text = text.replace("Yeah, you too.", "好的，你也一样。");
	text = text.replace("The chain moves again and is met with another hushing.", "链条又动了一下，发出了另一个声音。");
	text = text.replace("Who knows what the hell was going on here, but the company has places to be.", "谁知道这到底是怎么回事，但战队有它自己的任务。");
	
	text = text.replace("You take a step forward.", "你向前迈了一步。");
	text = text.replace("The old man springs off his chair and spits.", "老人从椅子上一跃而起，吐了一口唾沫。");
	text = text.replace("Sonuvabitch.", "混蛋。");
	text = text.replace("He lifts the crossbow and shoots it from the hip.", "他举起那把弩，蹲着射了出去。");
	text = text.replace(/The shot goes wide and into the trees where it clacks and clatters off branches and shrubs\. (.*?) rushes the porch and tackles the man to the ground\./, "弩矢很沉重，射进了树林，树枝和灌木噼啪作响。$1 冲进门廊，把男人扑倒在地。");
	text = text.replace("Get your whoremongering hands off me you, you, you whoremonger!", "把你那淫荡的手拿开，你，你个贱货！");
	text = text.replace("While the man spits and kicks, you calmly walk up to the porch and open the door to his hut.", "当那个人又啐又踢的时候，你平静地走到门廊，打开他小屋的门。");
	text = text.replace("The chain shoots across the floorboards and goes taut.", "链子沿着地板，绷紧了。");
	text = text.replace("A dark shape takes to the corner, scuttling up its walls trying to get further than its shackles will allow.", "一个黑暗的身影出现在角落里，在它的镣铐所能允许的范围内，迅速爬上墙壁。");
	text = text.replace("You take a torch and wave it into the darkness.", "你拿起火把，在黑暗中挥舞。");
	text = text.replace("There you see the prisoner.", "你看到那个囚犯了吗。");
	text = text.replace("The old man shouts from the porch.", "老人在门廊里大喊。");
	text = text.replace("You leave us alone!", "你别来烦我们！");
	text = text.replace("Go on now, you leave us alone!", "现在就走，你别管我们");
	text = text.replace("There, shrinking away from your torch, is a goblin.", "在那里，正在躲闪火把的，是个哥布林。");
	
	text = text.replace("You take a step forward.", "你向前迈了一步。");
	text = text.replace("The old man springs off his chair and spits.", "老人从椅子上一跃而起，吐了一口唾沫。");
	text = text.replace("Sonsabitches, I warned ye!", "混蛋，我警告过你们！");
	text = text.replace("I warned ye good and clear!", "我警告过你们要小心！");
	text = text.replace("He lifts the crossbow and shoots it from the hip.", "他举起那把弩，蹲着射了出去。");
	text = text.replace(/The shot sails over your shoulder and shoots clear through (.*?)\'s arm\./, "弩矢飞过你的肩膀，穿过 $1的手臂。");
	text = text.replace("The sellsword looks down, a feather of a shot teetering from one end of the hole, a bloodied shaft wiggling from the other.", "佣兵往下看，一根弩矢的羽毛从伤口的一端摇摇欲坠，一根血淋淋的箭杆从另一端抖动着。");
	text = text.replace("He takes a seat.", "他坐了下来。");
	text = text.replace("Well fark me.", "我操。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) screams and rushes ahead\./, "$1 尖叫着向前冲。");
	text = text.replace("As the old man tries to reload, the mercenary kicks the crossbow away and throws the shooter to the ground.", "当老人试图重新装填弹药时，雇佣兵把弩踢开，把射手掀翻在地。");
	text = text.replace("You tell the sellsword to keep the man alive.", "你告诉佣兵留他一命。");
	text = text.replace("While the man spits and kicks, you calmly walk up to the porch and open the door to his hut.", "当那个人又啐又踢的时候，你平静地走到门廊，打开他小屋的门。");
	text = text.replace("As the door swings wide, the chain shoots across the floorboards and goes taut.", "当门开得很大时，链子沿着地板，绷紧了。");
	text = text.replace("A dark shape takes to the corner, scuttling up its walls trying to go further than its shackles will allow.", "一个黑暗的身影出现在角落里，在它的镣铐所能允许的范围内，迅速爬上墙壁。");
	text = text.replace("You take a torch and wave it into the darkness.", "你拿起火把，在黑暗中挥舞。");
	text = text.replace("There you see the prisoner.", "你看到那个囚犯了吗。");
	text = text.replace("The old man shouts from the porch.", "老人在门廊里大喊。");
	text = text.replace("You leave us alone!", "你别来烦我们！");
	text = text.replace("Go on now, you leave us alone!", "现在就走，你别管我们！");
	text = text.replace("There, shrinking away from your torch, is a goblin.", "在那里，正在躲闪火把的，是个哥布林。");
	
	text = text.replace("You take out your sword and step into the cabin.", "你拿出剑，走进地窖。");
	text = text.replace("The old man calls out to you.", "那个老人大声呼唤你。");
	text = text.replace("All the threat and posturing is gone.", "所有的威胁和傲慢都消失了。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s almost manically pleading for you to not hurt the goblin.", "他近乎疯狂地恳求你不要伤害那个哥布林。");
	text = text.replace("But you do just that, thrusting a blade through the greenskin\'s chest.", "但你就是这么做的，用一把利刃刺穿绿皮的胸膛。");
	text = text.replace("It heaves against the metal, gripping it with its slimy, disgusting fingers.", "它用它那黏糊糊令人作呕的手指抓住金属。");
	text = text.replace("Its grip weakens as the light leaves its eyes.", "它的抓地力减弱了，正如他的眼睛失去了光芒。");
	text = text.replace("You draw out the blade and wipe the blood on your pants.", "你拔出利刃，把你裤子上的血擦干净。");
	text = text.replace("As though grief renewed him with unseen power, the old man cries out and manages to wrestle to his feet.", "悲伤仿佛以一种看不见的力量使他恢复了活力，老人大哭，挣扎着站了起来。");
	text = text.replace(/He draws a dagger and comes after you, but (.*?) stops him with a dagger of his own, bedding the blade just beneath the man\'s breast\./, "他抽出一把匕首跟在你后面，但是 $1 用自己的匕首阻止了他，把匕首插进了他的胸膛。");
	text = text.replace("Blood spews over the hilt as his heart rapidly beats the last of its life.", "血从刀柄上喷涌而出，他的心脏在急促地跳动，生命的最后一刻。");
	text = text.replace("The old man\'s knees buckle and slides down, clutching at his killer\'s arms.", "老人双膝发软，倒了下去，紧紧抓住凶手的手臂。");
	text = text.replace("Cruel creatures... cruel...", "残忍的生物…残忍…");
	text = text.replace("He collapses onto the floorboard.", "他在地板上断气。");
	text = text.replace("You tell the company to search the cabin and take what they can.", "你命令战队竭尽所能地搜查地窖。");
	
	text = text.replace("Keeping the goblin in sight at all times, you ask the man why he has a greenskin tied up in his cabin.", "一直盯着哥布林，你问他为什么把一个绿皮绑在他的小屋里。");
	text = text.replace("The hermit cries into the floorboards.", "隐士对着地板哭泣。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s a friend! My only friend!", "他是一个朋友！我惟一的朋友！");
	
	text = text.replace("You retreat from the cabin and crouch before the old man.", "你从木屋里撤退，蹲在老人面前。");
	text = text.replace("He wriggles and begs.", "他挣扎着乞求着。");
	text = text.replace("Please, don\'t kill \'im!", "求你，不要杀了他！");
	text = text.replace("The man has gone mad and you tell him as much.", "那人疯了，你也得跟他沟通。");
	text = text.replace("He sobs into the porch floorboards, his breath powdering sawdust into the air.", "他对着门廊的地板抽泣着，呼出的气把木屑吹向空中。");
	text = text.replace("Finally, he eases his breathing and calms down.", "最后，他放松呼吸，平静下来。");
	text = text.replace("Yer right. I\'m not all there in the head.", "你们是对的。我脑子不太清醒。");
	text = text.replace("I found the goblin in a trap a few days ago and took him in, healed him.", "几天前我在一个陷阱里找到了那个哥布林，把他抓了起来，治好了他。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ve no company in these parts.", "在这些地方我没有同伴。");
	text = text.replace("It gets lonely, you understand.", "很孤独，你懂的。");
	text = text.replace("You take and reload the crossbow and then offer it to the old man.", "你把那把弩装上子弹，然后把它交给老人。");
	text = text.replace("Can you do it?", "你能做到吗？");
	text = text.replace("The old man stares at the crossbow.", "老人凝视着那把弩。");
	text = text.replace("He blinks a number of times and nods.", "他眨了几下眼睛，点了点头。");
	text = text.replace("Your sellswords let him up.", "你的佣兵们放开他。");
	text = text.replace("He takes the crossbow and steps into the cabin.", "他拿着弩走进小屋。");
	text = text.replace("His aim is shaky and he\'s muttering apologies under his breath.", "他的瞄准并不坚定，嘴里还嘟囔着道歉的话。");
	text = text.replace("The goblin is curled into a ball, shielding itself with its sickly hands.", "哥布林蜷成一团，用它那病态的手保护着自己。");
	text = text.replace("I\'m so sorry. So very sorry.", "我对不起你。非常抱歉。");
	text = text.replace("The old man readies the crossbow\'s release, slides his finger over the trigger, and then puts the bolt beneath his chin and fires.", "老人准备好弩的射击，将手指滑过扳机，然后将弩矢对准他的下巴开火。");
	text = text.replace("He buckles to the floor, the shot twanging as it slams into the ceiling, scant blood dripping off its feathers.", "他扣动扳机，弩矢砰的一声落在天花板上，稀稀落落的鲜血从羽毛上滴落下来。");
	text = text.replace("You shake your head and step into the cabin and kill the goblin off yourself.", "你摇摇头，走进小屋，亲手杀死了哥布林。");
	text = text.replace("Finished, you tell the men to search the hut and take what they can.", "完事后，你告诉队员们去搜查那间小屋，尽他们所能把东西拿走。");
	
	text = text.replace("Cautiously, you go back to the old man.", "小心翼翼地，你回到老人身边。");
	text = text.replace("You pick up the chain and rankle it, asking the man.", "你拿起铁链去激怒它，问那个人。");
	text = text.replace("A friend you keep shackled?", "一个被你束缚的朋友？");
	text = text.replace("If it were your true friend, you wouldn\'t need the chains, no?", "如果他是你真正的朋友，你就不需要锁链了，不是吗？");
	text = text.replace("The hermit shrugs.", "隐士耸耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("Yer right. Lemme go and I\'ll prove to you he\'s a real friend.", "你们是对的。让我去，我要向你证明他是一个真正的朋友。");
	text = text.replace("You let the man up and tell him to \'prove\' it.", "你让那个人站起来，让他“证明”一下。");
	text = text.replace("He pats the dust off his clothes and steps into the cabin.", "他拍拍衣服上的灰尘，走进地窖。");
	text = text.replace("The chain slackens a bit as the goblin takes a step away from the fall.", "链条稍稍松了一点，哥布林在他蜷曲的地方退了一步。");
	text = text.replace("Crouching before the greenskin, the hermit extends a hand.", "隐士蹲在这个绿皮面前，伸出一只手。");
	text = text.replace("Hey there, buddy.", "嘿，伙计。");
	text = text.replace("As he reaches to unshackle the greenskin, the goblin growls and launches forward, sinking its teeth into the man\'s face.", "当他试图解开绿皮的枷锁时，哥布林咆哮着向前冲去，用牙齿咬住了他的脸。");
	text = text.replace("You rush into the cabin and kick the goblin back.", "你冲进小木屋，把哥布林踢了回去。");
	text = text.replace(/It lands against the corner, flesh and blood hanging from its lips. (.*?) stabs a sword through the creature\'s face\./, "它落在墙角上，血肉挂在它的嘴唇上。$1 用剑刺穿这个畜生的脸。");
	text = text.replace("The old man cries out, his face a visage of gore.", "老人喊了一声，满脸是血。");
	text = text.replace("You were right, I knew it true, but my heart... it\'s in so much pain.", "你是对的，我知道这是真的，但是我的心…太痛苦了。");
	text = text.replace("Getting a better look, you now see a seeping crimson chasm where his nose should be.", "仔细一看，你发现他的鼻子处有一个深红色的伤口。");
	text = text.replace("As the hermit crawls into a ball, he points across the cabin.", "隐士蜷缩着像一个球，他指了指小屋。");
	text = text.replace("Beneath the floorboards there, where the dust is unsettled.", "在地板下面，尘土很多。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ve no use for it anymore.", "我已经不再需要它了。");
	text = text.replace(/You nod and tell (.*?) to fix the man up\./, "你点了点头，告诉 $1 去给隐士包扎。");
	text = text.replace("The rest of the company starts ripping out the floorboards to look beneath the crawlspace.", "战队的其他人开始拆地板，看看下面的隐藏空间。");
	text = text.replace("After getting what they need, you tell the men it\'s time to leave.", "在得到他们需要的东西后，你告诉他们是时候离开了。");
	text = text.replace("The hermit returns to his rocking chair and takes a seat.", "隐士回到他的摇椅上坐下。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s got his hands face up on his knees, blood running down the lengths of the fingers, and more blood dripping from a wound that is sure to fester.", "他把双手仰起放在膝盖上，鲜血沿着手指流了下来，更多的血从一个肯定会溃烂的伤口流出来。");
	text = text.replace("You can hear the blood choking him on every breath.", "你能听到他每一次呼吸都被血呛到。");
	text = text.replace("I should\'ve hidden away.", "我应该藏起来的。");
	text = text.replace("That\'s what I always do.", "那是我经常做的事。");
	text = text.replace("Why didn\'t I hide?", "为什么我没有藏起来？");
	
	text = text.replace("You back out of the cabin and yell at the man.", "你从地窖里出来，对着那个人大喊。");
	text = text.replace("What in the old hells do you think you\'re doing?", "你到底在搞什么鬼？");
	text = text.replace("If that thing gets loose, it will run to the nearest greenskin encampment and bring their wrath upon this land!", "如果链子松动了，它会跑到最近的绿皮营地，把他们的愤怒带到这片土地上！");
	text = text.replace("The old man nods toward the chain.", "老人朝铁链点了点头。");
	text = text.replace("My very good friend is very safe, stranger, you shouldn\'t worry.", "我好的朋友很安全，陌生人，你不必担心。");
	text = text.replace("You know nothing about who he is or his character!", "你根本不知道他是谁，也不知道他的性格！");
	text = text.replace("You knock down the man with a punch and crouch low so he hears you good and proper.", "你一拳把那个人打倒在地，然后蹲下身子，让他好好地听你说话。");
	text = text.replace("That thing is not your friend.", "那东西不是你的朋友。");
	text = text.replace("It is a danger.", "他是一个祸害。");
	text = text.replace(/You nod to (.*?) who promptly enters the cabin and kills the goblin with a quick stab\./, "你向 $1 点头示意，他迅速进入地窖，很快用匕首杀死了哥布林。");
	text = text.replace("The old man cries out, blood already clotting between his teeth like crimson rinds.", "老人叫道，血已经在他的牙齿间凝结成深红色的皮。");
	text = text.replace("But why? What did he ever do to you?", "但这是为什么？他对你做了什么？");
	text = text.replace("Have you no honor, killing a creature such as he?", "杀了像他这样的生物，你有什么荣誉可言？");
	text = text.replace("You shake your head at the madman and order the rest of the company to fan out and search for items.", "你对那个疯子摇了摇头，然后命令战队的其他人散开去搜寻物品。");
	text = text.replace("When they\'re done, you leave the old man to his cabin and dead friend.", "当他们结束时，你把老人留给他的小屋和死去的朋友。");

//greenskins_slayer_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/While marching, a man crosses paths with the (.*?)\. He is well armored and appears rather knightly save for one feature: a bone necklace hanging from his neck\./, "在行军途中，$1 偶遇一个人。他全副武装，看上去相当有骑士风范，除了一个特征：脖子上挂着一条骨头项链。");
	text = text.replace("With each step it clatters with sickly hollowness against his breastplate.", "每走一步，它就以病态又空虚地弄响着他的盔甲。");
	text = text.replace("You regard this stranger and his skeletal adornments with caution, lest he make a belt out of yer cock and a breast plate out of yer...", "你小心地对待这个陌生人和他的骨骼装饰，以免他用你的鸡鸡做皮带，用你的胸脯做盘子…");
	text = text.replace("Evening, sellswords.", "晚上好，佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("The warrior waves. There\'s an unseen weight to this man, as though surrounded by dead air or perhaps the souls of his victims.", "这个战士挥挥手。对这个人来说，有一种看不见的重量，就好像被死亡之气或者受害者的灵魂包围着。");
	text = text.replace("He nods and continues speaking.", "他点头，继续说。");
	text = text.replace("You seem the greenskin skinnin\' sort, and that\'s the sort of company I\'d be most agreeable to joining.", "你似乎是那种细皮嫩肉的人，我最愿意加入这种人。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) exchanges a glance with you and shrugs\./, "$1 与你交换了一个眼神，耸耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("He whispers his indifference.", "他低声说他漠不关心。");
	text = text.replace("If he\'s a problem, we can handle him.", "如果他有问题，我们可以对付他。");
	//text = text.replace("The man shakes his head.", "那人摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("Oh, I\'ll be no problem.", "噢，我没有问题。");
	text = text.replace("I just want to kill orcs and goblins.", "我只想杀死兽人和哥布林。");
	text = text.replace("What more do you need to know?", "你还需要知道什么？");
	text = text.replace("Once these greenskins are taken care of, I\'ll be out of your hair.", "一旦这些绿皮被处理好了，我就离开你了。");

//greenskins_slayer_leaves_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) the orcslayer walks up to you\./, "$1 向你走来。");
	text = text.replace("Well, I guess that\'s it then.", "好吧，我想就这样了。");
	text = text.replace("There ain\'t as many orcs and goblins around to kill.", "没有那么多的兽人和哥布林可以杀了。");
	text = text.replace("I bid you farewell, sellsword.", "我向你道别，佣兵。");
	text = text.replace("You ask what he\'s going to do..", "你问他打算做什么。");
	text = text.replace("He takes off his armor and puts it on the ground before you.", "他脱下盔甲，放在你面前的地上。");
	text = text.replace("My family has been avenged.", "我家人的仇已经报了。");
	text = text.replace("You nod and wish him well now that his apparent demons have been put to rest. He laughs.", "既然他那明显的恶魔已经安息了，你点头祝他一切顺利。他笑着说。");
	text = text.replace("Just kidding. I don\'t have no family.", "开玩笑的。我没有家庭。");
	text = text.replace("I killed them bastards because I enjoyed spilling their guts, but my heart isn\'t in it anymore.", "我杀了那些混蛋，因为我喜欢听他们的哀嚎，但我的心已经不在那里了。");
	text = text.replace("Send the rest of the men my regards.", "代我向其他人问好。");
	text = text.replace("And with that the orcslayer, or former-orcslayer, departs the company.", "这个兽人杀手，或者说曾经的兽人杀手，离开了战队。");

//greenskins_town_destroyed_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/Somber news on the road\. Refugees and traders are reporting that (.*?) has been destroyed by the greenskins!/, "路上的坏消息。难民和商人报告说 $1 已经被绿皮摧毁了！");
	text = text.replace("If this keeps up, there shan\'t be a land to call home when it\'s all said and done.", "如果这种情况持续下去，当一切尘埃落定的时候，就不会有一个地方叫做家了。");
	text = text.replace("You find a noble messenger watering his horse beside the path.", "你发现一位贵族的信使正在路边给他的马浇水。");
	text = text.replace(/He states that the greenskins have annihilated the human armies around (.*?) and destroyed the town itself!/, "他声称，绿皮已经消灭了 $1 周围的人类军队，并摧毁了这个城镇！");
	text = text.replace("You come across a cartographer and a trader with an empty cart.", "你遇到一个制图师和一个推着空车的商人。");
	text = text.replace(/They\'re redrawing a map and there\'s something curious about it: the mapmaker is erasing (.*?) from the paper\./, "他们正在重画一张地图，其中有一些奇怪的地方：地图制作者正在从纸上擦去 $1。");
	text = text.replace("When you ask why, he raises an eyebrow.", "当你问为什么时，他挑了挑眉毛。");
	text = text.replace(/Oh, you haven\'t heard\? (.*?)\'s been destroyed\./, "噢，你没听说吗？$1 被摧毁了。");
	text = text.replace("Greenskins overran the defenses and killed everyone they got their hands on.", "绿皮越过了防御工事，杀死了他们能抓到的每一个人。");
	text = text.replace("You come across a trader on the path.", "你在路上碰到一个商人。");
	text = text.replace("His cart is emptied and missing some draught animals.", "他的货车空了，少了一些牲畜。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s blood on his face and clothes.", "他的脸上和衣服上都有血迹。");
	text = text.replace("You ask the man for his story. He straightens up.", "你问他的故事。他挺起身。");
	text = text.replace("My story? No, it ain\'t my story.", "我的故事吗？不，这不是我的故事。");
	text = text.replace(/I was on my way to (.*?) only to find it overrun by greenskins\./, "我在去 $1 的路上，却发现那里到处都是绿皮。");
	text = text.replace("I barely escaped with my life.", "我差点没逃过一劫。");
	text = text.replace("The town itself is done for.", "这座城市本身已经完蛋了。");
	text = text.replace("If that\'s the way you was headed, don\'t bother.", "如果那是你的方向，不要自找麻烦了。");
	text = text.replace("It\'s gone. Completely gone.", "它不见了。完全消失了。");

//greenskins_trapped_goblin_event.nut
	text = text.replace("The company steps through some brush and into a clearing where they find a goblin squatting.", "战队穿过一片灌木丛，进入一片空地，在那里他们发现了一个蹲着的哥布林。");
	text = text.replace("It turns toward the company, its breath labored, its eyes somber.", "它转向人群，呼吸困难，眼神忧郁。");
	text = text.replace("You see that there\'s a large bear trap tightly clenching its lower thigh.", "你看到一个巨大的捕熊器紧紧地夹住它的大腿下部。");
	text = text.replace("The greenskin tries a growl, but only manages to cough some blood.", "绿皮试图咆哮，但只咳出一些血。");
	text = text.replace("Beside the dying goblin is a man face down in the grass.", "在奄奄一息的哥布林旁边，一个人脸朝下倒在草地上。");
	text = text.replace(/There\'s something shiny attached to his hip, but you can\'t quite tell what it is\. (.*?) comes to your side\./, "他的屁股上有个亮闪闪的东西，但你不知道那是什么。$1 来到你身边。");
	text = text.replace("Could be a trap.", "可能是个陷阱。");
	text = text.replace("A trap within a trap.", "陷阱中的陷阱。");
	text = text.replace("The rest of his buddies are probably not far.", "他的其他伙伴可能离这里不远。");
	text = text.replace("Then again, if we leave, he might get free and tell everyone we were here.", "然后，如果我们离开，他一旦得到自由，会告诉每个人我们在这里。");
	text = text.replace("What should we do?", "我们应该怎么做？");
	
	text = text.replace("One way or another, the goblin cannot be allowed to live.", "不管怎样，哥布林是不能活下去的。");
	text = text.replace("You step into the clearing to put it out of its misery and, perhaps, get a glimpse at what treasures the corpse might carry.", "你走进空地，想把它从痛苦中解脱出来，也想看看尸体里藏着什么宝物。");
	text = text.replace(/The greenskin shrinks at the sight of you, snarling and rearing up, the trap wrinkling the chains to which it is attached\. (.*?), weapon in hand, carefully gets near to the beast and then kills it with a single blow\./, "绿皮一看到你就收缩起来，咆哮着爬起来，它把依附的锁链弄松动了。$1 手持武器，小心地接近野兽，然后一击杀死它。");
	text = text.replace("With the threat taken care of, you roll the dead man\'s body over and loot everything worth taking.", "威胁解除后，你把死人的尸体翻过来，把所有有价值的东西带走。");
	
	text = text.replace("This is a war of annihilation and no greenskin can be allowed to live.", "这是一场你死我活的战争，没有一个绿皮可以活着。");
	text = text.replace("You step into the field and slay the foul thing.", "你走到田野里，杀死这个肮脏的东西。");
	text = text.replace("With it out of the way, you roll the dead man\'s body over and loot all that\'s worth taking.", "在此基础上，你滚动死者的尸体，并抢夺所有值得拿走的东西。");
	text = text.replace(/Just as you get ready to leave, a gargling growl rumbles from the treeline\. (.*?) takes out his weapon and points\./, "正当你准备离开的时候，一声咕噜作响的咆哮声从树林中传来。$1 拿出武器并伸出手指。");
	text = text.replace("Nachzehrers!", "食尸鬼！");
	text = text.replace("Damn! They must have smelled the dying goblin and came to feast.", "该死！他们一定是闻到了快死的妖精的味道，才来享用的。");
	text = text.replace("Some of them are already picking their teeth with orc bones...", "他们中的一些人已经在用兽人的骨头剔牙了…");
	
	text = text.replace("You\'re not going to risk the company over a single measly goblin and a dead man who may or may not have anything valuable.", "你不会为了一个微不足道的哥布林和一个或有或无任何值钱东西的死人而拿整个战队去冒险的。");
	text = text.replace("The company gives a wide berth to the clearing and continue on through the forest without any issue.", "战队离开了一片空地的距离，继续穿过森林，没有遇到任何麻烦。");
	
	text = text.replace("You\'re not going to risk the company over a single measly goblin and a dead man who may or may not have anything valuable.", "你不会为了一个微不足道的哥布林和一个或有或无任何值钱东西的死人而拿整个战队去冒险的。");
	text = text.replace("The company gives a wide berth to the clearing and continue on through the forest.", "战队离开了一片空地的距离，继续穿过森林。");
	text = text.replace("No more than five minutes down the road do you hear a thundering of footsteps coming up from the rear.", "走了不到五分钟，你就听到从后面传来隆隆的脚步声。");
	text = text.replace("Loud and burly enough that whoever is making it has no fear of being heard.", "声音够大，够有力，不管是谁干的，都不怕被人听见。");
	text = text.replace("You duck and wait and, unsurprisingly, orcs and goblins come through the trees.", "你低头等待，兽人和哥布林毫无意外地从树林中穿过。");
	text = text.replace("One of them is the bastard you\'d left to the bear trap, his leg hurriedly wrapped in linens and leaves.", "其中一个是你留在捕熊器里的那个杂种，他的腿匆匆裹上了亚麻和树叶。");

//greenskins_warnings_event.nut
	text = text.replace("You walk out of your tent and see a wasteland set ablaze.", "你走出帐篷，看到一片被烧毁的荒地。");
	text = text.replace("What isn\'t fire, is blackened by its passing, what isn\'t dead, is screaming as the flames eat their flesh.", "不是火的什么东西，把它经过的地方都熏黑了，也不是什么死了的东西，因为在火焰吞噬它们的肉时在尖叫。");
	text = text.replace("Amidst the smog of this ruin march a stream of burly orcs, chained human slaves dragged forward at their sides, a swarm of goblins skipping around to relish in the chaos.", "在这片废墟的烟雾中，一队身材魁梧的兽人向前行进着，他们身边拖着被锁链锁住的人类奴隶，一群哥布林蹦蹦跳跳地在混乱中寻找乐趣。");
	text = text.replace(/And\.\.\. (.*?)\? The mercenary pokes you and this burning world disappears in an instant\./, "还有… $1？这个雇佣兵戳了你一下，这个燃烧的世界瞬间消失。");
	text = text.replace("All that\'s left is the sellsword standing over you.", "剩下的就是你身边的佣兵了。");
	text = text.replace("Sorry to wake you, sir, but your bedding caught fire by the waning candle there.", "抱歉吵醒你，先生，你的床上用品被那边的残烛烧着了。");
	text = text.replace("I put it out before it could do any harm. Hey, you alright?", "我在它可能造成任何伤害之前就把它扑灭了。嘿，你还好吗？");
	text = text.replace("Nodding, you tell the man to clear out and prepare the men for another day\'s march.", "点头，你告诉他离开，让队员们准备好第二天的行军。");
	text = text.replace("You try to put the memory of the dream out of your head, but it lingers as though it were not meant to be forgotten.", "你试着把梦中的记忆从脑海中抹去，但它却挥之不去，似乎并不想被遗忘。");
	text = text.replace("A man comes barreling out of the treeline beside the path.", "一个男人从路旁的林间小路飞奔而来。");
	text = text.replace(/He\'s wearing rags and half his cheek has been ripped open, his tongue bouncing aloll and with no shape to utter more than guttural screams and desperate pleas\. (.*?) jumps back as the man tries to glom on\./, "他衣衫褴褛，半张脸颊被撕开，舌头跳动着，除了喉咙里的惨叫和绝望的哀求外，再也发不出声音了。当那个人企图抢上前的时候，$1 向后跳了一步。");
	text = text.replace("You draw your sword, but the stranger merely falls to the ground, his back peppered with darts, the skin the points already pulsing green with poison.", "你拔出了剑，但那个陌生人只是倒在地上，背上布满了飞镖，皮肤上的伤口已经被毒液染成了绿色。");
	text = text.replace("The company stays alert for a time, but nothing else comes.", "战队 保持了一段时间的警惕，但没有其他的事情发生。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s a general agreement that this had to have been the work of greenskins, though it appears that there\'s evidence of both orcs and goblins work here...", "大家一致认为这一定是绿皮干的，尽管似乎有证据表明兽人和哥布林都在这里活动…");
	text = text.replace("A young fella comes by with his dog trotting beside him.", "一个小伙子带着他的狗小跑着经过。");
	text = text.replace("He pauses before the company, patting his little mutt on the head.", "他停在人群前，拍了拍他的小杂种狗的头。");
	text = text.replace("You soldiers after the greenies?", "你们是追杀绿皮的士兵？");
	text = text.replace("Tall ones be hard to kill, way I hear it, and the shorties are a real crafty sort.", "据我所知，那些大个子的很难被杀死，而矮个子的是一种很狡猾的生物。");
	text = text.replace("You ask the man where he\'s from. He shrugs.", "你问那个人他来自哪里。他耸耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("Far, far away from here.", "离这里很远很远的地方。");
	text = text.replace("I\'m a wanderer, sirs, me and m\'dog.", "我是一个流浪者，先生们，我和我的狗。");
	text = text.replace("But I\'ve seen a lot in my travels.", "但是我在旅行中看到了很多。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) barges forward\./, "$1 冲了过来。");
	text = text.replace("You\'re telling me you\'ve seen orcs and goblins working together?", "你看到兽人和哥布林合作了？");
	text = text.replace("The boy nods.", "这个男孩点头。");
	text = text.replace("Yup! Why wouldn\'t they?", "是的！他们为什么不呢？");
	text = text.replace("Heh, well, you\'re not who I thought you were.", "嘿，好吧，你们不是我想象中的那种人。");
	text = text.replace("May your days be long, your nights short, and your dreams as long as want.", "祝你们地久天长，好梦不断。");
	text = text.replace("He steps through some standing brush.", "他走过一些矗立的灌木丛。");
	text = text.replace("You give chase, but when you break through to the other side the boy and dog are both gone.", "你追过去，但当你追到另一边时，男孩和狗都不见了。");
	text = text.replace("You heard the flies before seeing the chaos upon which they beset.", "你先听到了苍蝇的叫声，然后才看到它们所制造的混乱。");
	text = text.replace(/A small hovel, simply shaped wooden supports, a nice thatched roof, some pots hanging from strings, a dreamcatcher spinning in the wind, wooden chimes to bring some delight to the air, and three mutilated bodies in the grass, a cloud of bugs swarming on the corpses\. (.*?) crouches before one, prodding at some bones sticking out of the gore\./, "一个小茅屋，简单的木制构架，一个漂亮的茅草屋顶，一些挂在绳子上的罐子，一个在风中旋转的风铃，给空气带来欢乐的木制编钟，草地上有三具残缺不全的尸体，一堆虫子在尸体上成群结队。$1 蹲在一具尸体前面，戳着血里突出的骨头。");
	text = text.replace("Must\'ve been orcs. Footsteps there certainly make it seem so.", "一定是兽人干的。那里的脚步声可能就是。");
	text = text.replace("You nod, but notice that there\'s a few darts stuck to the hovel\'s door.", "你点了点头，但注意到小屋的门上粘着几条飞镖。");
	text = text.replace("You pick one off and smell it.", "你摘了一个，然后闻一闻。");
	text = text.replace("Poison. More than just orcs were here.", "毒药。不仅仅是兽人在这里。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) sniffs one of the darts and nods\./, "$1 嗅了嗅其中一个飞镖，点了点头。");
	text = text.replace("Aye, orcs and goblins.", "是，兽人和哥布林。");
	text = text.replace("Working together? I sure as hell hope not.", "一起合作吗？我当然不希望这样。");
	text = text.replace("It would be a disaster if they were, but for now you\'ll just sit happy in the idea that all the evidence here is merely coincidental.", "如果它们是，那将是一场灾难，但现在你只能高兴地坐着，认为所有的证据都只是巧合。");
	text = text.replace("You look at your map then look at the scene before you.", "你先看地图，然后再看眼前的景色。");
	text = text.replace("A hamlet was supposed to be here.", "这里应该有一个小村庄。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) walks past, chowing down on an apple with a satisfying crunch\./, "$1 走过时，嘴里嚼着一个苹果，发出令人满意的嘎吱嘎吱的声音。");
	text = text.replace("Mmhmm, might wanna pen in some edits then, sir.", "嗯哼，也许要来只笔来记述一下，先生。");
	text = text.replace("The village is nothing but ash.", "这个村庄成了一片废墟。");
	text = text.replace("Its inhabitants are hanging from wooden posts or any tree still standing.", "它的居民被挂在木桩上或任何仍然挺立的树上。");
	text = text.replace("Bones of those not hanged are piled in the middle of what was probably the town square.", "那些没有被绞死的人的尸骨堆在可能是城镇广场的中央。");
	text = text.replace("Staring at the ground, you see footprints leading away from the carnage.", "盯着地面，你看到了从大屠杀中延伸出来的脚印。");
	text = text.replace("Small ones, big ones.", "小的，大的。");
	text = text.replace(/Goblins, orcs\. (.*?) shakes his head\./, "哥布林，兽人。$1 摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("Surely they are not working together, right?", "他们肯定没有在合作，对吧？");
	text = text.replace("You shrug and answer.", "你耸耸肩答道。");
	text = text.replace("I\'m sure the orcs swept through and then the goblins came and picked the remains, or possibly the other way around.", "我敢肯定兽人横扫而过，然后哥布林来了，捡起了遗骨，或者可能是反过来的。");
	text = text.replace("The sellsword nods, assured by your explanation though you both know deep down that the collection of tracks are most likely not a coincidence.", "佣兵点了点头，你的解释让他确信你们俩都知道这两件事很可能不是巧合。");
	text = text.replace("You come across a kid squatting beside a creekbed.", "你看到一个孩子蹲在河床上。");
	text = text.replace(/He\'s using a stick to draw figures in the mud - little stick-men with great horned helms and little \'uns beside them, though even the smaller figures appear well-armed and armored\. (.*?) asks the runt what exactly he\'s doing\./, "他正在用一根棍子在泥里画人物－小棍子一样的人，旁边有带角的大头盔和小帽子，即使是小棍一样的人也全副武装。$1 问孩子到底在做什么。");
	text = text.replace("Drawin\' the greenies. Been seeing them a lot, skittering and scattering the hills they are, like rats in an open pantry my pa says.", "画绿皮。我经常看见他们，他们在山上乱窜乱撞，我爸说就像敞开着门的食品间里进了老鼠。");
	text = text.replace("You ask where he lives.", "你问他住哪儿。");
	text = text.replace("He points up the wooded slopes of a nearby hill.", "他指了指附近山上树木繁茂的山坡。");
	text = text.replace("Yonder. Got a good view of what\'s coming.", "那边。可以很好地看到不少事情。");
	text = text.replace("S\'pose you will in time, too.", "也希望你们去瞅瞅。");
	text = text.replace("An old man yells out for the kid and he obeys, dropping his tools of atavistic artistry and heading for the hill.", "一位老人大声喊着孩子的名字，他答应了，放下了他的复古艺术工具，朝小山走去。");
	text = text.replace("I gots\'ta work. You fellas have fun!", "我正在创作。你们玩得开心！");
	text = text.replace("And don\'t step on m\'drawings!", "不要踩到我的画！");
	text = text.replace("Now you realize the stick figures are orcs and goblins, but maybe the kid is just playing fantasy.", "现在你意识到简笔画是兽人和哥布林，但也许孩子只是在幻想。");
	text = text.replace("You find a fella beside the road cradling his arms in his chest.", "你在路边发现一个小伙子，他把胳膊抱在胸前。");
	text = text.replace("Both the hands appear to be missing.", "两只手好像不见了。");
	text = text.replace("He stares up at you and the momentum carries him backward, the poor man falling flat and staring up at the skies, pawing at it with nubby forearms.", "他抬头望着你，可能是你的气场让他向后倒去，这个可怜的人直挺挺地倒在地上，抬头望着天空，胖乎乎的前臂胡乱挥舞着。");
	text = text.replace("They\'re working together. Killed... Killed everyone.", "他们合作了。杀了…杀了每个人。");
	text = text.replace("I couldn\'t believe the sight of it.", "我不敢相信所看到的。");
	text = text.replace("I always said if they came, I\'d be prepared, for one or the other.", "我总是说，如果他们来了，我会做好准备，其中一种或另一种。");
	text = text.replace("But there they were. Together.", "但是现在他们是。合作了。");
	text = text.replace("You ask who or what he\'s talking about.", "你问他在说谁或什么。");
	text = text.replace("The man\'s chest seizes up, pain crookedly crawls across his face, and he takes his last breath.", "那人的胸脯紧绷着，痛苦歪歪扭扭地爬过他的脸，他咽下了最后一口气。");
	text = text.replace(/A reflected sky arcs in the glisten of his opened eyes, all to see in death\'s blindness\. (.*?) checks the body, but there\'s nothing to take\./, "在他睁开的眼睛里，反射出一道弧形的光，这一切都是为了在死前最后看看这个世界。$1 搜查了他的尸体，但没有东西可以带走。");
	text = text.replace("A totem of skulls, leathered skins flapping off the segments, each head wearing a cape quite gruesomely of their own making.", "一个头骨图腾，皮质的皮肤从碎片上剥落下来，每个头都披着一件他们自己制作的可怕的斗篷。");
	text = text.replace("Blood speckles and fills the ground.", "鲜血染红了大地。");
	text = text.replace("More bones. Muscles and tendons, things unused or uneaten.", "更多的骨头。肌肉和肌腱，未使用或未食用的东西。");
	text = text.replace(/Scorched earth where a campfire grew and scattered ash where it died\. (.*?) picks around the scene, looking for clues\./, "营火造成的焦土，熄灭的灰烬。$1 在现场寻找线索。");
	text = text.replace("He holds up the shaft of a crude weapon, and a couple of darts found in a goatskin bag.", "他举起一件简陋武器的枪杆，在一个山羊皮包里找到了两支飞镖。");
	text = text.replace("This is too big for a man\'s hand, and these are clearly gobbo arrows tipped with, hmm, yes, poison.", "这对一个人的手来说太大了，而这些显然是带有毒药的哥布林箭。");
	text = text.replace("Greenskins no doubt came through here and they did so working together.", "毫无疑问，绿皮来到这里，他们一起工作。");
	text = text.replace("Working together? That\'s a horrible thought, but it does appear to be true. Are the savage tribes up to something?", "一起工作？那是一个可怕的想法，但似乎是真的。这些野蛮部落接下来会做什么呢？");
	text = text.replace("You come to the burnt remains of a hovel.", "你来到一间茅屋的废墟。");
	text = text.replace("There are skeletons about the rubble, bones jagged and clambering in what was final, painful desperations.", "瓦砾堆上到处是骷髅，骨头参差不齐，在这最后的痛苦和绝望之地滚动。");
	text = text.replace("A lock lays in a pile of ash beside what should have been the door, suggesting the people held up inside, while the outsiders simply burned the place down.", "一把锁放在本该是门的旁边的一堆灰烬里，暗示着里面的人被挡住了，而外面的人只是把这个地方烧了。");
	text = text.replace("Sir, you should see this.", "先生，你应该看看这个。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) beckons you over\./, "$1 招手唤你过来。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s standing before a tree.", "他站在一棵树前。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s a dead goblin leaning against the trunk, palms out, empty, an ugly look on its face, and a pitchfork in its chest.", "有一个死去的哥布林倚在树干上，两手摊开，空空的，脸上一副丑陋的表情，胸前插着一把干草叉。");
	text = text.replace(/A dead orc is beside it with a shovelhead sticking out of its skull\. (.*?) wonders if they killed each other\./, "一个死去的兽人站在它旁边，脑袋上插着一个铲子头。$1 不知道他们是否互相残杀。");
	text = text.replace("You hope so, but their mortal wounds look a lot like a human\'s doing, and if it were a human\'s doing, it\'s possible these greenskins were working together.", "你希望如此，但是他们致命的伤口看起来很像人类的行为，如果这是人类的行为，那么这些绿皮可能在一起工作。");
	text = text.replace("The thought frightens you deeply.", "这个想法让深深恐惧的想法。");
	text = text.replace("Refugees on the road, a stream of them, women with babes swaddled and roped behind their backs and affront their bellies, men with pitchforks for walking sticks, discalced friars cutting religious rites through the air with their fingers and breathing prayers under their breath.", "难民们在路上，一群一群的难民，妇女们用襁褓裹着婴儿，用绳子绑在背后，磨破了她们的肚皮，男人们用干草叉当拐杖，剃光了胡须的修士们用手指在空中比划宗教仪式，低声祈祷。");
	text = text.replace("You try and talk, but they shrink from you, wide-eyed.", "你试着和他们交谈，但他们却睁大眼睛躲避你。");
	text = text.replace("Finally, an elderly speaks to you quietly.", "最后，一位老人轻声对你说话。");
	text = text.replace("Don\'t try, sir, they\'ve seen too much.", "不要去尝试了，先生，他们看起来太多了。");
	text = text.replace("The greenskins... they came in the night.", "绿皮…他们昨晚来了。");
	text = text.replace("Orcs in the village, goblins outside it waiting to ambush all that ran.", "兽人在村子里，哥布林在村子外面等着伏击一切逃跑的人。");
	text = text.replace("The militia was massacred.", "民兵遭到屠杀。");
	text = text.replace("Only us cowardly folk survived, and even then only the fastest among us.", "只有我们这些胆小的人才能活下来，即使这样，也只有我们当中跑得最快的人才能活下来。");
	text = text.replace("You ask the man if he just said goblins and orcs were working together.", "你问他是不是说哥布林和兽人在一起工作了。");
	text = text.replace("He nods and pats you on the shoulder.", "他点头，拍拍你的肩膀。");
	text = text.replace("Aye, I did. Safe travels, stranger.", "啊，我确定。旅途平安，陌生人。");
	text = text.replace("A man dressed for pomp and pleasure is standing beside the road.", "路边站着一个打扮得漂漂亮亮的人。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s staring ahead, his hands out to his side, perhaps to balance out a little too much drink in the system.", "他眼睛盯着前方，双手向两侧伸出，也许是为了平衡体内过量的酒精。");
	text = text.replace("You grab and wheel the man around.", "你抓住那个人，把他推来推去。");
	text = text.replace("His face rocks forward, eye sockets emptied, tendrils of his sight hanging down to his cheeks like rotten crawfish.", "他的脸向前晃动，眼神空洞，眉毛的卷须像腐烂的小龙虾一样垂到脸颊上。");
	text = text.replace("Two handless arms slap your shoulders as he tries to grip you.", "当他试图抓住你时，两只没有手的手臂拍着你的肩膀。");
	text = text.replace("His face contorts into a guttural scream that reflects the barbarities he\'s come to experience.", "他的脸扭曲着用喉咙发声，反映出他所经历的野蛮。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) quickly jumps to action and cuts the man down\./, "$1 迅速采取行动，砍倒了这个人。");
	text = text.replace("The stranger falls backward, his fine mink coat opening up to show a brutalized naked body, and now you realize you\'d rather see a man\'s parts than see them missing.", "陌生人向后倒去，他的貂皮大衣敞开着，露出一具被残忍虐待的裸体，现在你意识到，你宁愿看到一个男人身体的某部分，也不愿看到他们消失。");
	text = text.replace("As he hits the ground, his mutilations are his undoing, the cuts and slices opening his flesh up like a puzzle come apart.", "他受到的残害使他毁灭，那些刀痕和切口撑开了他的肉，就像破解谜题一样。");
	text = text.replace("His organs burst through the gaps, unfurling in purpled ropes and bags. The man screams.", "他的器官从缝隙中钻了出来，在紫色的绳索和包里舒展开来。这个人尖叫着。");
	text = text.replace("Orcs! Goblins! Orcs! Goblins! Orcs! Gob... goblins...", "兽人！哥布林！兽人！哥布林！兽人！哥布…哥布林…");
	text = text.replace("His breath leaves him.", "他的呼吸停止了。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s dead, thank the old gods.", "谢天谢地，他已经死了。");
	text = text.replace("Is there something to make of his final words?", "他最后说的话有什么意义吗？");

//undead_crusader_event.nut
	text = text.replace("A man in a suit of armor stops you on the path.", "一个穿着盔甲的人挡住了你的去路。");
	text = text.replace("You put a hand to your sword and order him to announce his intentions, all the while keeping your eyes peeled for an ambush.", "你把手放在你的剑上，命令他讲明他的意图，与此同时，你要密切注意是否有埋伏。");
	text = text.replace("The stranger takes a step forward and removes his helm.", "陌生人向前走了一步，摘下了头盔。");
	text = text.replace(/I am (.*?), a fighter from a fiery land with no name\./, "我是 $1，一个来自无名烈焰之地的战士。");
	text = text.replace("I stood upon the hills of evil counsel.", "我站在邪恶诡计的山上。");
	text = text.replace("I slew the monsters of Dev\'ungrad.", "我杀死了德文格勒的怪物。");
	text = text.replace("I gave peace to the spirits at Shellstaya.", "我在雪尔斯塔亚给灵魂带来了安宁。");
	text = text.replace("When the ancients speak, I listen.", "当古人的喻示的时候，我虔诚倾听。");
	text = text.replace("And so here I am.", "所以我来到了这里。");
	text = text.replace("You take your hand off your sword and ask him of the ancients.", "你把手从剑上拿下来，向他请教古人。");
	text = text.replace("He nods and speaks.", "他点头继续说。");
	text = text.replace("The men before men, the ancients were suzerain over all things, having forged an empire that stretched to realms far beyond this one.", "在人类之前，古人是所有事物的宗主，他们建立了一个疆域远超人类的帝国。");
	text = text.replace("All this chaos is mere fragments of their destruction.", "所有这些混乱只是他们毁灭的碎片。");
	text = text.replace("A man may die, but an empire does not.", "一个人可能会死，但一个帝国不会。");
	text = text.replace("An empire decays, piece by piece, and takes with it all that it thinks it is owed.", "一个帝国会逐渐衰落，它认为自己亏欠的东西也会随之衰落。");
	text = text.replace("The crusader puts his helmet back on and holds his sword up.", "十字军战士戴上头盔，举起他的剑。");
	text = text.replace("The Empire of the Ancients stirs in its grave.", "古代帝国在坟墓里骚动。");
	text = text.replace("I wish to help quiet it.", "我想帮你平息它。");
	text = text.replace("I offer you my sword, mercenary.", "我想为你效劳，雇佣兵。");

//undead_crusader_leaves_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) the crusader approaches you with his armor off and his helmet tucked into the nook of his elbow\./, "$1 这个十字军战士接近你的时候脱掉了他的盔甲，把头盔塞进了他的肘窝里。");
	text = text.replace("Good sir, I must bid the company adieu.", "你好，先生，我得跟战队说再见了。");
	text = text.replace("With the undead beaten, my mission is complete.", "亡灵被打败后，我的任务就完成了。");
	text = text.replace("You go to shake the man\'s hand, but he simply hands you his helm and weapon.", "你去和他握手，但他只是把头盔和武器递给你。");
	text = text.replace("You\'ve more use for these than I.", "你比我更需要它们。");
	text = text.replace("My fighting days are over.", "我的战斗生涯结束了。");
	text = text.replace("It was a pleasure to ride them into the twilight with you by my side.", "和你一起经历它们进入黄昏是一种乐趣。");
	text = text.replace("Send the men my regards.", "代我向其他人问好。");

//undead_frozen_pond_event.nut
	text = text.replace(/While traversing the cold wastes, you come to the lip of a frozen pond\. (.*?) spots something sticking out its middle\./, "当你穿越寒冷的荒野时，你来到了一个结冰的池塘边。$1 发现有东西从里面伸出来。");
	text = text.replace("You see that it\'s a knight whose body has been frozen hip-deep, but the upper body is still moving around.", "你看到一个身体已经冻在臀部以下的骑士，但上半身还在活动。");
	text = text.replace("The eyes glow red and its fingers, jet black from frost bite, still manage to clench and grip.", "它的眼睛红红的，手指被冻伤后变得乌黑，但仍然紧握着。");
	text = text.replace("Its jaw is held together by ice for muscles as though with decaying and translucent tendons.", "它的下颚是由冰来保持肌肉的，就好像它有腐烂的半透明的肌腱一样。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) points to the giant wiederganger with the frozen visage\./, "$1 指向有着冰冻面孔的巨大僵尸。");
	text = text.replace("Hey, look! That farker\'s got a big ol\' sword on him.", "嘿，瞧！那个混蛋身上有一把大剑。");
	text = text.replace("That might be worth trying to nab, no?", "这可能值得一试，不是吗？");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) elects to try and make a run on getting the dead knight\'s sword\./, "$1 选择尝试去获得死去骑士的剑。");
	text = text.replace("His first step on the pond sends an icy warble clear across the underbelly of the frozen sheet.", "他在池塘上的第一步发出了一声冰冷的颤音，轻巧地踏上冰封的冰层。");
	text = text.replace("He tests his footing again.", "他再次试探自己的立足点。");
	text = text.replace("The ice shifts and chitters, but it does not crack.", "冰会移动，但不会破裂。");
	text = text.replace("With every step, the sellsword measures his own weight and its likelihood to collapse the ice - all the meanwhile, making sure he doesn\'t step on one of the corpses littered about.", "每走一步，佣兵都要估测自己的体重和冰层崩塌的可能性，同时还要确保自己不会踩到四处散落的尸体。");
	text = text.replace("He successfully gets to the undead knight.", "他成功地找到了这个亡灵骑士。");
	text = text.replace("Icicles dangle off its sword, the blade itself encapsulated in a layer of ice.", "冰柱悬在剑上，锋刃包裹着一层冰。");
	text = text.replace("The sellsword grabs the blade and yanks.", "佣兵抓起利刃猛拉。");
	text = text.replace("The undead knight\'s arm lurches forward and breaks off at the elbow, sending the sellsword arse-skating backward across the pond.", "亡灵骑士的手臂向前一倾，从肘部断了下来，佣兵向后滑过池塘。");
	text = text.replace("He slides up against the edge where your men help him up.", "他滑到边上，你的人扶他起来。");
	text = text.replace("The sword will need to be heated to get the ice off, but the weapon is definitely usable.", "这把剑需要加热才能把冰弄掉，但是这把剑绝对是有用的。");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) tries the ice, putting a foot right on the edge of the pond\./, "$1 测试冰面，把一只脚踩在池塘边的上。");
	text = text.replace("A soft warble echoes across the pondwater\'s cold underbelly, as though someone had skipped a drumming rock across a barreled surface.", "一种柔和的颤音回荡在冰冷的池水深处，仿佛有人跳过了鼓鼓作响的岩石，穿过了这木桶形状的水面。");
	text = text.replace("He looks back at the party and shrugs.", "他回头看了看众人，耸耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("Seem\'s aight.", "看起来还行。");
	text = text.replace("His next step sends him crashing through the ice.", "他的下一步动作使他撞破了冰面。");
	text = text.replace("Shards break into a sort of chevron entrapment and when he reaches out to grab one it slices his hands.", "当他伸手去抓取时一点东西的时候，碎片划破了他的手。");
	text = text.replace("The men quickly throw him a rope and drag him out.", "那些人迅速地扔给他一根绳子，把他拖了出来。");
	text = text.replace(/Bloodied and shivering, (.*?) shakes his head as he\'s wrapped in blankets\./, "他浑身是血，瑟瑟发抖，$1 裹着毯子摇摇头。");
	text = text.replace("I-I-I-I believe that was aw-aw-aw-awful.", "我－我－我－我相信这很－很－很－糟糕。");
	text = text.replace("Aw-aw-awful idea, sir.", "糟－糟－糟糕的主意，先生。");
	
	//text = text.replace(/(.*?) steps forward\./, "$1 走上前去。");
	text = text.replace("Ice? Ice is nothing.", "冰？那不是事儿。");
	text = text.replace("You can glide on it like this.", "你可以像这样在上面滑动。");
	text = text.replace("Without even a pause, the man leaps out onto the frozen pond and skates across its surface.", "甚至没有停顿，这个人就跳上了结冰的池塘，在水面上滑行。");
	text = text.replace("Cracks emerge out from behind him like a wake of imminently bad news, but he remains unperturbed.", "他的身后出现了裂痕，就像一个即将到来的坏消息的提醒，但他仍然泰然自若。");
	text = text.replace("He swings by the undead knight and grabs the frozen sword.", "他从亡灵骑士身边荡过，抓住了冰冻的剑。");
	text = text.replace("The wiederganger groans as its arm breaks off at the elbow.", "这个亡灵的胳膊在肘部断了，呻吟着。");
	text = text.replace(/The man merrily skates his way back to the edge of the pond and presents the sword to you\. (.*?) steps forward and cracks the wiederganger\'s frozen arm off the handle like a man breaking a crab claw\./, "那人愉快地滑回到池塘边，把剑交给你。$1 走上前来，把亡灵那只冻僵的手臂从剑柄上折断，就像一个人折断了一只螃蟹的爪子。");
	text = text.replace("Would ya look at that?", "你看到这些了么？");
	text = text.replace("He crushes the fingers into fragments and in the powdered remains there is a signet.", "他把手指压成碎片，粉末状的残留物上有一个图章。");
	text = text.replace("A sword and jewelry, what\'s not to love about this result?", "一把剑和一件珠宝，有什么理由不喜欢这个结果呢？");

//undead_hoggart_event.nut
	text = text.replace("Marching through a foggy, hot rain, you spot a figure standing in the middle of the path.", "行军穿过一片雾，雨水也是热的，你发现一个人影站在路中间。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s holding a metal-wreathed torch, no doubt the fire of a man wanting to be seen.", "他手里拿着一支带金属环的火炬，无疑是一个想要用火炬来吸引人注意的人。");
	text = text.replace("As you draw near, he puts the torch down, giving light to an oddly familiar face, though you can\'t quite put your finger on it.", "当你走近时，他放下手里的火炬，照出一张熟悉得出奇的脸，但是你不敢用手指碰他。");
	text = text.replace("You order him to announce himself.", "你命令他宣布自己的身份。");
	text = text.replace("Are ye a lot of sellswords, hm?", "你们是一群佣兵，哼？");
	text = text.replace("You tell him that is not a name.", "你告诉他这不是一个名字。");
	text = text.replace("He clears his throat, a soft orange glow of his face peering through the storm\'s dark.", "他清了清嗓子，脸上泛着柔和的橘红色，透过暴风雨的黑暗向外张望。");
	text = text.replace("My name is Barnabas.", "我的名字是巴纳巴斯。");
	text = text.replace("Are ye sellswords or not?", "你们是不是佣兵？");
	text = text.replace("Carefully, you cross the path and come close to the man.", "你小心地穿过小路，靠近那个人。");
	text = text.replace("He waves the torch aside.", "他把火炬挥到一边。");
	text = text.replace("Yeah, I figured as much.", "是的，我想也是。");
	text = text.replace("My brother, I need someone... I mean, I can\'t..", "我的兄弟，我需要一个人…我是说，我不能…");
	text = text.replace("You nod and speak for him.", "你点头听他说话。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s come up out of the grave and now you want someone to take care of him.", "他从坟墓里出来了，现在你需要派人来照顾他。");
	text = text.replace("The man nods, he waves the torch to a yonder spot where a dim light burns in the distance.", "那人点了点头，把火把朝远处一个有着昏暗亮光的地方一挥。");
	text = text.replace(/He\'s thataway\. I\'ll pay you (.*?) crowns, seeing as how you\'re sellswords and all\./, "他在那个方向。我会给你 $1 克朗，看看你们这些佣兵会怎么做。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You tell the man to show the way, bringing (.*?) with you and leaving another sellsword in charge while you\'re gone\./, "你告诉那个人带路，带着 $1，让另一个佣兵在你不在的时候负责。");
	text = text.replace("Barnabas leads you down a hillside and to the fence line of a property home to a decently sized stone house.", "巴纳巴斯带你下了山坡，来到一处房产的围栏边，那里有一座大小适中的石屋。");
	text = text.replace("Candlelight flickers beyond the windows. Barnabas stares forward.", "烛光在窗外闪烁。巴纳巴斯凝视着前方。");
	text = text.replace("Nobody\'s there. The only one here is Hoggart.", "没人在那里。这里唯一的人就是霍加特。");
	text = text.replace("That name... Barnabas\'s face...", "这个名字…巴纳巴斯的脸…");
	text = text.replace("You grab the man and push him into the fence, demanding to know if he is the bandit\'s brother. Barnabas quickly nods.", "你抓住那个人，把他推到栅栏里，问他是不是强盗的兄弟。巴纳巴斯迅速点了点头。");
	text = text.replace("Aye, that I am! What of it?", "是啊，就是我！怎么了？");
	text = text.replace(/You tell him that Hoggart nearly wiped out the (.*?) and that, in return, you slew the man dead\./, "你告诉他，霍加特几乎毁灭了 $1，为了报仇，你杀了他。");
	text = text.replace("Barnabas holds his hands up.", "巴纳巴斯举起双手。");
	text = text.replace("If that\'s so, it is what it is.", "如果是这样，那就对了。");
	text = text.replace("Hoggart was only doing what he needed to keep the property in the family.", "霍加特所做的只是把财产留在家里。");
	text = text.replace("After our father died, we took on debts - debts we could not pay.", "父亲去世后，我们负债累累－债务我们无力偿还。");
	text = text.replace("You draw a dagger and put it to the man\'s throat.", "你拔出匕首，刺向他的喉咙。");
	//text = text.replace("He shakes his head.", "他摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("I\'m not here to ambush or rob you.", "我不是来这里伏击或抢劫你的。");
	text = text.replace("The home\'s been sold.", "房子已经卖出去了。");
	text = text.replace("It\'s out of the family.", "这是我们家的事。");
	text = text.replace("But Hoggart... he\'s come back and he won\'t leave.", "但是霍加特…他回来了，他不会离开。");
	text = text.replace("You look over Barnabas\'s shoulder.", "你看着巴纳巴斯的肩膀。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s a dark figure standing before the home, its silhouette lit by the windowlight.", "有一个黑影站在房子前面，它的轮廓被窗户的灯光照亮了。");
	
	text = text.replace("Bloodlines are not easily broken.", "血缘关系不是那么容易被打破的。");
	text = text.replace("Whatever Barnabas is saying, it\'s likely that he\'ll come after the company someday, someday when it\'s cold and quiet and the fires of vengeance can\'t be so easily quenched.", "无论巴纳巴斯怎么说，总有一天他会来找我们战队的，这一天寒冷而宁静，复仇的火焰不会轻易熄灭。");
	text = text.replace("You tell the man to lead the way, and the second he turns about you stab him just beneath the armpit, piercing his heart.", "你叫那个人带路，他一转身，你就在他腋窝下捅了一刀，刺穿了他的心脏。");
	text = text.replace("He doesn\'t say anything.", "他什么也没说。");
	text = text.replace("He simply goes to his knees, facing the back of his brother and the home he grew up in.", "他只是跪倒在地，面对着他兄弟的背影和他从小到大的家。");
	text = text.replace(/He sits there, crumpled and dying, the rain pattering against the torch until it sizzles dead\. (.*?) spits\./, "他坐在那里，瘫倒在地，奄奄一息，雨水噼噼啪啪地打在火炬上，直到它发出死亡一般的嘶嘶声。$1 吐了口水。");
	text = text.replace("Good call, sir.", "好办法，先生。");
	text = text.replace("He rifles through the body and finds a shiny dagger.", "他搜查尸体，发现了一把闪亮的匕首。");
	text = text.replace("Perhaps the tool to an assassin, perhaps the last heirloom of a dead family name.", "也许是一个刺客的工具，也许是一个没落家族的最后传家宝。");
	text = text.replace(/Either way, you take it and return to the (.*?)\./, "不管怎样，你拿着它回到 $1。");
	
	text = text.replace("This is not your problem, nor should it ever be.", "这不是你的问题，也不应该是。");
	text = text.replace("Hoggart is dead and that\'s all you need, or want, to know about him or any of his family name.", "霍加特已经死了，这就是你需要的，或者你想知道的，而不是他和他的家族那些事。");
	text = text.replace(/You leave Barnabas there in the rain and return to the (.*?) to plan for the next trip\./, "你把巴纳巴斯留在雨中，返回 $1 去制定新的行程。");
	
	text = text.replace("Against better judgment, you go and see if this really is Hoggart.", "抛开更谨慎的判断，你去看看这是不是真的霍加特。");
	text = text.replace("Marching toward him, he growls and peers over his shoulder.", "你朝他走去，他一边咆哮一边回头张望。");
	text = text.replace("It is indeed Hoggart, but he does little more than snarl at you before turning to stare at the home again.", "这确实是霍加特，但他只是对你咆哮了几声，然后又转过头去盯着他的家。");
	text = text.replace("Taking out your sword, you approach carefully.", "你拿出剑，小心地靠近。");
	text = text.replace("From closer up, you can see that the man\'s head has been stitched back onto someone else\'s body, perhaps a knight\'s based upon the armored crest it is wearing.", "从近距离看，你可以看到这个人的头被缝回到了别人的身体上，从盔甲和装束上看似乎是个骑士。");
	text = text.replace("But enough lollygagging. You swing your sword back and bring it down upon Hoggart for one final blow - but a faint, blue hand launches out, stopping the blade as though you\'d struck a slab of stone.", "真是浪费时间。你把剑往后一挥，最后一击落在了霍加特身上－但一只微弱的蓝色的手伸了出来，把锋刃停下来，就好像你碰到了一块石头。");
	text = text.replace("Slowly, a spectral face turns, independent of Hoggart, and looks at you.", "慢慢地，一张幽灵般的脸转向了你，与霍加特无关，看着你。");
	text = text.replace("He shrieks before disappearing back into the dead man\'s lent body.", "他尖叫了一声，然后又消失在死人的躯体里。");
	text = text.replace("Barnabas stands beside you.", "巴纳巴斯站在你们旁边。");
	text = text.replace("If I could do it that easily, I would have done it myself.", "如果能那么容易地做到这件事，我就自己做了。");
	text = text.replace("It appears there\'s a powerful, malevolent force at play here.", "这里似乎有一股强大的邪恶力量在作祟。");
	text = text.replace("You will need to find a different solution.", "你需要找到一个不同的解决方案。");
	
	text = text.replace("Hoggart reaches a hand out to his home, gripping at it from a distance.", "霍加特把手伸向他的家，似乎想从远处抓住什么。");
	text = text.replace("His growls turn to soft moans.", "他的咆哮变成了轻柔的呻吟。");
	text = text.replace("A disfigured and desiccated tongue rolls a few words out.", "一个变形了的，干瘪了的舌头吐出几个字。");
	text = text.replace("Ours... ours... always...", "我们的…我们的…总是…");
	text = text.replace(/You glance at the house, then at (.*?)\. He nods\./, "你瞥了眼房子，然后又看了看 $1。他点头。");
	text = text.replace("The house has to be ridden of.", "这房子得毁掉。");
	text = text.replace("You go about setting the place aflame from the inside, pitching torches through its windows and setting alight its thatched roof.", "你四处走动，决定从里面点燃这个地方，把火把从窗户里扔进去，并点燃茅草屋顶。");
	text = text.replace("Even in the rain it catches ablaze.", "即使在雨中它也会着火。");
	text = text.replace("Hoggart growls and his body lurches forward, arms out, hands reached to the furthest fingertips.", "霍加特咆哮着，身体向前倾去，伸出双臂，双手用指尖伸向远处。");
	text = text.replace("The specter spawns out of his shoulders, its translucent arms grabbing Hoggart by the head and trying to hold him back.", "幽灵从他的肩膀上冒了出来，半透明的手臂抓住了霍加特的脑袋，试图把他拉回来。");
	text = text.replace("The dead man growls and tries to run forward, his head tearing at the seams of his stitches. He screams.", "死者咆哮着试图向前跑去，他的头在缝线处撕裂着。他尖叫道。");
	text = text.replace("OURS! I TRIED. SO. HARD!", "我们的。我尽力了。唉。太难了！");
	text = text.replace("The stitches snap free and his body somersaults backwards, his head torn asunder and falling into the mud.", "缝线松了，他的身体向后翻了个跟头，脑袋被撕开了，掉进了泥里。");
	text = text.replace("The blue specter, wrenched free from the neck, screams and soars into the night sky, a mere shimmer against the rain until it is gone.", "蓝色的幽灵摆脱了脖子，尖叫着冲向夜空，在雨中闪着微光，直到消失。");
	text = text.replace(/Barnabas goes and sits beside Hoggart, the dead man\'s eyes staring blankly at the inferno consuming their childhood home\. (.*?) retrieves the armor from the body upon which Hoggart\'s head had rested\./, "巴纳巴斯走过去坐在霍加特身边，死者的眼睛茫然地盯着吞噬他们童年家园的烈火。$1 从霍加特尸体处取回盔甲，他的人头也在那。");
	text = text.replace("You try and talk to Barnabas, but he refuses to speak.", "你想和巴纳巴斯谈谈，但他拒绝说话。");
	text = text.replace("Understanding, you do not prod him and leave the place behind, the fires still unerring against the rain when you depart.", "你明白了，所以没有催促他离开，当你离开的时候，火焰依然不会在雨中熄灭。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You whisper to (.*?) to attack Hoggart, but only to try and distract the specter inhabiting his body\./, "你向 $1 耳语说要攻击霍加特，但只是为了转移附身的幽灵的注意力。");
	text = text.replace("The sellsword nods and immediately gets to work, drawing out his weapon and charging forward.", "佣兵点头，立即开始工作，拔出武器，向前冲去。");
	text = text.replace(/Predictably, a blue arm shoots out, crossing its unerring yet translucent shape with (.*?)\'s weapon\./, "可以预见的是，一只蓝色的手臂伸出来了，它那可以确信的半透明形状与 $1的武器交相辉映。");
	text = text.replace("He looks over the interlocking and screams.", "他向四周看了一下这环环相扣的场景，发出了尖叫声。");
	text = text.replace("Now!", "现在！");
	text = text.replace("You jump forward and swing your sword.", "你跳上前去挥动你的剑。");
	text = text.replace("The specter whips around, screaming, but it is too late.", "幽灵尖叫着转过身来，但已经太迟了。");
	text = text.replace("Your blade passes through Hoggart\'s neck, rending his head free with a quick slash, his dome rolling down his chest into the mud while the body flails backward.", "你的利刃穿过了霍加特的脖子，一刀把他的头砍了下来，他的头从他的胸口滚进了泥浆里，而他的身体向后乱甩。");
	text = text.replace(/Ushered into the world all by itself, the specter shrieks and swirls around in the sky, finding naught but chaos in its newfound freedom\. (.*?) looks at the chest armor that had been on Hoggart\'s body and shakes his head. Damn thing broke\./, "幽灵只好独自面对这个世界了，它尖叫着，在空中盘旋，在它新发现的自由中除了混乱什么也没有。$1 看着霍加特身上的胸甲，他摇了摇头。这该死的东西坏了。");
	text = text.replace("A group of men suddenly start across the yard, holding out torches and swords alike.", "一群人突然跑过院子，手里拿着火把和剑。");
	text = text.replace("One especially opulent fellow leads them.", "一个特别有钱的家伙领导着他们。");
	text = text.replace("Is that you Barnabas?", "是你吗，巴纳巴斯？");
	text = text.replace("I thought I told you to never step foot on my property again!", "我想我告诉过你不要再踏进我的地盘！");
	text = text.replace("You explain to them what happened.", "你向他们解释发生了什么事。");
	text = text.replace("The man, ostensibly the buyer of the land, nods, saying he\'d brought with him a cleric to solve the issue, but now that you have he pays you a tidy sum of crowns.", "这个人，宣称是土地的买主，点头，说他带了一个牧师来解决这个问题，但现在你办到了，他付给你一笔可观的克朗。");
	text = text.replace("When you turn back around, Barnabas and Hoggart\'s head are both gone.", "你回头一看，巴纳巴斯和霍加特的脑袋都不见了。");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) says that (.*?) probably knows what to do here\./, "$1 说 $2 可能知道此时该怎么办。");
	text = text.replace("You agree and run to go get the witch hunter.", "你同意了，跑去找女猎巫人。");
	text = text.replace("On your return, he assesses the situation before consulting a thick book that\'d been hidden away in a pocket.", "你回来时，他先估计了一下情况，然后看了看藏在口袋里的厚书。");
	text = text.replace("He nods, murmuring to himself as he reads.", "他点了点头，边读边喃喃自语。");
	text = text.replace("Finally, he snaps his fingers.", "最后，他打了响指。");
	text = text.replace("This is a Gespenst von Zwei, a haunting of two souls.", "这是一只双头鬼魂，两个鬼魂缠绕在一起。");
	text = text.replace("In this case, Hoggart\'s and that of the man whose body his head now rests upon.", "在这种情况下，一个是是霍加特的，另一个是个身首异处的家伙。");
	text = text.replace("One soul egregiously cast out is simple enough, but two combined is a malevolent and angry force.", "一个灵魂被狠狠地抛弃是很简单的，但是两个结合在一起是一种恶毒和愤怒的力量。");
	text = text.replace("If we simply destroy the body or the head, the souls will be bound together and will haunt the lands forever.", "如果我们只是简单地摧毁身体或头部，两个灵魂将被捆绑在一起，并将永远萦绕在这片土地上。");
	text = text.replace("Some even blunder into the skies.", "有些甚至撞向了天空。");
	text = text.replace("Unfortunately, instead of finding the heavens, they find a hell of unending confusion and the fury that brings.", "不幸的是，他们发现的不是天堂，而是无尽的混乱和愤怒所带来的地狱。");
	text = text.replace("I believe Hoggart\'s soul, or whatever binds him to this world, is stronger than that of the other man\'s.", "我相信霍加特的灵魂，或者是任何把他和这个世界联系在一起的东西，比另一个人的灵魂更强大。");
	text = text.replace("The struggle he had in life was too great to simply end on his final breath and that is why he stands at his old home.", "他一生中所经历的坎太多了，不可能在最后一口气的时候就结束了，这就是他在老家游荡的原因。");
	text = text.replace("You stop the witch hunter and ask the most pertinent question...", "你打断女巫猎人，问了一个最关键的问题…");
	
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) forces a smile\./, "$1 挤出一个微笑。");
	text = text.replace("Apologize to him.", "向他道歉。");
	text = text.replace("Not sure you heard him right, you echo his phrase and the witch hunter nods.", "不确定你是否听对了，你重复了他的话，女巫猎人点了点头。");
	text = text.replace("Aye, apologize. And mean it, too.", "啊，道歉。我也是认真的。");
	text = text.replace("Many men are so filled with hate, or so filled with desire, that any failure contextualizes itself as an energy beyond the mortal coil.", "许多人充满了仇恨，或是充满了欲望，以至于任何失败都把自己化作一种难以想象的强大能量。");
	text = text.replace("You killed this man.", "你杀了这个人。");
	text = text.replace("It is you who upended a life which could not brook even the slightest of pauses, much less the ultimate defeat that is death.", "是你颠覆了一个连最轻微的停顿都无法容忍的生命，更不用说最终的失败了，那就是死亡。");
	text = text.replace("It is you who can end his struggle now.", "现在是你结束煎熬的时候了。");
	text = text.replace("I believe apologizing would do this.", "我想道歉就可以了。");
	text = text.replace("Barnabas steps forward and explains, again, that Hoggart only worked to ensure that the estate stayed within the family.", "巴纳巴斯迈步上前解释，又一次的，霍加特的工作只是为了确保遗产留在家族之内。");
	text = text.replace("All that he did was for the family.", "他所做的一切都是为了家族。");
	text = text.replace(/He was not an evil or cruel man, he was only doing what he thought was right\. (.*?) throws a hand out as if to say \'see\'\./, "他不是一个邪恶或残忍的人，他只是在做他认为正确的事情。$1 伸出一只手，好像在说“看”。");
	text = text.replace("Well, there ya go. Captain, listen.", "好的，你去吧。队长，听。");
	text = text.replace("Whatever feud there was between you two is over.", "你们之间的宿怨就要过去了。");
	text = text.replace("This is something else.", "这是另一回事。");
	text = text.replace("No man deserves this fate.", "没有人配得上这种命运。");
	text = text.replace("Apologize to him from the heart and you can end his suffering once and for all.", "发自内心地向他道歉，你就可以彻底的结束他的痛苦。");
	
	text = text.replace("You step toward Hoggart.", "你向霍加特走去。");
	text = text.replace("He growls and eyes you for a moment before staring back at the home.", "他咆哮着，盯着你看了一会儿，然后回望着他的家。");
	text = text.replace("With another cautionary step, you come to stand in front of him.", "你又谨慎地走了一步，来到他面前。");
	text = text.replace("His glazed, desiccated eyes glare at you, but he doesn\'t look away this time. You speak.", "他呆滞干瘪的眼睛瞪着你，但这次他没有把目光移开。你说道。");
	//text = text.replace("Hoggart...", "霍加特…");
	text = text.replace("The undead man leans back, his eyes slimming incredulously, his hand touching his chest.", "亡灵人向后一靠，眼睛怀疑地眯着，手摸着胸口。");
	text = text.replace("His voice seems to unfurl, strained from the depths of a borrowed body.", "他的声音似乎从一具借来的尸体的深处舒展出来。");
	text = text.replace("Ho...ggart... I... tried...", "霍…加特…我…尽力了…");
	text = text.replace("Nodding, you jack your thumbs into your belt line.", "点着头，你把你的拇指抵住你的声带。");
	text = text.replace("I know you tried.", "我知道你尽力了。");
	text = text.replace("I mean, I didn\'t know you were trying to begin with, but now I know.", "我是说，我不知道你一开始就想这么做，但现在我知道了。");
	text = text.replace("Look, your brother told me everything.", "听着，你兄弟把一切都告诉我了。");
	text = text.replace("Had I known, I wouldn\'t have taken that contract. You didn\'t...", "如果我知道的话，我就不会接受那份合同了。你没有…");
	text = text.replace(/You glance at (.*?) who nods\. You continue\./, "你瞥了一眼正在点头的 $1。你继续道。");
	text = text.replace("Hoggart, you didn\'t deserve to die.", "霍加特，你不值得去死。");
	text = text.replace("Not like that. Were I in your shoes, I would have been doing the same.", "不是这样的。如果我处在你的位置，我也会这样做的。");
	text = text.replace("But I wasn\'t in your shoes.", "但是我没有站在你的立场上。");
	text = text.replace("I could not have understood who you were or what you were doing.", "我无法理解你是谁，你在做什么。");
	text = text.replace("I was only doing what I was paid to do.", "我只是在做别人付钱让我做的事。");
	text = text.replace("I can\'t take back what\'s been done, all I can do is say... I\'m sorry.", "我无法收回我所做的一切，我所能做的只是说…我对不起你。");
	text = text.replace("You don\'t deserve this pain and I am sorry.", "你不应该承受这种痛苦，我很抱歉。");
	text = text.replace("Hoggart\'s glazed, drooping eyes stare at you a moment longer, then suddenly his body wobbles and falls forward.", "霍加特呆滞低垂的眼睛又盯着你看了一会儿，然后他的身体突然晃了晃，向前倒了下去。");
	text = text.replace("Two spirits emerge, one twisting and shooting across the muddied land, wimpling stones with tears of its blue spectra as it streaks straight to the horizon.", "两个鬼魂出现了，一只在泥泞的土地上扭曲着，射击着，当它直冲地平线时，蓝色光芒的泪珠在石头上闪烁。");
	text = text.replace("But the other spirit remains, glowing a faint gold now, and it simply floats toward the home.", "但另一个灵魂依然存在，现在发出微弱的金色光芒，它只是朝家飘去。");
	text = text.replace("Barnabas follows after it and you after him.", "巴纳巴斯跟着它，而你们紧随其后。");
	text = text.replace("Together, you round a corner and head toward the back end of the property where Hoggart\'s ghost pauses.", "你们一起绕过一个角落，朝庄园的后边走去，霍加特的幽灵就停在那里。");
	text = text.replace("All I did, for this.", "我所做的一切，都是为了这个。");
	text = text.replace("No longer mine. Yours.", "现在它不再属于我了。归你了。");
	text = text.replace("The spirit fades away as Barnabas reaches out to it, glistening dust floating away from his touch.", "当巴纳巴斯伸出手去触摸时，他的鬼魂渐渐消失，闪闪发光的灰尘从他的触摸中飘散。");
	text = text.replace("You notice that the earth has been upturned here and a crate is sinking into the rainwater.", "你注意到这里的泥土被翻了起来，一个板条箱正沉入雨水中。");
	text = text.replace("Dragging it up and opening it, you find an enormous sword with decorations of Hoggart\'s family name.", "把它拖起来打开，你会发现一把巨大的剑，上面装饰着霍加特的姓。");
	text = text.replace("Baranabas looks as shocked as you about it.", "巴纳巴斯看起来和你一样震惊。");
	text = text.replace("The family heirloom. He said he\'d never sell it to save the estate, he thought one couldn\'t be without the other.", "家族的传家宝。他说这用来作为遗产，永远不会卖掉，他认为这是独一无二的。");
	text = text.replace("When I told him it had to be done he took it town and then came back and told me he lost it gambling...", "当我告诉他必须这么做时，他从城市跑回来告诉我他在赌博中输掉了这把剑…");
	text = text.replace("I never talked to him again.", "我再也没跟他说过话。");
	text = text.replace("Last thing I said to him was that he was a no good vagrant and the worst brother anyone could ever have.", "我对他说的最后一句话是，他不是一个好流浪汉，是世上最糟糕的兄弟。");
	text = text.replace("Now I know the truth.", "现在我知道真相了。");
	text = text.replace("You have brought me and my brother peace, sellsword, and that peace is all I want to remember.", "你给我和我的兄弟带来了安宁，佣兵，而这种安宁正是我想要记住的。");
	text = text.replace("Please, as my brother said, take the heirloom.", "请，就像我兄弟说的那样，收下这个传家宝。");
	text = text.replace("You take the sword and wish Barnabas the best.", "你拿起剑，祝巴纳巴斯安好。");
	text = text.replace("The last you see of him he is sitting in the mud, body hunched, tottering and weeping with the rain all around him until there\'s no man at all, just a warm home and a storm booming with golden lightning.", "你最后一次看到他的时候，他正坐在泥里，身体蜷缩着，颤巍巍的，哭泣着，周围都是雨，直到一个人也没有了，只有一个温暖的家庭和一场伴随着金色闪电轰鸣的暴风雨。");

//undead_intro_event.nut
	text = text.replace("You put your head down for a nap.", "你低下头准备打个盹。");
	text = text.replace("The silky bedsheet slides off your body as you roll to a side.", "你翻个身，丝质的被单溜了出去。");
	text = text.replace("Birds flutter past a sleek, ivory-framed window.", "有鸟飞过镶有象牙的窗棂。");
	text = text.replace("A voice pours into your ear, a hint of an aroma you\'ve never smelled before gracing you.", "仿佛有一种浸在前所未有的优雅芳香里的声音侵入你的耳朵。");
	text = text.replace("You\'re awake.", "你醒啦。");
	text = text.replace("A woman rolls herself over, running a finger down your chest before going back up and seizing your chin.", "一个女人翻过身，沿着你胸前纤纤玉指轻轻向下游离，复又逆行而上攫取你的下巴。");
	text = text.replace("Lithe, pretty, the sun glowing across her smooth face, and lighting up a set of emerald eyes.", "轻盈而又美丽，阳光映照在她光洁的脸上，绿宝石般的眼眸熠熠生辉。");
	text = text.replace("She goes for a kiss.", "她向你索吻。");
	text = text.replace("You quickly slide out of the bed and frantically look around.", "你狂乱地滚下床，四下张望。");
	text = text.replace("She grips the sheets and comes to her knees, confused.", "她攥着床单跪在床上，非常疑惑。");
	text = text.replace("What\'s wrong? Where are you going my Emperor?", "怎么了？你要去哪我的帝王？");
	text = text.replace("Looking up, you see a ceiling that stretches so far up you can hardly even see the artwork which has been exquisitely embroidered there.", "抬起头，你看到一个天花板，那么宽广你甚至看不清可称为艺术品的精致花边。");
	text = text.replace("You open a door and step out onto a balcony.", "你打开一扇门，走到阳台上。");
	text = text.replace("Impossibly tall buildings, red, white, gold banners, a horizon steepled with black shapes stretching as far as the eye wishes to see.", "难以置信的高耸群楼，红，白和金色的旗帜，一直延伸到目之所及凝成黑色形状的奇点。");
	text = text.replace("Domes, fountains, great arches, statues that stand so tall they seem to be commanding the structures as soldiers.", "穹顶，喷泉，巨大的拱门，以及高高耸立的雕像，如此雄伟好像它们就像统领士兵一样指挥着建筑群。");
	text = text.replace("Atop each roof is a garden greater and more flush than anything you\'ve seen in the eternal springs of nature itself.", "每个屋顶上都有一个花园，比你在永恒的春天里看到的任何自然形成的花园都要更大，更壮观。");
	text = text.replace("Suddenly, two men emerges at your sides with cages of doves and let them out.", "这时两个男人从你身边冒出来，放出提着的笼子里的鸽子。");
	text = text.replace("The birds desperately scatter and just then a roar erupts beneath you.", "鸟儿们拼命四散飞出去，在你脚下发出尖啸。");
	text = text.replace("Great crowds of people jumping and waving banners around.", "周围的人群雀跃着挥舞起旗帜。");
	text = text.replace("They love their Emperor.", "他们爱戴他们的帝王。");
	text = text.replace("The woman speaks from the doorway.", "那个女人出现在门口。");
	text = text.replace("Go to them.", "去迎接他们吧。");
	text = text.replace("You look down to see a stream of soldiers marching down the middle of the road, each man stepping in unison with his brother, a steady staccato clap of boots.", "你低头一看，只见一群士兵正沿着大路行进，每个人都和队友的步调一致，靴子踏着地面发出整齐的步伐声。");
	text = text.replace("Their faces stern in their gilded helms, long polearms glistening upward as though they meant to defeat their enemies with opulence itself.", "囿于镀金的头盔里的是坚定的神色，长长的长柄武器向上泛起着阳光般的色泽，仿佛他们要用财富本身来击败敌人。");
	text = text.replace("They\'re going off to war.", "他们整装待发。");
	text = text.replace("To face the Great Beyond, and to defeat it.", "准备迎击远大的未来，并征服它。");
	text = text.replace("The woman is at your side.", "女人待你身边。");
	text = text.replace("She smiles warmly, taking you by the arm.", "温和地笑着，挽着你的胳膊。");
	text = text.replace("You feel ready to agree to it, to this new reality, whatever it be.", "无论这个新现实是什么，你都准备好接受它了。");
	text = text.replace("You take her by the cheek, ready to fall into her embrace, but a cry from below wails loud and clear over all else.", "你把她的脸颊握在手心里，正准备拥她入怀，但从下面传来清晰响亮的惨叫却地盖过了一切。");
	text = text.replace("You glance down to see the soldiers, once joined in perfect uniformity, breaking rank.", "你往下看了一眼，曾经列着整齐划一队形已经不复存在。");
	text = text.replace("In the distance, a great mountain is erupting, jetting great bursts of red fire and an enormous cloud of hot ash which quickly pools into the city.", "远处，一座大山正在爆发，喷出大量的红色火焰和满天的巨大的灼热灰烬，炼狱很快涌进城市。");
	text = text.replace("Buildings disintegrate, gardens burst into flames, and the people... the people scream.", "建筑物分崩离析，花园被火焰吞噬，人们…人们尖叫着。");
	text = text.replace("They turn away, but there is no escaping the heat.", "逃跑，但是没人能逃脱炼狱。");
	text = text.replace("The soldiers collapse and scream.", "士兵们尖叫着脱离了阵型。");
	text = text.replace("A surging, searing heat, and soon enough you see the denizens melting in it, the soldiers becoming metal golems, singed into the very armor which was meant to protect them, and the unarmored crowds simply burst aflame.", "随着一股灼热、汹涌的热浪，很快你就看到居民们融化在这股热浪之中，士兵们变成了金属像，原本保护他们的盔甲也被烧焦，而没有盔甲保护的人群直接燃烧起来。");
	text = text.replace("The woman cries at your side.", "女人在你身边尖叫起来。");
	text = text.replace("Oh, it is horrible! Horrible!", "噢，太恐怖了！太恐怖了！");
	text = text.replace("Would you look at it?", "你看到了吗？");
	text = text.replace("But it\'s okay, understand?", "但没关系，明白吗？");
	text = text.replace("It\'s perfectly okay.", "完全没关系。");
	text = text.replace("Look at me. Look at me!", "看着我，看着我！");
	text = text.replace("The woman grabs you and spins you.", "那个女人伸出手抱住你。");
	text = text.replace("Her once soft features have hardened into blackened flakes, the top of her head already burnt bald, her teeth falling out of dripping gums. Yet she\'s grinning.", "她那曾经柔美的面容已经成了焦黑的薄片，头顶业燃烧枯涸，牙龈和牙齿都在破碎离析。如此，她仍然咧开嘴笑着。");
	text = text.replace("We\'ll rise again, Emperor!", "我们会复兴的，帝王！");
	text = text.replace("We... shall... rise... again!", "我们…终将…重拾…荣光！");
	text = text.replace("Her skull breaks apart and her body collapses into a pile of burning bones.", "她的颅骨崩溃了，身体也崩塌成一堆燃烧着的骨头。");
	text = text.replace(/You jerk awake to find (.*?) shaking you\./, "你一个激灵醒来，发现 $1 在摇你。");
	text = text.replace("Sir, wakeup! We\'ve got a group of refugees here saying that the dead are rising from the earth and killing everything in sight!", "先生，醒醒，我们在这碰到一群难民说死者从地里复活起来，见一个杀一个！");
	text = text.replace("The woman\'s face flashes before your eyes.", "女人的脸在你眼前一闪而过。");
	text = text.replace("It is horrifically scarred, but this doesn\'t stop her from grinning.", "带着可怕的伤疤，但这没阻止她的笑容。");
	text = text.replace("The Empire rises.", "帝国复生了。");

//undead_necrosavant_event.nut
	text = text.replace("A pile of rubble stands off the side of the path.", "路边有一堆碎石。");
	text = text.replace("There before it is a studious greybeard looking keenly at the stones.", "在它的前面，有一个灰胡子老头正在专注地盯着那些石头。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s so deep in thought he probably wouldn\'t notice if you simply walked on.", "他思考太过投入，大概根本不会注意到你刚刚路过。");
	
	text = text.replace("You\'re not about to leave this poor old sod out here by himself.", "你不能把这个可怜的老家伙一个人留在这儿。");
	text = text.replace("You sidle over to him and ask what he\'s up to.", "你悄悄走到他身边，问他在做什么。");
	text = text.replace("He looks over at you, what must be at least seventy winters having weathered his skin into a leathery and permanent wince. He laughs.", "他看着你，他的皮肤至少要七十个冬天才能磨砺的褶皱斑斑。他笑着说。");
	text = text.replace("Trying to make sense of it all.", "我试图了解这一切。");
	text = text.replace("The dead are rising up out of the earth and, seeing as how I\'m about to shuffle off to a grave of my own any day now, I figured why not be sure I\'m not one to join their ranks?", "死者正在从地下爬起来，眼看着我随时都可能被迫步入自己的坟墓，我想，何不确保自己不会成为他们中的一员呢？");
	text = text.replace("This here was a temple where I was offered purgation as a child.", "这里曾是一个神殿，当我还是个孩子的时候，在这里接受洗礼。");
	text = text.replace("I was also wedded here and saw my only son wedded here as well.", "这里也是我结婚，以及看着我惟一的儿子结婚的地方。");
	text = text.replace("Curious, you ask what destroyed the building.", "激起了你的好奇心，你又问是什么摧毁了这个建筑。");
	text = text.replace("The man laughs again.", "那人又笑了。");
	text = text.replace("People came here asking the same questions I did.", "人们带着和我同样的问题来这里。");
	text = text.replace("Godly questions in a world where the earth has manifested itself deific and rebirthed the dead.", "显示神威，重生死者是只有神才能解决的问题。");
	text = text.replace("Violence was the answer they found - and so they decided to dismantle it stone by stone.", "他们却找到暴力这个答案，于是他们决定一块一块地拆除它。");
	text = text.replace("I\'d admonish them for that, but it\'d be a ruse.", "我原想就此告诫他们，但这也不过是自欺欺人罢了。");
	text = text.replace("I\'d probably do the same as they did had I the means, but, you know, I\'m old as shite and can\'t do much beyond lifting my own fingers.", "如果有办法的话，我可能也会像他们那样做的，但是，你明白吧，我老得要命，除了抬抬手，什么也干不了。");
	text = text.replace("It\'s quite easy to be the pacifist when even a fly can lick your nose free of punishment.", "当一只苍蝇都能肆无忌惮舔你的鼻子时，你就只能成为和平主义者对吧。");
	text = text.replace("His hearty laugh returns.", "他衷心地笑了。");
	text = text.replace("He offers you a silver bowl.", "他给你一个银碗。");
	text = text.replace("Found this in my search.", "我找到了这个碗。");
	text = text.replace("Monks used to splash water in it to cleanse the sick.", "僧侣们过去常常用它泼圣水消除病瘴。");
	text = text.replace("It ain\'t the answer I was looking for, but here, take it.", "这不是我要找的答案，但是，拿去吧。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ve no use for such things.", "这东西这对我没什么用，。");
	text = text.replace("Not now. Not in any sense.", "不仅是当前。从各种意义上都没有。");
	text = text.replace("Good luck out there and if you, you know, see me again like \'that\', please put me out of my misery.", "祝你好运，另外如果，你知道吧，下次看到我是“那个”样子的话，请把我从痛苦中解脱出来。");
	
	text = text.replace("These are dangerous times for even men of strong stock, it sure as hell isn\'t safe for an old fart who has probably lost a couple of marbles.", "即使对那些身强力壮的人来说，这也是一个危险的时代，对一个可能已经神志不清的糟老头来说，绝对不会很安全。");
	text = text.replace("You go over and call out to him.", "你走过去大声叫他。");
	text = text.replace("Instantly, he jerks his head around, eyes flared, the pupils bloated to make his sight a starless abyss.", "他立刻扭过头来，眼睛睁得圆圆的，浮肿的瞳孔让他的眼睛变成没有神色的深渊。");
	text = text.replace("He points a finger right at you.", "他用手指着你。");
	text = text.replace("Your blood. Give it to me.", "你的血。把它给我。");
	text = text.replace("The stranger slowly rises to his feet.", "陌生人慢慢地站了起来。");
	text = text.replace("His cloak falls off his body, revealing a naked skeleton with only the thinnest veneer of flesh.", "他的披风从身上掉了下来，裸露出一具只有很薄一层皮肉裸露的骨架。");
	text = text.replace("He shambles toward you.", "他颤颤巍巍地向你走来。");
	text = text.replace("His mouth is open, but there are no articulations.", "他的嘴是张开的，但没有发音。");
	text = text.replace("He seems to be speaking from some other world entirely.", "声音像是从另一个世界传来的一样。");
	text = text.replace("My reckoning, your crimson, my reckoning, your crimson.", "我的审判，你深红色的，我的审判，你深红色的。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) jumps forward, weapon in hand\./, "$1 手里拿着武器跳出来。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s a sorcerer!", "他是个巫师！");
	text = text.replace("The men arm themselves as the necromancer leans back, his cloak lifting up off the ground and clothing him as though the wind itself were at his beck and call.", "人们武装起来，亡灵巫师向后仰着身子，披风从地上飘起，重新盖住他的身子，就好像风在听从他的召唤。");
	text = text.replace("Suddenly, bodies emerge from the earth, growling and mewling.", "突然，尸体从地下冒出来，咆哮着，哀号着。");
	text = text.replace("He stares at you from beneath the rim of hat slowly lowering over his eyes.", "他从帽沿下慢慢地垂下眼睛，凝视着你。");
	//text = text.replace("So be it.", "就这样吧。");
	
	text = text.replace("Suddenly, a crossbow aims over your shoulder and fires so closely you can feel the air rushing past the twang of its rope.", "突然之间，一把弩越过你的肩膀上发射，在如此之近的地方发射，以至于你能感受到到绳子的当啷声中剧烈振动的空气。");
	text = text.replace("The bolt pierces the old man\'s skull and he tips forward, head to the mud, arse in the air, hands still beside himself in dispirited supination.", "弩箭穿透了老人的脑袋，他向前一倾，屁股朝上一头栽进在泥里，双手以一种颓萎的姿势向后翻着。");
	text = text.replace(/You turn to see (.*?) the witch hunter standing behind you\./, "你转过身看到女巫猎人 $1 站在你后面。");
	text = text.replace("He lowers the crossbow and walks over to the corpse, grabbing it by the nape of the neck and putting a stake through its back.", "他放下弩，走到尸体跟前，抓住尸体的后颈，把一根木桩楔进尸体的背部。");
	text = text.replace("The body wretches with a shriek and the clothing bloats as the body implodes, a swirling dust hurriedly exiting out the cloak as though it had been caught impersonating a man.", "尸体惨叫一声在斗篷里爆裂开，把衣服撑得鼓了起来，一团旋动的粉尘迅速从斗篷里飞了出来，就好像冒充别人被抓了现行。");
	text = text.replace("The witch hunter turns to you.", "女巫猎人转向你。");
	text = text.replace("Necrosavant. Rare. Extremely dangerous.", "吸血鬼。罕见。极其危险。");

//undead_outro_event.nut
	text = text.replace("You take a nap.", "你打了个盹儿。");
	text = text.replace("Blackness. Darkness. All what a dream should be, save for one small fact: you know you\'re in it.", "黑。暗。完全是一个正常的梦境，除了一个小事实：你了解到你在梦里。");
	text = text.replace("Standing in the void like a lost thought.", "像迷惘的思绪伫立于虚空一样。");
	text = text.replace("A voice breaks over you, dripping down from all sides as though you were in the very mouth that produced it.", "一个声音从各个方向向你渗透过来，仿佛你就在那个发出声音的人的嘴里。");
	text = text.replace("Why did you forsake us, Emperor?", "你为什么抛弃我们，帝王？");
	text = text.replace("You spin about, or at least think you do, for there is nothing around with which to base even the faintest of movements.", "你旋转起来，或者说至少你自己以为在转，因为附近什么东西都没有，连最微小的活动的立足点都没有。");
	text = text.replace("You promised me, don\'t you remember?", "你答应过我的，你不记得了吗？");
	text = text.replace("You said it would be okay if it all fell apart.", "你说如果一切都崩溃了也没关系。");
	text = text.replace("You said you had a plan, that you had made a deal with that ugly, ugly man. What happened?", "你说你有个计划，你和那个丑陋的男人做了个交易。发生了什么？");
	
	text = text.replace("You raise your voice.", "你抬高声音。");
	text = text.replace("I am not the chosen one.", "你们要找的不是我。");
	text = text.replace("Before the admission even clear the air, she begins sobbing.", "你的意思还未传达到位，她就开始啜泣起来。");
	text = text.replace("Her words burst through the weeps like hiccupped honesty.", "夹杂在哭泣中她边打着嗝哭诉着。");
	text = text.replace("I-I know... I did not wish to admit it, but I know.", "我－我知道…我原不想承认的，但我确实明白了。");
	text = text.replace("The Empire dies with us.", "帝国和我们一起消亡了。");
	text = text.replace("Sy\'leth daef\'nya, my Emperor.", "亲爱的，我的帝王。");
	text = text.replace("\'Emperor\' echoes, fainter by the repeat, until you are left with darkness and silence.", "“帝王”的回音回荡着，每次重复都更加微弱，最终只留下黑暗和寂静。");
	
	text = text.replace("At first, you say nothing.", "一开始，你什么也没说。");
	text = text.replace("She begins to cry.", "她开始哭了。");
	text = text.replace("You hear the tears, each drop reverberating all around you.", "你听到了泪水的声音，每一滴泪水都在你周围回响。");
	text = text.replace("Are you there, my Emperor?", "你在吗，我的帝王？");
	text = text.replace("You clear your throat and answer.", "你清了清喉咙回答到。");
	text = text.replace("Yes, I am. The Empire will not rise again.", "是我，帝国不会再兴起了。");
	text = text.replace("We must go. There is nothing to fear in Death.", "我们必须得接着走下去了，死亡没有什么可怕的。");
	text = text.replace("The woman weeps, but slowly steadies herself.", "那个女人还是在哭，但慢慢缓和下来。");
	text = text.replace("I am not afraid.", "我并不害怕。");
	text = text.replace("On the other side, ish\'nyarh ishe\'yarn, my Emperor.", "另一件事，是他的故事、他的故事，我的帝王。");
	text = text.replace("As her words fade from the black, and perhaps your mind, all you are left with is silence.", "当她的话从黑暗中消失，也许你的思想，你剩下的只有沉默。");
	
	text = text.replace("You turn about.", "你转过身。");
	text = text.replace("Who is the ugly man?", "那个丑男人是谁？");
	text = text.replace("The woman\'s voice stutters in shock.", "震惊让她结巴了。");
	text = text.replace("You, you don\'t remember?", "你，你都不记得了吗？");
	text = text.replace("Clearing your throat, you feign the honesty of lost memories.", "清了清喉咙，你假装承认你忘了。");
	text = text.replace("I remember nothing, my love.", "是的亲爱的，我什么都不记得了。");
	text = text.replace("A great sigh falls over the darkness.", "黑暗中传来一声长叹。");
	text = text.replace("You can feel its frustration.", "你能感受到蕴藏在之中的沮丧。");
	text = text.replace("She talks with exasperation.", "她恼了。");
	text = text.replace("I knew we should not have trusted him...", "我也知道我们不该相信他…");
	text = text.replace("The ugly man came to us in the night when our child was born still.", "那个丑陋的男人在我们的孩子还没出生的那个晚上来找我们。");
	text = text.replace("He said if he could take our blood, as well as that of our dead child, he would ensure that the Empire would never die, us its eternal rulers.", "他说，如果他能取走我们的血，以及我们死去的孩子的血，他就能确保帝国永远不灭亡，我们也会永远统治下去。");
	text = text.replace("But... it had a cost.", "但是…这有个代价。");
	text = text.replace("You quickly figure it out and respond.", "你一下子就听懂了，回应道。");
	text = text.replace("He made you barren.", "他剥夺了你育子的能力。");
	text = text.replace("The woman sobs.", "那个女人继续哭。");
	text = text.replace("We should have never trusted him!", "我们不应该相信他！");
	text = text.replace("I will have that ugly man!", "我要抓住那个丑男人！");
	text = text.replace("Have no doubt, kearem su\'llah.", "毋庸置疑，凯瑞姆苏拉。");
	text = text.replace("I will treat him to eternity, an eternity of pain and suffering!", "我会让他尝尝永恒的痛苦和折磨！");
	text = text.replace("The once black void glows red, flashing a world of crimson, ferocity in color.", "曾经漆黑的虚空开始泛红，闪出着一个深红色的世界，强烈的红。");
	text = text.replace("You throw a hand up, shielding your eyes.", "你抬起一只手遮住眼睛。");
	text = text.replace("She screams, piercing your ears until all you hear is a harsh ringing.", "她尖叫起来，刺痛你的耳朵，直到你剧烈耳鸣。");
	
	text = text.replace("You wake. A rough wind bends the tent, curling the leather and rolling tides across the ceiling.", "你醒来了。一阵狂风压弯了帐篷，卷起帐篷的皮革像浪潮一样拍打着顶棚。");
	text = text.replace(/Faint candlelight flicks and dashes darkness and light all the same\. (.*?) is standing there, watching you, shadows crossing back and forth across his chest\./, "微弱的烛光摇晃着驱赶着黑暗。$1 站在那里看着你，影子跳动着在他的胸前明灭不定。");
	text = text.replace("He shifts on his feet, an uneasy look on his face.", "他不断换着支撑的腿，脸上露出不安的神色。");
	text = text.replace("Who were you talking to?", "你刚在和谁说话？");
	text = text.replace("Rolling out of bed, you put your boots to the ground, wanting to be sure of this reality before you dare parlay with it.", "翻下床，你把靴子叩在地上，打算在说事情之前先搞清楚是否处于现实世界。");
	text = text.replace("Dirt rustles and crunches beneath your feet. You answer.", "泥土踩在你脚下咯吱作响。你回答道。");
	text = text.replace("I\'m not sure. I think... I think the invasion is over.", "我也不知道，但我认为…我想危机已经结束了。");
	text = text.replace("The mercenary nods and turns a hand to the tent\'s entrance.", "佣兵点头，把手转向帐篷的入口。");
	text = text.replace("Aye, that\'s why I\'m here.", "是啊，这就是我来这里的原因。");
	text = text.replace("A noble messenger arrived just a minute ago.", "一分钟前一个高贵的信使来了。");
	text = text.replace("He says the undead have ceased erupting from the ground.", "他说亡灵已经停止从地面出现。");
	text = text.replace("The scribes believe it is over.", "书记员相信这一切都结束了。");
	text = text.replace("Are you alright, sir?", "先生，你还好吧？");
	text = text.replace("You rub your head.", "你挠挠头。");
	text = text.replace("Is it time to retire?", "是时候退休了吗？");
	text = text.replace("What can you make of this world now that you know what you do?", "既然你知道你在做什么，你能为这个世界做些什么？");
	text = text.replace(/It is either go live out the rest of your days in peace, or say damn it all and command the (.*?) to further glory\./, "要么平静地度过你的余生，要么诅咒这一切，并率领 $1 追寻更大的荣耀。");
	text = text.replace("You\'ve won! Battle Brothers is designed for replayability and for campaigns to be played until you\'ve beaten one or two late game crises.", "你已经胜利了！战场兄弟是为可重玩性和战役而设计的，直到你在游戏后期打败了一两次危机。");
	text = text.replace("Starting a new campaign will allow you to try out different things in a different world.", "开始一个新的战役会让你在不同的世界尝试不同的东西。");
	text = text.replace("That said, you can choose to continue your campaign for as long as you want.", "也就是说，你可以选择继续你的战役，只要你想。");
	text = text.replace("Just be aware that campaigns are not intended to last forever and you\'re likely to run out of challenges eventually.", "只是要意识到，战役并不是要永远持续下去的，你可能最终会尝尽所有的挑战。");

//undead_plague_or_infected_event.nut
	text = text.replace("You come across a group of peasants sitting by the edge of the path.", "你偶然遇到一群坐在路边的农民。");
	text = text.replace("Men, women, children. Dirtied clothes, muddied boots, sores on their skin.", "男人，女人，孩子。衣服很脏，靴子满是泥泞，皮肤都溃烂了。");
	text = text.replace("A few carry wounds shaped like bitemarks.", "有些人带着像是咬痕的伤口。");
	text = text.replace("The eldest of the party speaks.", "队伍的长者说。");
	text = text.replace("Please, sir, do you have any food or water to give us?", "拜托了，先生，你有吃的或水能给我们吗？");
	text = text.replace("He seems to see you eyeing the pustules and bitemarks.", "他似乎看到你在盯着脓疱和咬痕。");
	//text = text.replace("He shakes his head.", "他摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("Oh, don\'t mind those.", "噢，别介意那些。");
	text = text.replace("Simple fox huntin\' gone awry.", "仅仅是的猎狐出了点问题。");
	text = text.replace("We could just use a bit of help and then we can be on our way.", "我们只需要一点点帮助，然后我们就可以自己走了。");
	
	text = text.replace("You command these sickened souls to be well - by commanding your men to kill them all.", "你命令手下善待他们－通过把他们全部杀掉。");
	text = text.replace("The elder leads the women and children away while the men rise up to stand their ground.", "长者带着妇女和小孩离开，一边男人们从地上站了起来。");
	text = text.replace("One, wavering on green and peeling legs, points at you.", "其中一个，摇晃着泛着碧绿色开始蜕皮的腿，指着你。");
	text = text.replace("What a saint you are ya prick.", "你这混蛋可真是个大善人啊。");
	text = text.replace("I hope I do come back from the dead.", "我真希望我会复活成亡灵。");
	text = text.replace("I hope my corpse kills the lot of you ya farkin\' savages.", "这样我的尸体就能杀死你们这些该死的野蛮人。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You tell (.*?) to hand out some food and supplies\./, "你让 $1 分发一些食物和用品。");
	text = text.replace(/The elder thanks you and says he\'ll speak highly of the (.*?) wherever he goes\./, "长者一边感谢一边说，无论他走到哪里，他都会高度赞扬 $1。");
	text = text.replace("A few of the men seem relieved that you didn\'t ask something awful of them.", "有几个人因为你没有做过分的事，似乎松了一口气。");
	
	text = text.replace(/You tell (.*?) to hand out some food and supplies\./, "你让 $1 分发一些食物和用品。");
	text = text.replace(/The elder thanks you and says he\'ll speak highly of the (.*?) wherever he goes\./, "长者一边感谢一边说，无论他走到哪里，他都会高度赞扬 $1。");
	text = text.replace("Taking a piece of bread, you squat beside a sickly child and the father holding him.", "拿着一块面包，你蹲在一个父亲抱着的生病的孩子旁边。");
	text = text.replace("But when you hold the loaf out, the child turns its head up and bites into his father\'s neck.", "但是当你递出一片面包的时候，这个孩子却抬起头来，咬住了他父亲的脖子。");
	text = text.replace("Any peasant healthy enough to stand does so and runs off.", "任何一个只要还够健康能站起来的农民都跑了。");
	text = text.replace("The rest... well, the rest shamble to their feet, faces pale, jaws slacked, eyes glowing red with furious hunger.", "剩下的...剩下的摇摇晃晃地站起来，脸色苍白，下巴松弛，眼睛因狂乱的饥饿而发红。");
	text = text.replace("You quickly order the mercenaries into formation.", "你赶快命令雇佣兵们组成阵型。");

//undead_town_destroyed_event.nut
	text = text.replace("You come across a donkey standing beside a cart full of burnt corpses.", "你碰到一头驴子站在一辆装满烧焦尸体的车旁。");
	text = text.replace("A man stands beside it looking, understandably, worse for the wear.", "一名男子站在它旁边，可以理解的是，他看起来衣衫褴褛。");
	text = text.replace("He looks at you and shakes his head.", "他看着你，摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace(/Hope yer not heading to (.*?)\./, "希望你们不要去 $1。");
	text = text.replace("Not one to tell strangers where you\'re heading, you simply ask him why.", "没有人会告诉陌生人你要去哪里，你只需问他为什么。");
	text = text.replace("He shakes his head a second time.", "他第二次摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("Walking dead got it.", "行尸明白了吗。");
	text = text.replace("Disease spread through the town and those who were dying kept rising up again.", "恶疾在城里蔓延开来，那些即将死去的人又重新站了起来。");
	text = text.replace("Wasn\'t long until the whole place fell to those undying souls.", "没过多久，整个地方都落入了那些不死的灵魂的手中。");
	text = text.replace("Word has it that the city is now governed by necromancers, but who really knows.", "据说这座城市现在由亡灵巫师统治，但谁知道呢。");
	text = text.replace("I sure as hell ain\'t gonna get close to find out.", "我绝对不可能靠近那里去调查。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s a pale greybeard squatting in the middle of the path.", "一个苍白的灰胡子人蹲在路中间。");
	text = text.replace("He hears you coming, but doesn\'t turn to look.", "他听到你来了，但没有回头看。");
	text = text.replace("Instead he simply speaks.", "相反，他只是说话。");
	text = text.replace("Saw you in the vision. All of you.", "在异象中看见你。你们所有的人。");
	text = text.replace("Sellswords on the path to righting the ills of this world, though ye might not know this purpose any better than a royal infant understands its kingly place.", "正在纠正世间谬误道路上的佣兵，尽管你们可能不知道事情的本质，就像一个皇家婴儿不知道它的王权地位一样。");
	text = text.replace("But you\'re too late.", "但是你们太迟了。");
	text = text.replace("His head snaps around.", "他的脑袋扭来扭去。");
	text = text.replace("White eyes stare out from beneath bushy eyebrows.", "浓密的眉毛下露出一双白白的眼睛。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s missing a nose and his lips sneer with sickly yellow creases.", "他缺了一个鼻子，他的嘴唇上布满黄色的皱纹。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) is lost! The dead wander the streets, leashed by the ones you call necromancers\./, "$1 沦陷了！死者在街上游荡，被你称为亡灵巫师的人控制着。");
	text = text.replace("Carefully, you tread forward and ask how he knows any of this.", "你小心翼翼地走上前去，问他是怎么知道这些的。");
	text = text.replace("The pale man holds up a round bauble that ripples as though a god were holding the shape of a pond in his palm.", "脸色苍白的人手里拿着一个圆形的小玩意，上面的波纹荡漾开来，就好像一个神手里拿着一个池塘形状的东西。");
	text = text.replace("Images twist in its reflections, coming and going, events with no start or end. He laughs.", "图像在它的倒影中扭曲，来来去去，显示的事件无始无终。他笑着说。");
	text = text.replace("Who better to know the fate of the city than the man who orchestrated its demise?", "谁能比那个安排城市灭亡的人更了解这个城市的命运呢？");
	text = text.replace("Suddenly, the stranger\'s flesh shatters, revealing nothing but air beneath, and the blackened shards of his new form spread out into a cloud of bats.", "突然，这个陌生人的皮肉粉碎了，下面只露出空气，他的新身体的黑色碎片展开成一团蝙蝠。");
	text = text.replace("You draw out your sword, but the creatures wheel away, shrieking and chirping as they soar toward the horizon.", "你拔出剑，但那些动物却转身走开了，一边尖叫一边向地平线飞去。");
	text = text.replace("Two men are found off the side of the path.", "在路边发现了两个人。");
	text = text.replace("One is standing before an easel, in one hand a brush, in the other a palette of mixed colors.", "一个人站在画架前，一只手拿着画笔，另一只手里拿着调着各色颜料的调色板。");
	text = text.replace("The other man is posing, hands to his head, holding an expression of absolute horror.", "另一个人摆着姿势，双手放在头上，保持着绝对是恐怖的表情。");
	text = text.replace("The painter glances at you.", "画家瞥了你一眼。");
	text = text.replace("Ah, sellswords. I suppose you\'re heading toward city, yeah?", "唉，佣兵们。我猜你们要去城里面，对嘛？");
	text = text.replace("You ask why he would say that.", "你问他为什么这么说。");
	text = text.replace("He nervously puts the brush down.", "他紧张地把刷子放下。");
	text = text.replace("You see his painting is of a darkened city with blue miasma rising out from behind its walls, a pale moon hovering oppressively overhead.", "你看他的画是一个黑暗的城市，蓝色的瘴气从高墙后升起，苍白的月亮令人窒息地压在头顶上。");
	text = text.replace("A half-painted figure stands in the foreground, mirroring the look of the painter\'s model.", "一个画了一半的人站在前景中，映射着画家模特儿的表情。");
	text = text.replace("Without moving an inch, the poser answers your question.", "没有丝毫动作，做模特的人回答了你的问题。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?)\'s been destroyed\. Well, not destroyed, but overrun with those walking corpses\./, "$1 已经被摧毁了。好吧，不是被摧毁了，而是被亡灵颠覆了。");
	text = text.replace("Word has it that pale men hold governance over it.", "据说苍白之人支配着那里。");
	text = text.replace("You ask if they know this for sure.", "你问情况是否属实。");
	text = text.replace("The painter waves an arm to present his work.", "画家挥舞着双手展示他的作品说到。");
	text = text.replace("Had I not seen it with my own eyes, would this not be the work of a madman?", "如果不是我亲眼所见，这难道不是疯子的杰作吗？");
	text = text.replace("Now, please, I must get back to work before the macabre memory fades.", "现在，请吧，我必须在可怕的记忆消失之前回去工作。");

//undead_warnings_event.nut
	text = text.replace("While stopping for a brief respite, a stranger approaches the camp.", "在短暂休息时，一个陌生人走近营地。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s got a wooden stake for a leg, though he wobbles on it with practiced efficiency.", "他找了根木桩代替腿，然而他能熟练地摇摇晃晃的走。");
	text = text.replace("Hobbling to you, he tips a cap of broomstraw.", "他一瘸一拐地走到你跟前，手里拿着一顶扫帚草帽。");
	text = text.replace("I suppose you fellas are here for the happenings?", "我猜你们是来看热闹的吧？");
	text = text.replace(/You glance at (.*?) then back to the man\. He shrugs\./, "你看了眼 $1 然后看向那个人。他耸耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("Ah, mayhaps ye don\'t know.", "唉，也许你不知道。");
	text = text.replace("I don\'t really know, either, but there be a lot of grisly stories about what is happening all around these parts.", "我也不很清楚，但是我知道关于这附近正在上演的事的一些消息。");
	text = text.replace("The way I hear it, the dead are walking the earth, but that\'s hogwash.", "我听到的说法是，死人们在地面上走来走去，但那不是狗屁吗。");
	text = text.replace("I think it\'s just a bunch of brigands with new tricks up their sleeves.", "我认为那不过是一群突发奇想的强盗罢了。");
	text = text.replace("Anyway, be seeing you.", "不管怎样，再见。");
	text = text.replace("Stay safe and all that malarkey.", "注意安全，刚说的都是胡扯哈哈。");
	text = text.replace("The man laughs as he stilts away.", "那个人笑着蹦跳离开了。");
	text = text.replace("A child is found beside the path with a skull laid between their legs.", "在小路旁边发现了一个孩子，两腿间夹着一个头骨。");
	text = text.replace("Its upside down with insects battling one another in the bowl of the brainpan.", "昆虫在那个倒置的头骨里里互相争斗。");
	text = text.replace("The kid briefly looks up.", "孩子抬头简单看了你一眼。");
	text = text.replace("Hi there.", "你好啊。");
	text = text.replace("You ask where his parents are.", "你问他的父母在哪里。");
	text = text.replace("He picks up a dead bug from the skull, looks at it, then tosses it over his shoulder.", "他从头盖骨里捡起一只死虫子，看了看，然后把它扔到身后。");
	text = text.replace("He puts another wriggling gladiator into the grey arena then stares at you.", "捡起另一个扭来扭去的角斗士，把它放进灰色的竞技场，然后看着你。");
	text = text.replace("Parents? Why they ain\'t been around for awhile.", "父母？为什么他们好一段时间都没出现了。");
	text = text.replace("Father went to his parents, and mother to hers.", "父亲去找他的父母，母亲去找她的父母。");
	text = text.replace("And they both was ate\'n.", "所以他俩都不在。");
	text = text.replace("You raise an eyebrow and ask for him to repeat what he just said, but the kid ignores you, absentmindedly cheering into the hollow head as his bugs do battle.", "你挑了挑眉毛，让他再说一遍，但他没理你，心不在焉地对着空洞脑袋里正进行的战斗欢呼。");
	text = text.replace("You come to a man standing in the path.", "你走到一个站在路上的人面前。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s got a shovel yoked over both shoulders, his hands crucifixed across each side, and he\'s dripping with mud.", "把铁锹横跨搭在两个肩膀上，双手放在两端，身上还滴着泥水。");
	text = text.replace("He glances up, this golem of earth, and asks where you\'re going.", "这个大地魔像一样的人，抬头瞥向你，问你要去哪里。");
	text = text.replace("Before you answer, he interrupts.", "你还没回答，他就又打断了。");
	text = text.replace("Don\'t go that way.", "不要走那条路。");
	text = text.replace("Don\'t go no way.", "那条路走不通。");
	text = text.replace("They\'re everywhere. I was digging, you see?", "他们到处都是。我正在挖，你看到了吗？");
	text = text.replace("Digging to get to them first.", "先挖到他们。");
	text = text.replace("But they know. They where we are.", "但他们知道。他们知道我们在哪儿。");
	text = text.replace("Don\'t go nowhere, because they\'re everywhere.", "哪也别去，因为他们无处不在。");
	text = text.replace("Don\'t go nowhere, because they\'re everywhere, and they know... they know, don\'t you see?", "哪也别去，因为他们无处不在，他们知道…他们知道，你没看见吗？");
	text = text.replace("He presses his head forward, his cringing face crooning forth from his dripping arms like some muddied bat come to feast on your dreams.", "他把头伸向前，畏缩的脸从他的滴着泥水的胳膊伸出来低低地唱着，像沾泥的蝙蝠要来吃你的梦。");
	text = text.replace(/You ease past the man\. (.*?) looks him up and down, shrugs, and follows you\./, "你轻易地越过了那个人。$1 上下打量着他，耸耸肩，然后跟上了你。");
	text = text.replace(/The (.*?) has no time for such madmen\./, "$1 可没时间耗在疯子身上。");
	text = text.replace(/While on the road, you come to a small, empty hut. (.*?) snoops around inside, you beside him, the both of you with blades out\./, "在路上，你来到一个小而空的小屋。$1 在里面看了看，你在他旁边，都抽出了利刃。");
	//text = text.replace("He shakes his head.", "他摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("Ain\'t shit here.", "他妈的不在这儿。");
	text = text.replace("He looks up and points.", "他抬起头指了指。");
	text = text.replace("Except there.", "除了那儿。");
	text = text.replace("You look up and see that the ceiling is covered in blood.", "你抬头看见天花板上全是血。");
	text = text.replace("Not just covered... written over.", "不是溅到上面…而人为写满了。");
	text = text.replace("Unfortunately, the script is hard to read as the crimson words are muddied by mold and termitic erasure.", "不幸的是，字迹很难读，因为深红色的字被霉菌覆盖和白蚁啮食弄得模糊不清。");
	text = text.replace("You mouth the visible letters: DO---GO---IDE---WE---LL---R---OOMED.", "你含糊地读出几个能看清的字：做－走－主意－我们－来－干－毁灭。");
	text = text.replace("Clearly the work of a madman.", "显然是一个疯子的杰作。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s a copse in the path, a little set of trees that stand tall in an otherwise flat clearing.", "小路上有一片小树林，一小片树林高高耸立在原本平坦的空地上。");
	text = text.replace("You take some respite there, for little trees such as these borrow the silence and sereneness from their larger forest cousins.", "你在那里稍作休息，因为像这样的小树能从它们在森林里的亲戚那里偷得宁静和安详。");
	text = text.replace("Except not this one.", "可是这个要除外。");
	text = text.replace("This one you find a dead child in the bushes.", "在这个灌木丛中你发现一个死去的孩子。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) comes up and covers his mouth\./, "$1 捂着嘴走上前。");
	text = text.replace("By the might of the old gods, who would do such a thing?", "以旧神的名义，谁会干这种事？");
	text = text.replace("You take a knee.", "你单膝跪地。");
	text = text.replace("There are tracks all over the area.", "地上有很多足迹。");
	text = text.replace("It appears the kid was chased and ended up running into the bushes.", "似乎是这个小孩被什么东西追赶，最终跑进了这个小灌木丛里。");
	text = text.replace("Probably got tied up there, stuck.", "可能是被什么勾住了，困在这里。");
	text = text.replace("More footsteps followed. Way more.", "更多足迹追寻过来。还有更多。");
	text = text.replace("They stayed for a while, then left with bloody footprints.", "然后留下带血的足迹离开。");
	text = text.replace("The kid, what is left of him, is covered in bite marks.", "这个小孩，剩下的躯体，被咬痕所覆盖。");
	text = text.replace("You turn to the mercenary and answer.", "你转向佣兵们，回答到。");
	text = text.replace("I think it\'s a matter of what, not who.", "我认为这是什么东西，而不是谁干了这种事。");
	text = text.replace("But they\'re gone. Somewhere yonder, a few days ahead I\'d wager, but...", "但是他们已经离开了。我敢打赌，就在我们前方两三天路程的地方，但是…");
	text = text.replace("You count the footsteps, but they prove too many.", "你数了数脚印，但是太多数不过来。");
	text = text.replace("I think whatever did this... we\'ll be seeing it soon.", "我想不管那是啥…我们很快就能见到他了。");
	text = text.replace("You come to a man standing with a white banner, an unthreaded sigil in the middle, its frayed remains billowing in the wind. He nods.", "你走进一个举着白色旗帜站在那的男人，旗帜中间是一个抽线的印章，饱经磨损的残留仍在风中飘扬。他点头。");
	text = text.replace("Good to see some flesh.", "能看到鲜活的肉真是太好了。");
	text = text.replace("Well, that was not what you were expecting as his first words.", "好吧，这样的开场白是你没预料到的。");
	text = text.replace("Naturally, you inquire as to what he means. He looks incredulous.", "很自然的，你问他什么意思。他看起来有点怀疑。");
	text = text.replace("You know, flesh. As opposed to bones.", "鲜活的肉。而不是白骨。");
	text = text.replace("I\'ve seen too many of those lately so, yeah, it\'s nice seeing some flesh.", "我最近看到太多这种东西了，所以，是的，看到鲜活的肉真不错。");
	text = text.replace("You inquire further, asking what kind of bones this man has been seeing.", "你继续问，这人看见的是什么骨头。");
	text = text.replace("He slims his eyes as if guarding them against the winds of a past he\'d prefer to forget.", "他眯起眼睛，好像是要阻挡他更愿意忘记的追来的吹自过去的风。");
	text = text.replace("The walkin\' kind. Bones that\'ll walk through your door in the middle of the night.", "能走的东西。半夜闯进门的骨头。");
	text = text.replace("Bones that kill everything in front of them.", "杀死所有在他们面前的东西的骨头。");
	text = text.replace("Bones that want to see more bones just like them.", "想看到更多和他们一样的骨头。");
	text = text.replace("Them sort of bones, got it?", "真的就是那种，那种骨头，你懂了吗？");
	text = text.replace("His face lightens up, the eyes widening.", "他睁大眼睛，的脸色亮了起来。");
	text = text.replace("He pivots toward you and suddenly leans forward.", "他突然转身，向你倾了点。");
	text = text.replace("You wouldn\'t happen to be made of bones, would you?", "你应该不会碰巧是骨头做的吧，嗯？");
	text = text.replace(/Sensing a threat in the words, (.*?) jumps in, positioning to kill the man before he can act\./, "觉察到言语中的威胁，$1 跳到你前面，做出在那名男子行动之前就结果他的姿态。");
	text = text.replace("You settle everyone down.", "你让所有人都冷静一下。");
	text = text.replace(/The stranger appears at ease, but you order the (.*?) to walk around him with care\./, "陌生人显得很惬意，但是你让 $1 小心围住他。");
	text = text.replace("He doesn\'t move. He simply stands as the last tendrils of his banner unravel into the wind.", "他根本没动，只是简单站在那里，任旗帜的最后一丝线缕飘入风中。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s a man in the path.", "在路上有一个人。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s on his hands and knees with scrolls littered all around.", "他伏在地上，手边到处都是散落的卷轴。");
	text = text.replace("He bounds from one to the other like a dog would a scattering of treats.", "他不停从一个卷轴跳到另一个，就像狗把东西弄满地东西那样玩一样。");
	//text = text.replace("He shakes his head.", "他摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("No no no, no!", "不，不，不，不！");
	text = text.replace("Where is it? Ah! Stranger!", "我弄哪去了？啊！陌生人！");
	text = text.replace("I mean, uh, sellsword, er, friend! Friend?", "我是说，呃，佣兵，呃，朋友！朋友？");
	text = text.replace("You ask what the man is doing.", "你问这个人在做什么。");
	text = text.replace("His hands are shaking as he answers.", "他手抖着回答道。");
	text = text.replace("I, uh, have a theory.", "我，呃，有个想法。");
	text = text.replace("About who we are, er, were. In the past.", "关于我们是谁，呃，曾经是。在过去。");
	text = text.replace("Way before today, understand? Of course you do.", "今天的很久之前，你明白吗？你当然知道的。");
	text = text.replace("You watch as the man gathers his notes, stuffing them into a satchel. He continues.", "你看着那个人整理他的笔记，把它们塞进一个袋子里。他继续道。");
	text = text.replace("I think our past is coming to haunt us again, my dear sir sellsword friend, and when they come, they will kill us all.", "我想我们的过去又开始困扰我们了，亲爱的佣兵朋友先生，当他们来的时候，他们会把我们所有人都杀了。");
	text = text.replace("Because they want it back.", "因为他们想取回。");
	text = text.replace("They want it ALL back.", "他们想要全部收回。");
	text = text.replace("The man throws the satchel over his shoulder and nods.", "那人把袋子扔在肩上，点了点头。");
	text = text.replace("Now I have others to inform.", "现在我还要去通知别人。");
	text = text.replace("Thanks for listening and, uh, farewell.", "谢谢你听了这么会儿，呃，那么再见。");
	text = text.replace("Well... bye.", "好吧…再见。");
	text = text.replace("While marching, something crunches awkwardly underfoot.", "行军时，有什么东西在脚下发出了怪异的嘎吱嘎吱声。");
	text = text.replace("You stop and take a knee to see.", "你停下来，单膝着地。");
	text = text.replace("Swiping away some dirt, you find splintered shards of pottery.", "擦去一些泥土，发现裂开的陶器的碎块。");
	text = text.replace("They appear to be, or used to be, part of a piece of art.", "它们好像是，或者曾经是，一件艺术品的一部分。");
	text = text.replace(/You piece them together until a picture comes into view\. (.*?) stands behind you and asks\./, "你把它们拼在一起，一个图画出现在你面前。$1 站在你后面问。");
	text = text.replace("So, what is that?", "那是啥？");
	text = text.replace("You trace a finger along the artwork.", "你用一根指头拂过工艺品。");
	text = text.replace("Depicted are armored soldiers with spears and behind them more men stand with polearms, their formation as thick as the forests from which they made their weapons.", "上面刻画着全副武装的手持矛的士兵，身后有更多使用长柄兵器的士兵，他们的阵型和森林一样厚密，他们的武器是由森林制作的。");
	text = text.replace("They appear to be marching forward one step at a time, cutting down all the enemies in their path with brutal efficiency.", "他们看起来一步一步向前行进，以残忍的效率消灭所有挡住道路的敌人。");
	text = text.replace("You try and pick the shards up.", "你试着把碎片捡起来。");
	text = text.replace("A low hum emits from the clay and each piece suddenly turns to powder, the remains streaming between your fingers.", "从粘土里发出一种低沉的嗡嗡声，然后每个碎块都突然变成了粉末，从你指缝里流走。");
	text = text.replace("Something that old... that peculiar... what is it doing out here in the middle of nowhere?", "这么古老…奇特…的东西。为什么在这个地方呢？");
	text = text.replace("An odd figure shuffles across the path.", "一个奇怪的人影拖着脚穿过小路。");
	text = text.replace("You draw your sword and follow, eventually creeping behind a small girl holding an infant.", "你拔出剑，跟在后面，最后慢慢跟到了一个抱着婴儿的小女孩身后。");
	text = text.replace("The child wheels around to look at you, the bundled babe in her arms comfortably asleep.", "女孩转过身来看了看你，襁褓里的婴儿正舒舒服服地在她的怀里睡着。");
	text = text.replace("You ask what they are doing way out here. The girl shrugs.", "你问他们在外面干什么。这个女孩耸耸肩。");
	text = text.replace("Running from the bads.", "逃离邪恶的东西。");
	text = text.replace("You cautiously glance around before asking what she means.", "在问她什么意思之前，你仔细地环顾四周。");
	text = text.replace("She responds as if the answer to the question is tiresomely obvious.", "她回答的时候好像问题的答案太明显了。");
	text = text.replace("The bads. We buried them good, but they came up bad.", "坏蛋。我们把它们埋得很好，但它们却坏了。");
	text = text.replace("Now they\'re killing everyone.", "现在他们要杀了所有人。");
	text = text.replace("So I run. I run from the bads.", "所以我跑了。我逃避那些坏蛋。");
	text = text.replace("She peers down at the infant and then out toward the land.", "她低头看着婴儿，然后朝外面的地面望去。");
	text = text.replace("Excuse me, sir. My grandfather lives yonder.", "劳驾，先生。我的祖父住在那边。");
	text = text.replace("He is expecting me and me alone.", "他在等我，就等我一个人。");
	text = text.replace("You grab her shoulder and ask where her parents are.", "你抓住她的肩膀，问她父母在哪里。");
	text = text.replace("She shrugs off your hand.", "她甩开你的手。");
	text = text.replace("They\'re with the bads.", "他们和坏人在一起。");
	text = text.replace("Now excuse me, I must get going.", "对不起，我必须得动身了。");
	text = text.replace("Clutching the baby, the girl quickly ducks into some brush.", "女孩抱着孩子，迅速没入灌木丛中。");
	text = text.replace("Such a little thing, she hardly makes a noise thereafter, and you\'ve little doubt that her safe silence will see her to her destination.", "她还这么小，之后几乎没发出任何声音，你几乎不怀疑，她的轻巧会让她安全到达目的地。");
	text = text.replace("You come to an old woman in the road.", "你在路上遇到一位老太太。");
	text = text.replace("She waves you down with one hand while the other clutches her neck.", "她一只手捂着脖子，另一只手向你挥手示意。");
	text = text.replace("As you get closer, you see that her white hairs are waning, leaving a dome of her skull revealed, and her garish nose wheeze with every breath.", "当你走近时，你发现她的白头发日趋势微，露出了脑门的一部分，她那滑稽的鼻子随着每一次呼吸都呼哧呼哧地响。");
	text = text.replace("Age has been most unkind in all resorts.", "年龄在任何方面都很不友好。");
	text = text.replace("Her words are expectedly labored.", "可以预见她说话很吃力。");
	text = text.replace("Have you seen an old man on the roads?", "你在路上看到一个老头吗？");
	text = text.replace("Shaking your head, you ask what happened to her.", "你摇着头，问她发生了什么事。");
	text = text.replace("She reveals her neck from which there are two holes.", "她露出有两个洞的脖子。");
	text = text.replace("A bit of pus flows from each until she covers back up.", "两个洞都在流脓，直到她重新用手捂住。");
	text = text.replace("My husband and I were attacked last night.", "我和我丈夫昨晚被袭击了。");
	text = text.replace("I don\'t know where he is.", "我不知道他在哪里。");
	text = text.replace("I think they took him.", "我想他们带走了他。");
	text = text.replace("They tried to take me, but the man attacking me must\'ve smelled something foul because he got but a small taste before running off.", "他们想带走我，但那个袭击我的人一定是闻到了什么难闻的东西，因为他只尝了一小口就逃跑了。");
	text = text.replace("Maybe it was my cooking.", "也许是我做的饭。");
	text = text.replace("I always add too much garlic.", "我总是放太多的大蒜。");
	text = text.replace("My husband, he skipped dinner that night, that grouchy fool.", "我丈夫那天晚上没吃饭，那个爱发牢骚的笨蛋。");
	text = text.replace("You put up a hand, slowing her down.", "你举起一只手，让她慢下来。");
	text = text.replace("You tell her to carefully explain who or what actually attacked.", "你要求她仔细解释到底是谁或什么东西攻击了她。");
	text = text.replace("She nods and responds.", "她点头回应。");
	text = text.replace("Right, it was...", "好吧，那是…");
	text = text.replace("She pauses and her eyes seem to change attention, as if she blinked without closing a single eyelid.", "她停顿了一下，她的目光似乎突然改变了聚焦，就好像根本没有动过眼皮地眨眼了一样。");
	text = text.replace("She glances back at you and smiles.", "她回头瞥了你一眼，笑了。");
	text = text.replace("Hello, have you seen an old man on the roads?", "你好，你在路上看到一个老头了吗？");
	text = text.replace("He\'s my husband. We were attacked last night and I think they took him...", "那是我的丈夫。我们昨晚被袭击了，我想他们把他带走了…");
	text = text.replace("You come to a tiny little town by the side of the path.", "你来到了路边的一个小镇。");
	text = text.replace("An insular place where no doubt everyone knows everyone.", "一个与世隔绝的地方，毫无疑问，这里的人们互相都认识。");
	text = text.replace("Outside one of the hovels, there\'s the charred remains of a bonfire.", "在一间小屋外，有一堆烧焦的篝火残留物。");
	text = text.replace("The sickly black shape of a person is in the ruins.", "一个黢黑的病恹恹的人躺在废墟里。");
	text = text.replace("One of the townspeople comes over, tipping their strawhat up while tenting their hands on a pitchfork.", "一个镇民过来了，双手搭在干草叉上，掀开草帽。");
	text = text.replace("He speaks rather cheerily.", "他说话相当愉快。");
	text = text.replace("That right there is taking care of a problem once and for all.", "那儿正打算彻底的解决问题。");
	text = text.replace("Curious, you ask what happened.", "出于好奇，你问发生了什么事。");
	text = text.replace("The man answers earnestly, as if happy to relive the moments.", "那人认真地回答，仿佛很高兴能重温那一刻。");
	text = text.replace(/Well, that there deadened thing you see used to be (.*?)\. The man lived yonder from here, in the backend parts of this backend town\./, "嗯，你看到的死掉的的东西曾经是 $1。那个人就住在离这儿不远的地方，在这个后端城市的后端。");
	text = text.replace("He used to do readings, like you know, from bones and blood or some sorry sortition.", "他过去经常阅读，就像你知道的那样，从骨头和血液中，或者一些令人感到不好的东西。");
	text = text.replace("Fool kept going on and on about how the dead were going to come back and kill us all.", "傻瓜不停地说着死人会怎样回来把我们都杀了。");
	text = text.replace("We don\'t take kindly to shamanistic reckonings so we gave him the straight-and-narrow side of what is right and lawful.", "我们无法对这种萨满式的审判保持仁慈，所以我们让他见识了正确又合法行为直接并且没度量的一面。");
	text = text.replace("The man spits and nods.", "那个男人啐了一口，点头。");
	//text = text.replace("And that was that.", "就这样。");
	text = text.replace("Almost as if on cue, the bonfire crumbles and the boneshards scatter.", "好像回应一样，篝火的残留物崩塌了，骨头碎片也四散。");
	text = text.replace("A plume of ash and smoke are all that remain.", "只剩下一团灰烬和飘升的烟。");
	text = text.replace("You come across a graveyard off to the side of the path.", "你在小路的一旁看到一片墓地。");
	text = text.replace("The place is a mess.", "这地方一片狼藉。");
	text = text.replace("The plots are uncovered and the gravestones overturned and scattered.", "罐子被打开，墓碑被推翻散落一地。");
	text = text.replace("It is as if a horde of graverobbers descended upon the place and picked it clean.", "就好像一群盗墓贼降临到到这个地方，把它搜刮得干干净净。");
	text = text.replace(/Except\.\.\. they took the bodies too\? (.*?) stands at your side and shakes his head\./, "除了…他们连尸体也带走了？$1 站在你旁边摇了摇头。");
	text = text.replace("Cannibals?", "食人族？");
	text = text.replace("This was not the work of cannibals, but you nod for that answer is more calming then what might be the truth: whatever was buried here got up and left on their own two feet...", "这不是食人族干的事，但你点头表示同意，因为这个答案相比可能的真相更能让人心安：埋在这里的东西都爬了起来，用自己的双腿离开了…");
	text = text.replace(/While marching, you come across an abandoned camp\. (.*?) walks through it and kick over a pan slick with oil\./, "行军时，你遇到一个废弃的营地。$1 走过去，踢翻一个还有油的平底锅。");
	text = text.replace("Rotten bacon and eggs spill into the grass.", "腐烂的培根和鸡蛋洒到草地上。");
	text = text.replace("He turns his attention to some bags but comes up empty.", "他把注意转到几个包上，但那是空的。");
	text = text.replace("The ground reveals fresh footprints.", "地面上露出了了新鲜的脚印。");
	text = text.replace("A clutter of them circle around what was the fire, but there is no dance in their evidence, instead it seems they were frantically rushing to and fro.", "在曾经是火的地方散乱围成一个圆，没有迹象表明跳过舞，相反，他们似乎在发疯似地跑来跑去。");
	text = text.replace("Marching toward them is a horde of prints, shuffling and dragging their feet with no order.", "有一大群脚印朝他们奔来，拖着脚没有秩序地行进。");
	text = text.replace("And then, as these two storied prints meet, only the latter continues forward.", "在这之后，这两拨痕迹相遇，只留下了后者继续推进。");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) pulls back a bush to reveal a dead body\./, "$1 拉过一撮灌木丛，露出一具尸体。");
	text = text.replace("There\'s a shovel firmly slotted into its skull.", "有一把铁锹牢牢地插在它的脑袋里。");
	text = text.replace("The skin of it makes you think the person had been dead for at least two or three weeks - so the footprints are far too fresh for this body to have created them.", "它的皮肤会让你觉得这个人已经死了至少两三个星期了－所以这些脚印对这个尸体来说太新鲜了，不可能是它造成的。");
	text = text.replace("You\'ve no idea what happened here, but it could not have been good.", "你不知道这里曾发生了什么，但绝不可能是什么好事。");
	text = text.replace(/Going forward, the men of (.*?) should stay sharp for some evil walks these lands\./, "继续行进时，$1 的小伙子们应该保持警惕，因为有什么邪恶的东西正在这篇大陆大行其道。");

//undead_zombie_in_granary_event.nut
	text = text.replace("You come across a man hollering for help, so hysterical that he seems to pay no mind to gaining the attention of armed sellswords who have no allegiance to any house or their laws.", "你偶然碰到一个正大声呼救的人，歇斯底里叫着，似乎完全不在意会引起全副武装的佣兵的注意，明明佣兵不效忠于任何贵族家族或者他们制定的法律。");
	text = text.replace("Please! Help me! There\'s a... a corpse! In the granary!", "拜托！帮助我！有一个…一具尸体！在谷仓里！");
	text = text.replace("He thumbs over his shoulder to a large, wooden building.", "他抬起拇指朝身后一个巨大的木质建筑指了指。");
	text = text.replace("Its front door rattles almost as if on cue.", "建筑的前门好像回应似的刚刚好嘎吱响了起了。");
	text = text.replace("The man loses his mind.", "那个人吓坏了。");
	text = text.replace("That\'s it! That\'s the monster!", "就是那个东西！那个怪物！");
	text = text.replace("Please, go in there and kill it!", "拜托了，请去杀掉他！");
	text = text.replace("We can\'t afford to lose all the food in there!", "我们不能失去里面的所有食物！");
	
	text = text.replace("You grab the man by the shoulders and stare at him as you talk.", "你抓住那个人的肩膀，盯着他说到。");
	text = text.replace("We are going to burn down the granary.", "我们准备烧掉这个谷仓。");
	text = text.replace("What food that is in there, are you listening?", "你听到了吗，里面到底有什么食物？");
	text = text.replace("Listen carefully to what I\'m going to say.", "我接下来要说的，听好了。");
	text = text.replace("The food in there is diseased and should not be eaten.", "那里面的食物已经异变，不能再食用了。");
	text = text.replace("There is nothing to save.", "没有什么需要挽救的。");
	text = text.replace("The peasant, his body shaking as though with a cold, steps out of the way.", "那个农民好像受凉了般哆嗦着让开路。");
	text = text.replace("He squishes his face behind both hands, barely able to watch as two of your sellswords step forward, torches in hand, and set the granary ablaze.", "他双手捂着脸，难以接受地看着你的两个佣兵拿着火把上前把谷仓点燃。");
	text = text.replace("The door stops rattling for a moment, then picks back up, nearly breaking its hinges.", "那扇门一时停了下来，接着又开始发着咯吱声音打开，几乎要把铰链损坏了。");
	text = text.replace("As smoke streams out from its bottom, someone begins crying out.", "随着烟从底部冒出来，有什么人开始尖叫起来。");
	text = text.replace("A joke! A joke!", "开玩笑！开玩笑！");
	text = text.replace("Please, let me out! Aaah, AAAHH!", "拜托，让我出去！啊，啊啊！");
	text = text.replace(/(.*?) rushes to the door and breaks it down\./, "$1 冲过去并砸开了那扇门。");
	text = text.replace("A little boy runs out, a body for a torch, limbs flailing arches of flame.", "一个小男孩跑出来，火炬一样燃着上半身，四肢扭动着带出弓型的火焰。");
	text = text.replace("He settles down on the ground where the mercenaries try to cover him, but it\'s too late.", "他一倒在地上，佣兵们就尝试扑灭他身上的火焰。");
	text = text.replace("He\'s a smoldering ruin by the time the fire is put out.", "当火焰扑灭时，只留下了无声燃烧着的余烬。");
	text = text.replace("The peasant man looks absolutely horrified.", "那个农民看起来一定是吓坏了。");
	text = text.replace("I... I had no idea, I thought it... he kept making growling noises.", "我…不知道，我原以为那是…那东西一直在发出低嗥。");
	text = text.replace("You shake your head and tell the company to quickly get back on the road.", "你对此摇摇头，告诉队伍迅速回去继续赶路。");
	
	text = text.replace("The food is no doubt lost to the diseases by now, and the entire building might be infected with evils beyond human measure.", "毫无疑问那些食物如今已经在恶疾中损坏了，整座建筑可能都被人类无法估量的邪恶所感染。");
	text = text.replace("Slowly, you explain to the man that you will burn his granary down.", "你慢慢地向那个男人解释你将烧掉他的谷仓。");
